var book = {
	"name": "Jingkheiñ",
	"numChapters": 36,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses ha ka ri khlaw Sinai, ha Ka Tabernakl jong ka jingïaseng, ha ka sngi ka banyngkong jong u bnai u ba-ar, ha ka snem ka ba-ar hadien ba ki la ïamih noh na ka ri Ijipt, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To phin shim ka jingkheiñ ïa u paidlang ki khun Israel baroh, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, lem bad ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng, u shynrang baroh uwei pa uwei;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> naduh kiba arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma ha Israel, ma me bad u Aaron phin ïakheiñ ïa ki katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lem bad phi ruh, un long uwei u briew na kawei pa kawei ka jaid; uwei uwei baroh un long u rangbah na ka ïing ki kpa jong u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kine te ki long ki kyrteng kita ki rangbah, ki ban ïeng lem bad phi: na ka jaid Reuben — u Elisur u khun u Shedeur.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ka jaid Simeon — u Shelumiel u khun u Surishaddai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ka jaid Judah — u Nahshon u khun u Amminadab.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ka jaid Issakhar — u Nethaniil u khun u Suar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ka jaid Sabulon — u Eliab u khun u Helon.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ki khun u Joseph; na ka jaid Ephraim — u Elishama u khun u Ammihud; na ka jaid Manasseh — u Gamaliel u khun u Pedahsur.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ka jaid Benjamin — u Abidan u khun u Gideoni.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ka jaid Dan — u Ahieser u khun u Ammishaddai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ka jaid Asher — u Pagiel u khun u Okran.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ka jaid Gad — u Eliasaph u khun u Deuel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ka jaid Naphtali — u Ahira u khun u Enan.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kine ki long kita kiba la ju donnam keiñ na uta u paidlang, ki rangbah jong ki jaid ki kpa jong ki, ki rangbah ki hajar ha Israel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la shim ïa kine ki rangbah ïa kiba la ïathuh ïa ki kyrteng jong ki:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ki la ïalum lang ruh ïa uta u paidlang baroh ha ka sngi banyngkong u bnai u ba-ar, ki la ïa-pynpaw ruh ïa ki jinghiar pateng jong ki katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, uwei pa uwei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumba u la hukum U Trai ha u Moses, kumta u la kheiñ ïa ki ha ka ri khlaw Sinai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki khun u Reuben, uba la kha nyngkong jong u Israel, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng jong ki, uwei pa uwei u shynrang baroh naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, na ka jaid Reuben, ki la long sawphew hynriew hajar sanspah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ki khun u Simeon, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kita ïa kiba la kheiñ kat ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng jong ki, uwei pa uwei u shynrang baroh naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ka jingkheiñ jong kita kiba na ka jaid Simeon, ka la long sanphew khyndai hajar laispah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ki khun u Gad, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Gad, ka la long sawphew san hajar hynriewspah sanphew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ki khun u Judah, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Judah, ka la long hynñiewphew saw hajar hynriewspah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ki khun u Issakhar, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Issakhar, ka la long sanphew saw hajar sawspah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ki khun u Sabulon, na ka jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Sabulon, ka la long sanphew hynñiew hajar sawspah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ki khun u Joseph, na ki khun u Ephraim, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Ephraim, ka la long sawphew hajar sanspah.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ki khun u Manasseh, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Manasseh, ka la long laiphew ar hajar arspah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ki khun u Benjamin, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Benjamin, ka la long laiphew san hajar sawspah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na ki khun u Dan, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Dan, ka la long hynriewphew ar hajar hynñiewspah.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ki khun u Asher, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Asher, ka la long sawphew wei hajar sanspah.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na ki khun u Naphtali, ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> ka jingkheiñ ïa kita kiba na ka jaid Naphtali, ka la long sanphew lai hajar sawspah.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba la kheiñ, ïa kiba la kheiñ u Moses bad u Aaron bad ki rangbah ki Israel, kita ki khat-ar ngut keiñ: uwei uwei u la long na ka bynta ka ïing ki kpa jong u.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Kumta, kita baroh kat kiba la kheiñ na ki khun Israel, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad tam, baroh ha Israel kat kiba lah ïaleit mih ban ïaleh thma;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> kita keiñ ïa kiba la kheiñ baroh ki la long hynriewspah lai hajar bad sanspah sanphew.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki Lebi na ka jaid ki kpa jong ki ym shym la kheiñ hapdeng jong ki.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Namar ba U la lah kren U Trai ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> “Hynrei, wat kheiñ ïa ka jaid Lebi, wat shim ruh ïa ka jingkheiñ ïa ki hapdeng ki khun Israel:",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> hynrei, men thung ïa ki Lebi halor Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla, bad halor kiei kiei baroh ki jingbuh jong ka, bad halor kiei kiei baroh kat kiba dei ïa ka: ki keiñ kin ïabah ïa kata Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa kita baroh ki jingbuh jong ka; kin shakri ruh ïa ka, bad kin ïashong baroh sawdong ïa kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te haba kan sa mih Ka Tabernakl, kita ki Lebi kin ïalied noh ïa ka: haba kan sah noh ruh Ka Tabernakl, ki Lebi kin pynïeng ïa ka: te ïa u nongwei uba nud ban wan hajan yn pynïap ïa u.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad ki khun Israel kin ïashong dara, uwei uwei baroh ha la ka jong ka jaka shong dara, bad uwei uwei baroh hapoh la ka jong ka lama, ha ki paidbah jong ki.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Hynrei, ki Lebi kin ïashong dara baroh sawdong Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla, ba ka jingbitar kan ym long halor u paidbah ki khun Israel: ki Lebi ruh kin ïa-ap ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla.”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la leh baroh kat kumba la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses, kumta ki la leh."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ki khun Israel kin ïashong dara uwei uwei baroh hajan la ka jong ka lama, hapoh ki dak ki ïing ki kpa jong ki: baroh sawdong ha pyrshah Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng kin ïashong na jngai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te shaphang mihngi na kaba mih ka sngi, kin ïashong dara kita kiba dei ïa ka lama ka jong u paidbah u Judah, katba long ki paidïapom jong ki: bad u rangbah ki khun u Judah, un long u Nahshon u khun u Amminadab.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u paidïapom jong u ruh, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long hynñiewphew saw hajar hynriewspah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kita ki ban ïashong kham hajan jong u, kin long ka jaid Issakhar: te u rangbah ki khun u Issakhar, un long u Nethaniil u khun u Suar:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> te u paidïapom jong u ruh, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sanphew saw hajar sawspah:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hadien kata te, ka jaid u Sabulon: bad u Eliab u khun u Helon, un long u rangbah ki khun u Sabulon,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sanphew hynñiew hajar sawspah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Baroh kat kiba la kheiñ lang na u paidbah u Judah, ha ki paidïapom jong ki baroh, ki la long shispah phraphew hynriew hajar bad sawspah. Kine, kin ïamih noh nyngkong keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Shaphang shathie, kan long ka lama ka jong u paidbah u Reuben, katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki: bad u rangbah ki khun u Reuben, un long u Elisur u khun u Shedeur.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u ruh, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sawphew hynriew hajar sanspah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Bad kita ki ban ïashong kham hajan jong u, kin long ka jaid Simeon; bad u rangbah ki khun u Simeon, un long u Shelumiel u khun u Surishaddai:”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sanphew khyndai hajar laispah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Hadien kata te, ka jaid Gad: bad u rangbah ki khun u Gad, un long u Eliasaph u khun u Reuel.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sawphew san hajar hynriewspah sanphew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Baroh te, kat kiba la kheiñ lang na u paidbah u Reuben, ha ki paidïapom jong ki baroh, ki la long shispah sanphew wei hajar bad sanspah sanphew. Kine te, kin sa mih noh ki ba-ar ha ka jingïaid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Hadien kata te, Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng kan sa mih noh, lem bad u paidbah jong ki Lebi hapdeng kita ki paidbah, kat kumba ki la ïashong dara, kumta keiñ kin ïamih noh, uwei uwei baroh ha la ka jong ka jaka, bad hapoh la ki jong ki lama de.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Shaphang sepngi, kan long ka lama u paidbah u Ephraim, katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki: bad u rangbah ki khun u Ephraim, un long u Elishama u khun u Ammihud.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sawphew hajar sanspah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Hajan jong u de, kan long ka jaid Manasseh: bad u rangbah ki khun u Manasseh, un long u Gamaliel u khun u Pedahsur.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long laiphew ar hajar arspah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Hadien kata te, ka jaid Benjamin: bad u rangbah ki khun u Benjamin, un long u Abidan u khun u Gideoni.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long laiphew san hajar sawspah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Baroh te, kat kiba la kheiñ lang na uta u paidbah u Ephraim, ha ki paidbah jong ki baroh, ki la long shispah phra hajar bad shispah. Kine ruh, kin long ki balai ha ka ban mih noh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Shaphang shatei de, kan long ka lama u paidbah u Dan, katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki; bad u rangbah ki khun u Dan, un long u Ahieser u khun u Ammishaddai.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long hynriewphew ar hajar hynñiewspah.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Bad kita ki ban ïashong dara kham hajan jong u, kin long ka jaid Asher: bad u rangbah ki khun u Asher, un long u Pagiel u khun u Okran.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sawphew wei hajar sanspah.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Hadien kata te, ka jaid Naphtali: bad u rangbah ki khun u Naphtali, un long u Ahira u khun u Enan.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u paidïapom jong u, bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long sanphew lai hajar sawspah.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Baroh te, kat kiba la kheiñ lang na uta u paidbah u Dan, ki la long shispah sanphew hynñiew hajar bad hynriewspah. Kine te, kin ïamih noh khatduh eh, lem bad la ki lama.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kine, ki long kiba la kheiñ lang na ki khun Israel, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki: baroh, kat kiba la kheiñ lang ha ki paidlang jong ki, ha ki paidïapom jong ki, baroh keiñ, ki la long hynriewspah lai hajar bad sanspah sanphew.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei ïa ki Lebi, ym shym la kheiñ hapdeng ki khun Israel; kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la leh baroh kat kiba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses, kumta, ki la ïashong dara hapoh ki lama jong ki, bad kumta ruh, ki la ïamih noh, uwei pa uwei katba kum ki kur jong u, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad kine de ki long ki jingkha pateng u Aaron bad u Moses ha kata ka sngi ba U la kren U Trai ha u Moses ha u lum Sinai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kine ruh ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Aaron: u Nadab ïa uba la kha nyngkong, bad u Abihu, u Eleasar, bad u Ithamar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kine ki long ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Aaron, ki lyngdoh ba la pynsleh, ïa kiba u la pynkyntang ma u ïa ka ban kam ïa ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Nadab bad u Abihu, ki la ïap noh ha khmat U Trai, haba ki la nguh da ka ding ka basang ha khmat U Trai, ha ka ri khlaw Sinai, bad kim shym la don khun: bad u Eleasar bad u Ithamar ki la shakri ha ka kam lyngdoh ha khmat u Aaron uba u kpa jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “To wallam hajan ïa ka jaid Lebi, to pynïeng ruh ïa ki ha khmat u Aaron lyngdoh, ba kin ïashakri ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kin ïasumar ruh ïa ka kam jong u, bad ïa ka kam u paidlang baroh de ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ba kin kam ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kin ïasumar ruh ïa ki jingbuh baroh ki jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ïa ka kam jong ki khun Israel, ba kin kam ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Men aiti ruh ïa ki Lebi ha u Aaron, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u: ïa kine, la aiti baroh phar keiñ ha u na ki khun Israel.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Men thung ruh ïa u Aaron, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, ba kin ïasumar ïa ka kam lyngdoh jong ki: te u nongwei u ban nud wan hajan, yn pynïap noh ïa u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ha khmih ruh, ma nga, nga la shimti ïa ki Lebi napdeng ki khun Israel, ha ka jaka kita baroh, ïa kiba la kha nyngkong ka kpoh na ki khun Israel; namar kata, ki Lebi kin long ki jong nga:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> namar kita ïa kiba la kha nyngkong baroh, ki long ki jong nga; naba ha kata ka sngi ba nga la shoh ïa u khun nyngkong baroh ha ka ri Ijipt, nga la pynkyntang ha lade hi ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh ha Israel, bad briew bad mrad: kin long ki jong nga keiñ; ma nga, nga long U Trai.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses ha ka ri khlaw Sinai, u da ong,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “To kheiñ ïa ki khun u Lebi, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ha la ki kur: men kheiñ na ki, ïa u shynrang baroh uba shi bnai ka rta bad tam.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Moses u la kheiñ katba kum kata ka ktien U Trai, kumba la hukum ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kine te, ki long ki khun shynrang u Lebi katba long ki kyrteng jong ki: u Gershon, bad u Kohath, bad u Merari.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kine de ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Gershon katba kum ki kur jong ki: u Libni, bad u Shimei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kohath katba kum ki kur jong ki: u Amram, bad u Ishar, u Hebron, bad u Ussiel.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Merari katba kum ki kur jong ki: u Mahli, bad u Mushi. Kine ki long ki kur ki Lebi, katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na u Gershon, la mih ki kur ki Libni, bad ki kur ki Shimei: kine ki long ki kur ki Gershon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, kat ka jingkheiñ ïa u shynrang baroh naduh kiba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, ïa kiba la kheiñ jong ki keiñ, ki la long hynñiew hajar sanspah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki kur jong ki Gershon kin ïashong dara shadien Ka Tabernakl shaphang sepngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u rangbah jong ka ïing u kpa ki Gershon, un long u Eliasaph u khun u Lael.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka jingsumar ki khun shynrang u Gershon, ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, kan long Ka Tabernakl hi, bad kata ka ïingjaiñ, ka jingsop jong ka ruh, bad ka jingkah ïa ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ki jingkah ïa ka phyllaw, bad ka jaiñ kah ïa ka jingkhang jong kata ka phyllaw, kaba long baroh sawdong ïa Ka Tabernakl, bad baroh sawdong ka duwan de, bad ki tyllai jong ka ruh kiba dei ha ka kam jong ka baroh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na u Kohath, la mih ki kur ki Amram, bad ki kur ki Ishar, bad ki kur ki Hebron, bad ki kur ki Ussiel de: kine ki long ki kur ki Kohath.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka jingkheiñ ïa ki shynrang baroh, naduh kiba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, ka la long phra hajar hynriewspah, kiba sumar ïa ka kam jong kata ka ïing kyntang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki kur jong kita ki khun shynrang u Kohath, kin ïashong dara ha ka phang ka bashathie jong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u rangbah ka ïing jong u kpa ki kur ki Kohath, un long u Elisaphan u khun u Ussiel.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ka jingsumar jong ki te kan long ïa kata ka synduk, bad ka miej, bad ka dieng pynïeng sharak, bad kita ki duwan, bad ki pliang jong kata ka ïing kyntang da kiba ki ju treikam, bad kata ka jingkah ruh de, bad kiei kiei baroh kiba dei ha ka.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad uba ha khlieh halor ki rangbah ki Lebi, un long u Eleasar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, bad un ïoh synshar halor kita kiba sumar ïa ka ïing kyntang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na u Merari, la mih ki kur ki Mahli, bad ki kur ki Mushi: kine keiñ ki long ki kur u Merari.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, kat kum ka jingkheiñ ïa ki shynrang baroh, naduh kiba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, ki la long hynriew hajar bad arspah.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u rangbah ka ïing u kpa kita ki kur u Merari, un long u Suriel u khun u Abihail: kine kin ïashong dara ha ka phang kaba shatei jong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad hapoh ka jingsumar jong kita ki khun shynrang u Merari, kin long ki lyntang jong Ka Tabernakl, bad ki dieng pynthap jong ka, bad ki rijied jong ka, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ka, bad ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad kiei kiei baroh kat kiba dei ha ka;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ki rijied jong ka phyllaw ruh baroh sawdong, bad ki thliew tnaw, bad ki prek jong ki, bad ki tyllai jong ki de.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, kita ki ban ïashong dara ha shuwa Ka Tabernakl shaphang mihngi, kata, ha shuwa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng shaphang mihngi, kin long u Moses, bad u Aaron, bad ki khun shynrang jong u de, ki da ïa-ap sumar ïa ka kam jong ka ïing kyntang, bad ïa ka kam jong ki khun Israel; hynrei, ïa u nongwei u ban nud wan hajan, yn pynïap noh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Baroh te kat kiba la kheiñ na ki Lebi, ïa kiba la kheiñ u Moses bad u Aaron da ka hukum U Trai, ha la ki kur jong ki baroh, ki shynrang baroh keiñ, naduh kiba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, ki la long arphew ar hajar.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U Trai ruh u la ong ha u Moses, “To kheiñ ïa ki shynrang baroh, ïa kiba la kha nyngkong ki jong ki khun Israel, naduh kiba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, to shim ruh ïa ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng jong ki.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Men shim ruh ïa ki Lebi ha nga (Nga long ma nga U Trai) ha ka jaka kiba la kha nyngkong baroh hapdeng ki khun Israel; bad ïa ki jingri jong ki Lebi ha ka jaka kiba la kha nyngkong baroh na ki jingri jong ki khun Israel.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te u Moses u la kheiñ, kumba la hukum U Trai ïa u, ïa baroh kat ïa kiba la kha nyngkong hapdeng ki khun Israel.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te ki shynrang baroh ba la kha nyngkong, katba shong ka jingkheiñ ïa ki kyrteng jong ki, naduh uba shi bnai ka rta bad tam, kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long arphew ar hajar bad arspah hynñiewphew lai.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “To shim ïa kita ki Lebi ha ka jaka ïa kiba la kha nyngkong baroh hapdeng ki khun Israel, bad ïa ki jingri jong ki Lebi ha ka jaka ki jingri jong ki: te kita ki Lebi, kin long ki jong nga: Nga long ma nga U Trai.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te na ka bynta kita ïa ki ban siewspah na kita ki arspah hynñiewphew lai ïa kiba la kha nyngkong jong ki khun Israel, kiba tam ïa ki Lebi,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> men sa shim san shekel namar uwei pa uwei; katba shong ka shekel ka jaka kyntang, men shim ïa ki (shi shekel ka long arphew gerah):",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> bad men ai ïa kita ki sbai, da kiba la siewspah ïa kita kiba tam, ha u Aaron bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim ïa ki sbai ka jingsiewspah jong kiba tam, nalor kita ïa kiba la siewspah da ki Lebi:",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> na kita ïa kiba la kha nyngkong jong ki khun Israel, u la shim ïa ki sbai; shi hajar bad laispah hynriewphew san shekel, katba shong ka shekel ka jaka kyntang:",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> u Moses u la ai ruh ïa ki sbai jong kita ïa kiba la siewspah ha u Aaron, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u, katba kum kata ka ktien U Trai, kumba u la hukum U Trai keiñ ïa u Moses."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To shim ïa ka jingkheiñ ki khun shynrang u Kohath napdeng ki khun shynrang u Lebi, ha la ka ïing ka ïing, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> naduh uba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam haduh uba sanphew snem, baroh kat kiba leit bsut ha ka kynhun lyngdoh, ban trei ïa ka kam ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kane kan long ka kam kita ki khun shynrang u Kohath ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, shaphang kiei kiei ki bakyntang tam:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> te haba uta u paidlang un sa ïaid noh, u Aaron un wan, lem bad ki khun shynrang jong u, bad kin ïalaw noh ïa ka jingkah bapynïakhlad, bad kin ïatap noh da ka, ïa ka synduk ka jingphla:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad halor kata ruh, kin buh ïa ka jingtap da ki snieh takash, te halor kata pat, kin siang da ki jaiñ bthuh baroh phar, bad kin ïa-pynphrung ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad halor ka miej ba buh ïa ki 'pu pyni, kin ïasiang da ki jaiñ bthuh, bad halor kata, kin ïabuh ïa ki pliang, bad ïa ki siang, bad ïa ki khuri, bad ïa ki jingtap ruh de, ïa ka ban tap: bad uta u kpu, un long halor jong ka ha la ka sngi:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> kin ïasiang ruh halor jong ki, da ka jaiñ basaw hain hain, bad halor kata de, kin ïatap da ka jingtap da ki snieh takash, bad kin ïa-pynphrung ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad haba ki la shim ïa ka jaiñ bthuh, kin ïatap ïa ka halor ka jingbat sharak jong ka jingshai, bad ki sharak jong ka, bad ki nap jong ka, bad ki pliang buh nap jong ka, bad ki khulpi jong ka baroh, da kiba ki ju shakri ïa ka:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad kin ïabuh ïa ka, bad ïa kiei kiei ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, hapoh ka jingtap da ki snieh takash, bad kin ïabuh ïa kata, halor u dieng jingbah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad halor ka duwan ksiar, kin ïasiang da ka jaiñ bthuh, kin ïatap ruh ïa ka da ka jingtap na ki snieh takash, bad kin ïa-pynphrung ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> kin ïashim ruh ïa ki atiar baroh ki jong kata ka kam, da kiba ki ïatrei jingtrei ha ka jaka kyntang, bad kin ïasop ïa ki hapoh ka jaiñ bthuh, bad kin ïatap ruh ïa ki da ka jingtap na ki snieh takash, bad kin ïabuh ïa ki de, halor ka jingbah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kin khat noh de, ïa ka dpei na ka duwan, bad kin ïasiang halor jong ka da ka jaiñ basaw bthuh:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> kin ïabuh ruh halor jong ka, ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, da kiba ki ïatrei ïa ka kam jong ka, kata, ïa ki khiew rah ding, bad ïa ki bnoh doh, bad ïa ki siang rah dpei, bad ïa ki pliang, baroh keiñ ki pliang kiba dei ïa ka duwan; bad kin ïasiang halor jong ka da ka jingtap na ki snieh takash, bad kin pynphrung ruh ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda u Aaron, bad ki khun shynrang jong u, ki la lah tap noh ïa ka jaka kyntang, bad ïa kiei kiei ki jingbuh baroh ki jong kata ka jaka kyntang, haba u paidlang un sa ïaid noh; ynda kumta, kin wan ki khun shynrang u Kohath ban ïabah ïa ki: hynrei, kin ym ktah ïa kaei kaei ka bakyntang, ïoh kin ïap noh. Kine kiei kiei, ki long ki jingkit ki khun shynrang u Kohath, ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ha ka kam u Eleasar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, ka dei ka umphniang ka jong ka jingshai, bad ka jingainguh thang baiwbih, bad ka jingainguh bam ba ha la ka sngi, bad ïa ka umphniang ban pynsleh, bad ban sumar keiñ ïa Ka Tabernakl baroh, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba don hapoh jong ka, ha kata ka jaka kyntang, bad ha ki jingbuh jong ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, u da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “To phi wat ot noh ïa ka jaid ki kur u Kohath napdeng ki Lebi:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> hynrei, to leh kumne ïa ki, ba kin ïoh im, bad ba kin ym ïap noh, haba ki wan hajan ïa kita kiei kiei ki bakhuid tam: u Aaron, bad ki khun shynrang jong u, kin ïaleit hapoh, bad kin ïabuh ïa ki uwei pa uwei ha la ka jong ka jong ka kam, bad ha la ka jong ka jong ka jingkit:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, wat shah ïa ki, ban bsut shapoh ban khmih haba dang ïatap noh ïa kita kiei kiei ki bakhuid, ïoh kin ïap noh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “To shim ruh ïa ka jingkheiñ, ïa ki khun shynrang u Gershon, ha la ki ïing ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, katba kum ki kur jong ki:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, men kheiñ ïa ki baroh kat kiba wan ïa ka ban kam jingkam, ban trei ïa ka kam ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kane kan long ka kam jong ki kur u Gershon, ha kaba trei, bad ha kaba kit:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> kin ïabah ïa ki jingkah jong Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ïa ka jingsop jong ka, bad ïa kata ka jingsop na ki snieh takash kaba halor jong ka, bad ïa ka jingkah ïa ka jingkhang jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ïa ki jingkah ka phyllaw ruh, bad ïa ki jingkah ka jingkhang ka khyrdop jong ka phyllaw, kaba baroh sawdong ïa Ka Tabernakl bad ïa ka duwan, ïa ki tyllai jong ki ruh, bad ïa ki atiar baroh ka kam jong ki, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ba la thaw na ka bynta jong ki, kumta kin ïakam.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Katba kum ka hukum u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u, kumta kan long ka kam baroh ka jong kita ki khun shynrang u Gershon, ha ki jingkit jong ki baroh, bad ha ka jingtrei jong ki baroh: phin aiti ruh ha ki, ïa ki jingkit jong ki baroh ban sumar.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kane te ka long ka kam jong ki khun shynrang u Gershon ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: bad ka jingsumar jong ki, kan long ha ka kti u Ithamar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Ïa ki khun shynrang u Merari ruh, ha la ki kur ki kur, men kheiñ ïa ki, katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam, haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, men kheiñ ïa ki, baroh kat kiba wan ha kata ka kam, ïa ka ban trei ïa ka kam Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kane ka long ka jingkit jong ki, ïa ka ban sumar ha ka kam jong ki baroh ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng; ïa ki lyntang jong Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa ki dieng pynthap jong ki, bad ïa ki rijied jong ki, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ki de;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ïa kita ki rijied jong ka phyllaw ruh baroh sawdong, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ki, bad ki prek jong ki, bad ki tyllai jong ki, lem bad ki atiar jong ki baroh, lem bad kiei kiei baroh kiba donkam jong ki: te da kaba buh ïa la ki kyrteng, phin kheiñ ïa ki atiar ba kin ïasumar, bad ba kin ïabah ma ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kane ka long ka kam jong kita ki kur ki khun shynrang u Merari, katba kum ka kam jong ki baroh, ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, hapoh ka kti u Ithamar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Aaron, bad ki rangbah uta u paidlang, ki la ïakheiñ ïa ki khun shynrang ki Kohath, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, bad katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam, haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, uwei uwei baroh uba wan shim ïa kane ka kam ban trei ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> te kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, ki la long ar hajar hynñiewspah sanphew.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na kita ki kur ki Kohath, baroh kat kiba lah ban kam jingkam ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ïa kiba u Moses, bad u Aaron, ki la ïakheiñ katba kum ka hukum U Trai da ka kti u Moses.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki khun shynrang u Gershon, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, bad katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam, haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, uwei uwei baroh uba wan shim ïa kane ka kam, ïa ka ban trei ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> te kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki la long ar hajar hynriewspah laiphew.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki kur ki khun shynrang u Gershon, na kita baroh kat kiba lah ban kam jingkam ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ïa kiba u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïakheiñ katba kum ka hukum U Trai.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki kur ki khun shynrang u Merari, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam, haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, uwei uwei baroh uba wan shim ïa kane ka kam, ïa ka ban trei ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, ki la long lai hajar bad arspah.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki kur ki khun shynrang u Merari, ïa kiba u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïakheiñ katba kum ka hukum U Trai da ka kti u Moses.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kita baroh ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki Lebi, ïa kiba u Moses, bad u Aaron, bad ki rangbah ki Israel ki la ïakheiñ, ha la ki kur ki kur jong ki, bad katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> naduh kiba laiphew snem ka rta bad tam, haduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, uwei uwei baroh uba wan shim ïa ka ban kam ïa ka jingkam shakri, bad ïa ka ban trei shaphang ki jingkit ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki, ki la long phra hajar sanspah phraphew.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Katba kum ka hukum U Trai, da ka kti u Moses u la kheiñ ïa ki, uwei pa uwei baroh katba kum ka kam jong u, bad katba kum ka jingkit jong u: kumne la kheiñ ïa ki, kumba la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To hukum ïa ki khun Israel, ba kin ïa-pynmih noh shabar ka jaka shong dara, ïa uwei uwei baroh u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh, bad ïa uwei uwei baroh u bapang mihsnam, bad ïa uwei uwei baroh ba la pyntngit sang da ka metïap:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad shynrang bad kynthei phin ïa-pynmih noh, shabar kata ka jaka shong dara phin buh noh ïa ki keiñ; ba kin ym ïa-pyntngit sang ïa la ki dara, hapdeng kiba nga shong ma nga.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kita ki khun Israel ki la leh kumta, bad ki la ïa-pynmih noh ïa ki, shabar ka jaka shong dara, kumba u la kren U Trai ïa u Moses, kumta ki la leh ki khun Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, ‘Lada u shynrang ne ka kynthei kin leh ïa kawei na kita ki pop ba ju leh ki briew, da kaba leh palat pyrshah ïa U Trai, bad ba kata ka mynsiem ka la rem;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> te kumta kin ïaphla ïa la ka pop ba ki la leh: bad un sa buria ïa la ka jingpalat da ka bai trai jong ka, bad un ai lang ruh lem bad kata, ïa shi bynta na kaba san bynta jong ka, bad un ai ïa ka ha uta ïa uba u la leh palat.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, lada u briew um don u kur, ïa ka ban buria ïa ka jingpalat ha u, to ai te ban buria ïa kata ka jingpalat ha U Trai, ïa ka ban long ka jong u lyngdoh; nalor uta u 'lang-kuna, da uba yn sa pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ïa ka jingainguh baroh ba pynkyntiew na kiei kiei baroh kiba la kyntang jong ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ki wallam ainguh sha u lyngdoh, kan long ka jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad kiei kiei baroh ba la kyntang jong u briew, kin long ki jong u: kaei kaei ruh ba u ai uno uno ruh ha u lyngdoh, kan long ka jong u.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Lada ka tnga jong uno uno u briew ka ïaid lyndet ïa u, bad ka leh palat pyrshah ïa u,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad lada don uwei u briew uba la ïoh ïa ka, bad ba kata ka long ba la buhrieh na ki khmat u tnga jong ka, ba ym shym da bna ruh, bad la pynkheiñ burom sang ïa ka, bad ba ym don sakhi pyrshah ïa ka, bad ba ym shym la kem ïa ka ha kata ka kam;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad haba khie shit ka mynsiem ka jingbishni ha u, bad ba u bishni ïa la ka tnga, haba la pynjahburom sang ïa ka: lane haba wan ka mynsiem ka jingbishni ha u, bad ba u bishni ïa la ka tnga, bad haba ym shym la pynjahburom sang ïa ka:’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> haba kumta te, ai ba uta u tnga un wallam ïa la ka tnga ha u lyngdoh, un wallam ruh ïa ka jingainguh jong ka na ka bynta jong ka, ïa ka bynta bashiphew na ka shi ephah u 'purew Kew; wat ai te ba un theh umphniang halor jong ka, lane buh ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ka; naba ka long ka jingainguh ka jingbishni, ka jingainguh ka jingpynkynmaw, kaba pynkynmaw keiñ ïa ka jingpalat.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Te uta u lyngdoh un wallam ïa ka hajan, bad un buh ruh ïa ka ha khmat U Trai:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad uta u lyngdoh un shim na ka um bakyntang ha u khiew khyndew; bad uta u lyngdoh un shim ruh na ka 'dewmet kaba don ha ka tbian Ka Tabernakl, bad un buh ïa ka ha ka um:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> to ai ruh ba uta u lyngdoh un buh ïa ka ha khmat U Trai, bad ba un loit noh ïa ka jaiñ tapmoh khlieh jong ka, bad un buh ha ki kti jong ka, ïa kata ka jingainguh ka jingpynkynmaw, kaba long ka jingainguh ka jingbishni: te kata ka um bakthang kaba pynlong ïa ka jingtim kan long ha ka kti uta u lyngdoh:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te uta u lyngdoh un pynsmai ïa ka, bad un ong ha kata ka briew, ‘Lada u briew um shym la thiah bad pha, bad lada pham shym la ïaidwir noh sha ka jingbymkhuid sang bad uwei pat ha ka jaka la u jong u tnga, to long pha kaba lait na kane ka um ka bakthang kaba pynlong ïa ka jingtim:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, lada pha la ïaid lyndet noh na la u tnga, bad ba pha long ïa kaba la pynkheiñ burom sang, bad ba uwei pat u briew nalor u tnga jong pha u la ïoh ïa pha:’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ynda kumta, ai ba u lyngdoh un pynsmai ïa kata ka briew da ka jingsmai ka jingtim, bad uta u lyngdoh un ong ha kata ka briew, ‘To ai ba U Trai un pynlong ka jingtim, bad ka jingsmai ïa pha hapdeng ki briew jong pha, haba U Trai un pynpyut ïa ka lbong jong pha, bad ïa ka kpoh jong pha un pyn-at;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> to ai ruh ba kane ka um kaba pynlong ïa kata ka jingtim, kan leit hapoh ki snier jong pha, ïa ka ban pyn-at ïa ka kpoh jong pha, bad ïa ka ban pynpyut ïa ka lbong jong pha:’ To ai ruh ba kata ka briew kan ong, ‘Amen, Amen.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Uta u lyngdoh ruh, un thoh ïa kine ki jingtim ha ka kot, bad un pyndam noh ïa ki ha kata ka um bakthang:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> te un pyndih ïa kata ka briew na kata ka um bakthang ba pynlong ïa kata ka jingtim: bad to ai ïa kata ka um ba pynlong ïa ka jingtim ban leit hapoh jong ka bad kan kylla kthang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u lyngdoh un shim na ka kti jong kata ka briew ïa kata ka jingainguh ka jingbishni, bad un pynkaweh ïa kata ka jingainguh ha khmat U Trai, bad un ainguh ïa ka halor ka duwan de:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> uta u lyngdoh un shim ruh shi kham na kata ka jingainguh, kaba long ka jingpynkynmaw jong ka, bad un da thang ruh ïa ka halor kata ka duwan, bad hadien kata, un pyndih ïa kata ka briew da kata ka um.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda u la pyndih te ïa ka na kata ka um, lada la pynkheiñ burom sang ïa ka, bad lada ka la leh palat ïa la u tnga, kan long ba kata ka um kaba pynlong ïa kata ka jingtim kan long kthang hapoh jong ka, bad kan pyn-at ïa ka kpoh jong ka, kan pynpyut ruh ïa ka lbong jong ka; te kata ka briew kan long ka jingtim hapdeng ki briew jong ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, lada ym shym la pynkheiñ burom sang ïa ka, bad ba ka long ka bakhuid; te kumta kan ïohlait noh, bad kan kha khun ruh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Kane ka long ka hukum ka jingbishni, haba ka tnga ka la phai wir noh sha uwei pat ha ka jaka la u jong u tnga, bad ba ka pynkheiñ burom sang ïa lade;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> lane haba ka mynsiem ka jingbishni, ka khie shit ha u briew, bad u bishni ïa la ka tnga; te kumta un buh ïa la ka tnga ha khmat U Trai, bad u lyngdoh un pyndep halor jong ka, katba kum kane ka hukum.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te uta u tnga un long uba lait ksan na kane ka jingleh pop, bad kata ka tnga kan kit ïa la ka jong ka jingleh pop.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki; ‘Haba u briew lane ka briew ki la pynkyrpang ïa lade ïa ka ban kular skhem ïa ka jingkular Nasar, ban pynkyntang ïa lade ha U Trai:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> to un kyndiah noh na ka Waiñ, bad ka kyiad; wat ai ruh ba un dih na ka Waiñ bajew, lane na ka kyiad bajew, to wat ai ruh ba un dih na ka um ki soh Waiñ, bad un ym ïoh bam ïa ki soh Waiñ ba-im lane ïa kiba la thad.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Baroh ki sngi ka jinglong Nasar jong u, un ym ïoh bam ei ei ruh em keiñ ba la thaw na u dieng soh Waiñ, naduh u shyieng haduh ka snep.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “ ‘Baroh kita ki sngi ka jingkular skhem ka jinglong Nasar jong u, ka syrti kan ym ktah ïa ka khlieh jong u: tad ynda ba la pyndep ïa kita ki sngi, ba u la pynkyntang ïa lade ha U Trai, un long u bakhuid, bad un shah ïa ki rynjup u shñiuh ka khlieh jong u ban nang san.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “ ‘Baroh kita ki sngi ba u la pynkyntang ïa lade ha U Trai, to un ym wan hajan ka metïap.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> To wat ai ba un pyntngit sang ïa lade namar u kpa jong u, lane namar ka kmie jong u, lane namar u para jong u, lane namar ka para jong u, haba ki ïap: naba ka dak ka jingpynkyntang ha U Blei jong u, ka don halor ka khlieh jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Baroh kita ki sngi ka jinglong Nasar jong u, un long u bakhuid ha U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “ ‘Hynrei, lada uno uno ruh un ïap noh ryngmang hajan jong u, bad ba la pyntngit ïa ka khlieh ka bakyntang jong u; te kumta, un khi ïa la ka khlieh ha ka sngi ka jingpynkhuid jong u, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew keiñ un khi ïa ka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka baphra, un wallam shi jur ki lyngdkhur, lane shi jur ki khun paro, ha u lyngdoh, ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> te ai ba uta u lyngdoh un ainguh ïa kawei, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop, bad ïa kata kawei, ban long ka jingainguh thang, kumta keiñ, un pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta jong u, namar ba u la leh pop hajan uta u baïap, un pynkyntang ïa la ka khlieh ruh, ha kata kajuh ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad un pynkyntang ha U Trai ïa ki sngi ka jinglong Nasar jong u, bad un wallam ïa uwei u khun langbrot uba shi snem, ban long ka jingkñia namar ka jingpalat: te yn sa pynlehnohei ïa kita ki sngi kiba mynshuwa, namar ba la pyntngit sang ïa ka jinglong Nasar jong u.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Kane te ka hukum ka jinglong Nasar, haba la pyndep ïa kita ki sngi ka jinglong Nasar jong u: ‘To ai ba yn wallam ïa u ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad un ainguh ïa la ka jingainguh ha U Trai, da uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem u ba-tlem janai, ban long ka jingainguh thang, bad da kawei ka khun langbrot ba shi snem ba-tlem janai, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop, bad da uwei u langbrot ba-tlem janai, ban long ka jingkñia bapynïasuk,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> da shi shang u kpu bakhlem thiat ruh, kata, da ki kpu ba la thaw da kaba khleh u 'purew bani bad ka umphniang, bad da ki kpu bastang bakhlem thiat ba la pynsleh da ka umphniang, lem bad da ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u lyngdoh un wallam ïa ki ha khmat U Trai, bad un ainguh ïa ka jingkñia sait pop jong u, bad ïa ka jingainguh thang jong u:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> un ainguh ruh ïa uta u langbrot ban long ka jingkñia bapynïasuk ha U Trai, lem bad ïa kata ka shi shang u kpu bakhlem thiat: bad uta u lyngdoh un ainguh ruh ïa ka jingainguh bam jong u, bad ïa ka jingainguh dih jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uta u Nasar un khi ïa ka khlieh ka jinglong Nasar jong u ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad un shim ïa uta u shñiuh ka khlieh ka jinglong Nasar jong u, bad un buh ïa u ha kata ka ding kaba hapoh ka jingkñia bapynïasuk.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u lyngdoh un shim ïa kata ka kti ba la shet ka jong uta u langbrot, bad ïa uwei u kpu bakhlem thiat na kata ka shang, bad ïa uwei u kpu bastang bakhlem thiat, bad un buh ïa ki ha ki kti jong uta u Nasar, ynda u la khi noh ïa u shñiuh ka jinglong Nasar jong u:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> te u lyngdoh un kaweh ïa ki ban long ka jingainguh bakaweh ha khmat U Trai; kane ka long ka bakhuid ïa u lyngdoh, lem bad ka krung kaweh, bad ka kti bakyntiew de: hadien kata te, uta u Nasar u lah ban dih Waiñ.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kane te ka long kata ka hukum u Nasar uba la kular skhem, bad ka jingainguh jong u ha U Trai namar ka jinglong Nasar jong u, nalor kata ba ka kti jong u ka lah ban kot: katba kum kata ka jingkular skhem ïa kaba u la kular, kumta ka dei keiñ ïa u ban leh, katba kum ka hukum ka jinglong Nasar jong u.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “To kren ha u Aaron, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u, da kaba ong, ‘Kumne phin kyrkhu ïa ki khun Israel; da kaba ong ha ki,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “ ‘ “U Trai un da kyrkhu ïa me, bad un da sumar ïa me:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Trai un da tyngshaiñ noh ïa la ka khmat halor jong me, bad un da leh isynei ïa me:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Trai un da kyntiew ïa la ka khmat halor jong me, bad un da ai ka jingsuk ïa me.” ’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Kumta keiñ, kin ïabuh ïa ka kyrteng jong nga halor ki khun Israel; ma nga te ngan kyrkhu ïa ki.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u Moses u la lah pyndep ban pynïeng ïa kata Ka Tabernakl, bad ban pynsleh ïa ka, bad ban pynkyntang ïa ka, bad ïa ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, ïa ka duwan ruh, bad ïa ki jingbuh jong ka, bad ba u la pynsleh ïa ki, bad ba u la pynkyntang ïa ki:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ki rangbah ki Israel kiba ha khlieh ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, kiba la long ki rangbah na ki jaid, bad kiba long halor kita ïa kiba la kheiñ, ki la ai la ki jingainguh:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ki la wallam ïa la ka jingainguh ha khmat U Trai, hynriew tylli ki kali ba la tap nalor, bad khat-ar tylli ki masi dab; shi kali na ka bynta ar ngut na kita ki rangbah, bad uwei u masi dab na ka bynta uwei pa uwei na ki: bad ki la wallam ïa ki ha khmat Ka Tabernakl.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “To pdiang ïa kine na ki, ba kin long ïa ka ban ïaitrei ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng; men sam ruh ïa ki ha ki Lebi, ha uwei pa uwei katba kum ka kam jong u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses u la pdiang ïa kita ki kali, bad kita ki masi dab, u la sam ruh ïa ki ha kita ki Lebi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ar tylli ki kali, bad saw tylli ki masi dab, u la ai ha ki khun shynrang u Gershon, katba kum ka kam jong ki:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad saw tylli ki kali, bad phra tylli ki masi dab, u la ai ha ki khun shynrang u Merari, katba kum ka kam jong ki, hapoh ka kti u Ithamar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, ha ki khun shynrang u Kohath, um shym la ai satia: naba ka kam ka jaka kyntang ka la dei ha ki; ki shu ïabah ïa ka halor ki tyrpeng jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki rangbah ki la ai ki jingainguh, ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa ka duwan ha kata ka sngi ba la pynsleh ïa ka, bad kita ki rangbah ki la wallam ïa ki jingainguh jong ki ha khmat kata ka duwan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “Uwei pa uwei u rangbah ha la ka jong ka sngi, un ai ïa la ka jingainguh, ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa ka duwan.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ka sngi nyngkong, u Nahshon u khun u Amminadab, na ka jaid Judah, u la ai la ka jingainguh:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ka jingainguh jong u ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa, ka jingkhia jong ka, ka la long shispah laiphew shekel, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel ba-dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Nahshon u khun u Amminadab.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, u la ainguh u Nethaniil u khun u Suar, u rangbah ka jaid Issakhar:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u la ainguh ïa la ka jingainguh, ïa kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Nethaniil u khun u Suar.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha ka sngi ka balai, u Eliab u khun u Helon, u rangbah ki khun u Sabulon, u la ainguh:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Eliab u khun u Helon.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ha ka sngi ka basaw, u Elisur u khun u Shedeur, u rangbah ki khun u Reuben, u la ainguh:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Elisur u khun u Shedeur.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ha ka sngi ka basan, u Shelumiel u khun u Surishaddai, u rangbah ki khun u Simeon, u la ainguh:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Shelumiel u khun u Surishaddai.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bahynriew, u Eliasaph u khun u Deuel, u rangbah ki khun u Gad, u la ainguh:",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Eliasaph u khun u Deuel.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, u la ainguh u Elishama u khun u Ammihud, u rangbah ki khun u Ephraim:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Elishama u khun u Ammihud.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Ha ka sngi ka baphra, u la ainguh u Gamaliel u khun u Pedahsur, u rangbah ki khun u Manasseh:",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop:",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Gamaliel u khun u Pedahsur.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bakhyndai, u la ainguh u Abidan u khun u Gideoni, u rangbah ki khun u Benjamin:",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Abidan u khun u Gideoni.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bashiphew, u la ainguh u Ahieser u khun u Ammishaddai, u rangbah ki khun u Dan:",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel, kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Ahieser u khun u Ammishaddai.",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bakhatwei, u la ainguh u Pagiel u khun u Okran, u rangbah ki khun u Asher:",
			"73": "<sup>73</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"74": "<sup>74</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"75": "<sup>75</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"76": "<sup>76</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"77": "<sup>77</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Pagiel u khun u Okran.",
			"78": "<sup>78</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bakhat-ar, u la ainguh u Ahira u khun u Enan, u rangbah ki khun u Naphtali:",
			"79": "<sup>79</sup> Ka jingainguh jong u, ka la long kawei ka pliang rupa kaba shispah laiphew shekel ka jingkhia jong ka, kawei ka khuri rupa kaba hynñiewphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang; baroh ar kiba dap da u 'purew bani ba la khleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam;",
			"80": "<sup>80</sup> kawei ka siang ksiar kaba shiphew shekel kaba dap da ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"81": "<sup>81</sup> uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, uwei u khun langbrot ba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang;",
			"82": "<sup>82</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop;",
			"83": "<sup>83</sup> te namar ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ar tylli ki masi dab, san tylli ki langbrot shynrang, san tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, san tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem: kane ka jingainguh u Ahira u khun u Enan.",
			"84": "<sup>84</sup> Kane ka long ka jingpynkyntang ïa kata ka duwan, ha kata ka sngi ba la pynsleh ïa ka, da kita ki rangbah ki Israel: khat-ar tylli ki pliang rupa, khat-ar tylli ki khuri rupa, khat-ar tylli ki siang ksiar:",
			"85": "<sup>85</sup> kawei kawei ka pliang rupa ka la khia shispah laiphew shekel, bad kawei kawei ka khuri rupa ka la khia hynñiewphew shekel: kita ki khiew rupa baroh ki la khia ar hajar sawspah shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang;",
			"86": "<sup>86</sup> kita ki siang ksiar, khat-ar tylli, kiba dap da ka jingiwbih thang, kawei kawei ka siang ka la khia shiphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang: ka ksiar jong kita ki siang baroh ka la khia shispah arphew shekel:",
			"87": "<sup>87</sup> kita ki masi dab baroh jong kata ka jingainguh thang, ki la long khat-ar tylli ki masi lyngraw, ki langbrot shynrang, khat-ar tylli, ki khun langbrot ba shi snem, khat-ar tylli, lem bad ki jingainguh bam jong ki: bad ki khun blang, khat-ar tylli, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop.",
			"88": "<sup>88</sup> Te kita ki masi dab baroh jong kata ka jingkñia bapynïasuk, ki la long arphew saw tylli ki masi lyngraw, ki langbrot shynrang, hynriewphew tylli, ki 'lang sohmoh, hynriewphew tylli, ki khun langbrot ba shi snem, hynriewphew tylli. Kane ka la long kata ka jingpynkyntang ïa ka duwan, ynda la lah pynsleh ïa ka.",
			"89": "<sup>89</sup> Te haba u Moses u da leit hapoh Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ïa ka ban kren ha U Blei, u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa ktien kaba kren ha u nalor kata ka jaka-isynei kaba halor kata ka synduk ka jingphla, napdeng kita ki ar tylli ki Kherub: U la kren ruh ha u."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha u Aaron, ong ruh ha u, ‘Haba me thang ïa ki sharak, to ai ba kita ki hynñiew tylli ki sharak kin ïa-pynshai marpyrshah ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak.’ ”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te kumta, u Aaron u la leh; u la thang ïa kita ki sharak jong ka marpyrshah ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak, kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kane ka jingthaw ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak, ka la long ka ksiar keiñ ba la shoh tylli: naduh ka met jong ka haduh ki syntiew jong ka, ka la long ka ksiar ba la shoh tylli: katba kum kata ka dur ba la pyni U Trai ha u Moses, kumta u la thaw ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “To shim ïa ki Lebi napdeng ki khun Israel, bad to pynkhuid ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kumne keiñ men leh ha ki ïa ka ban pynkhuid ïa ki: To synreit ïa ka um ka jingpynkhuid halor jong ki, kin khi ruh ïa ka met jong ki baroh, kin sait ïa la ki jaiñ ruh, kumta te, kin ïapynkhuid kyntang ïa lade.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, kin shim ïa u masi lyngraw, lem bad ka jingainguh bam jong u, kaba na u 'purew bani ba la khleh da ka umphniang, bad men shim ïa uwei pat u masi lyngraw ïa ka ban long ka jingkñia sait pop.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Men wallam ruh ïa ki Lebi ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: bad men lum lang ïa u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> men wallam ruh ïa ki Lebi ha khmat U Trai: bad ki khun Israel kin ïabuh ïa la ki kti ha kita ki Lebi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Aaron un aiti nguh ïa ki Lebi ha khmat U Trai, ban long ka jingainguh bakaweh ki khun Israel, khnang ba kin ïoh trei ïa ka kam U Trai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki Lebi, kin buh ïa ki kti jong ki ha ki khlieh kita ki masi lyngraw: me ruh men ainguh ïa uwei, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop, bad ïa uta uwei, ban long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai, ïa ka ban pynlong ka kuna na ka bynta ki Lebi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te men buh ïa ki Lebi ha khmat u Aaron, bad ha khmat ki khun shynrang jong u, bad men aiti nguh ïa ki, ban long ka jingainguh bapynkaweh ha U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Kumta men pynkyrpang ïa ki Lebi napdeng ki khun Israel, te ki Lebi, kin long ki jong nga.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Lebi kin ïaleit hapoh, ban trei ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: bad me men pynkhuid ïa ki, bad men aiti nguh ïa ki, ban long ka jingainguh bapynkaweh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar ha nga la ai ïa ki baroh phar napdeng ki khun Israel; ha ka jaka jong uta ïa uba la kha nyngkong ka kpoh baroh, ïa uba la kha nyngkong keiñ na ki khun Israel baroh, nga la shim ïa ki ha lade.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kita baroh ïa kiba la kha nyngkong hapdeng ki khun Israel, bad briew, bad mrad, ki dei ki jong nga; naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la shoh ïa kita baroh ba la kha nyngkong ha ka ri Ijipt, nga la pynkyntang ïa ki ha lade hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad nga la shim ïa ki Lebi na ka bynta kita ïa kiba la kha nyngkong baroh na ki khun Israel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te nga la aiti ïa ki Lebi kum ka jingai ha u Aaron, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u, napdeng ki khun Israel, ban trei ïa ka kam ki khun Israel ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ban pynlong ka kuna na ka bynta ki khun Israel: ba kumta, kaba ïapkhlam kan ym long shuh hapdeng ki khun Israel, haba ki khun Israel kin wan hajan kata ka jaka kyntang.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Aaron, bad uta paidlang baroh ki khun Israel, ki la leh ha kita ki Lebi: kat kumba ïa baroh ba la hukum U Trai ha u Moses shaphang ki Lebi, kumta ki khun Israel ki la leh ha ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ïa ki Lebi la pynkhuid, bad ki la sait ïa la ki jaiñ; bad u Aaron u la ainguh ïa ki, ban long ka jingainguh pynkaweh ha khmat U Trai: u Aaron ruh u la pynlong ka kuna na ka bynta jong ki, ïa ka ban pynkhuid ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Lebi ki la ïaleit hapoh, ïa ka ban trei ïa ka kam jong ki ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ha khmat u Aaron, bad ha khmat ki khun shynrang jong u: kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses shaphang ki Lebi, kumta ki la leh ha ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Kane ka long kata kaba dei ïa ki Lebi: naduh kiba arphew san snem ka rta bad tam, kin ïaleit hapoh, ïa ka ban shakri ha ka kam Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad naduh kiba sanphew snem ka rta, kin wan phai noh na kaba shakri ïa kata ka kam, ba kin ym shakri shuh;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> hynrei, kin ïashakri lem bad ki para jong ki, hapoh Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ïa ka ban ap khmih, hynrei, kin ym ïakam jingkam shuh. Kumne men leh keiñ ïa ki Lebi shaphang ki jingïasumar jong ki.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses ha ka ri khlaw Sinai, ha ka snem ka ba-ar ynda ki la ïamih noh na ka ri Ijipt, ha u bnai banyngkong, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To ai ba ki khun Israel kin ïarakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ruh ha ka aïom ba la buh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha ka bakhatsaw sngi, ha une u bnai, ha kaba la janmiet, phin ïarakhe ïa ka ha ka aïom jong ka: katba kum ki rukom jong ka baroh, bad katba kum ki niam ki rukom jong ka baroh, kumta keiñ phin ïarakhe ïa ka.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Moses u la kren ha ki khun Israel, ba kin ïarakhe ïa kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la ïarakhe ïa kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha ka bakhatsaw sngi, ha u bnai banyngkong, ha kaba la janmiet, ha ka ri khlaw Sinai: baroh kat kumba la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses, kumta ki la leh ki khun Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te la don ki briew ïa kiba la pynsang da ka metïap u briew, ba kumta kim lah ban ïarakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha kata ka sngi: te ki la ïawan ha khmat u Moses, bad ha khmat u Aaron, ha kata ka sngi:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kita ki briew te, ki la ong ha u, “Ïa ngi, la pynsang da ka metïap u briew: balei ba pynpep ïa ngi, ban ai ka jingainguh ha U Trai ha ka por kaba biang hapdeng ki khun Israel?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ha ki, “To da ïeng hangne; te ngan sngap ïa U Trai un hukum kumno shaphang jong phi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, da kaba ong, ‘Lada don mano mano ruh na phi, lane na ki khun ki ksiew jong phi, ba la pynsang ïa ki da ka metïap, lane ba la leit jingleit sha jngai, pynban, un rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha ka bakhatsaw sngi, ha u bnai u ba-ar, ha kaba la janmiet kin ïarakhe ïa ka, lem bad u kpu bakhlem thiat, bad ki jhur kthang kin ïabam ïa ka:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kin ym pynsah noh khyndiat ruh em na u haduh mynstep, kin ym pynkheiñ ruh ïa kawei na ki shyieng jong u: katba kum kita ki rukom baroh jong Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, kumta kin ïarakhe ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, uta u briew uba long bakhuid, bad u bym shym la leit jingleit, pynban, uba pep noh ïa ka ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ïa kata ka mynsiem keiñ yn ot noh napdeng ki briew jong u: namar ba um shym la wallam ïa ka jingainguh ka jong U Trai ha kata ka aïom ba la buh, uta u briew un kit ïa la ka pop.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lada u nongwei u wan shong basa hapdeng jong phi, bad ba u mon ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai: katba kum kata ka rukom Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, bad katba shong kata ka rukom jong ka, kumta un leh: ha u nongwei, bad ha uta ïa uba la kha ha ka ri, phin ïoh tang kawei ka rukom keiñ.’ ”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi ba la pynïeng ïa Ka Tabernakl, uta u lyoh u la tap noh ïa Ka Tabernakl, ïa kata ka ïing ka jong ka jingphla keiñ: te mynmiet, u la long halor kata Ka Tabernakl, syriem kum ka ding, haduh mynstep.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta ka la ju long ha la ka sngi: uta u lyoh u ju tap noh ïa ka, mynsngi, bad kata ka jing-i kum ka ding, mynmiet.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad haba la kyntiew sha jrong ïa uta u lyoh nalor Ka Tabernakl, te hadien kata, ki khun Israel ki la leit mih noh: bad ha kata ka jaka ha kaba u la shong uta u lyoh, hangta ki khun Israel ki la shong dara.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Da ka hukum U Trai, ki khun Israel ki la ju leit mih noh, bad da ka hukum U Trai ruh, ki la ju ïashong dara: katba u la shong uta u lyoh halor Ka Tabernakl, katta ki la ju shong ha ki ïing dara jong ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad haba uta u lyoh u la sah slem bun sngi halor Ka Tabernakl, te ki khun Israel ki la ju sumar ïa ka jingsumar ka jong U Trai, bad kim ju leit mih noh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka la long kumta haba uta u lyoh u la shong tang khyndiat sngi halor Ka Tabernakl; da ka hukum U Trai, ki la ju shong sah ha ki ïing dara jong ki, bad da ka hukum U Trai, ki la ju leit mih noh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ka la long kumta haba uta u lyoh u la shong naduh janmiet haduh mynstep; bad haba la kyntiew noh ïa u lyoh mynstep, te ki ruh ki la leit mih noh; lada la kyntiew ïa u lyoh mynsngi lane mynmiet, ki ruh ki la ju mih noh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Lane la uta u lyoh u la sah noh ar sngi, lane shi bnai, lane shi snem halor Ka Tabernakl, katba u shong sah halor jong ka, ki khun Israel ki la ju shong sah ha ki ïing dara jong ki, kim ju leit mih noh ruh: hynrei, haba u la kyntiew, ki la ju leit mih noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Da ka hukum U Trai, ki la ju shong dara, da ka hukum U Trai ruh, ki la ju leit mih noh: kumta keiñ, ki la sumar ïa ka jingsumar ka jong U Trai, katba kum kata ka hukum U Trai da ka kti u Moses."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To thaw ïa lade ar tylli ki ronsing rupa; na kawei ka dkhot tylli men thaw ïa ki: ba kin long ha me ban khot lang ïa uta u paidlang, bad ïa ka ban pynmih noh ïa kita ki paidlang bashong dara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba ki ïa-put ïa ki, uta u paidlang baroh un wan ïalang ha me ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, haba ki put tang da kawei, te kita ki rangbah, kiba ha khlieh ki hajar Israel, kin ïalum lang ha me.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba phi put ïa ka jingmaham, te kita ki paidbah kiba ïashong dara shaphang mihngi, kin ïaleit mih noh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba phi put ar sien ïa ka jingmaham, te kita ki paidbah kiba ïashong dara shaphang shathie, kin ïaleit mih noh: ïa ka ban leit mih noh, kin ïa-put ïa ka jingmaham.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ïa ka ban lum lang ïa u paidlang, phin put ïa ki ronsing; hynrei, wat put ïa ka jingmaham.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Aaron, ki lyngdoh keiñ, kin put da kita ki ronsing: te kin long ka rukom basah ha phi junom ki pateng la pateng jong phi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad lada phi leit ïaleh thma ha la ka ri pyrshah ïa u nongshun uba banbeiñ ïa phi, te phin put ïa ka jingmaham da kita ki ronsing; te ïa phi yn kynmaw ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong phi, bad yn pynim ruh ïa phi na ki nongshun jong phi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha kata ka sngi ka jinglehkmen jong phi ruh, bad ha ki sngi Ki Jingkhawai Niam bakyntang jong phi, bad ha ki jingsdang ki bnai jong phi, phin put da kita ki ronsing halor ki jingainguh thang jong phi, bad halor ki jingkñia bapynïasuk jong phi; ba kin ïoh long ka jingpynkynmaw ha phi ha khmat U Blei jong phi: Nga long U Trai U Blei jong phi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ka la jia ha ka ba-arphew sngi, ha u bnai u ba-ar, ha ka snem ka ba-ar, ba uta u lyoh u la kyntiew nalor Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leit mih noh na ka ri khlaw Sinai; bad uta u lyoh u la sah ha ka ri khlaw Paran.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, ki la leit mih noh nyngkong da ka hukum U Trai da ka kti u Moses.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha shuwa eh te, ka la leit mih noh ka lama u paidbah ki khun u Judah katba shong ki paidïapom jong ki; te halor u paidbah jong u, u la long u Nahshon u khun u Amminadab.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Issakhar, u la long u Nethaniil u khun u Suar.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Sabulon, u la long u Eliab u khun u Helon.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ïa kata Ka Tabernakl la lied noh; bad ki khun shynrang u Gershon, bad ki khun shynrang u Merari, ki la leit mih noh, ki da ïabah ïa Ka Tabernakl.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka lama u paidbah jong u Reuben, ka la leit mih noh katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki: te halor u paidbah jong u, u la long u Elisur u khun u Shedeur.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Simeon, u la long u Shelumiel u khun u Surishaddai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Gad, u la long u Eliasaph u khun u Deuel.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te kita ki Kohath ki la leit mih noh, ki da ïabah ïa ka jaka kyntang: bad kita kiwei ki la lah pynïeng ïa Ka Tabernakl hamar ka por ba ki la poi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ka lama u paidbah ki khun u Ephraim, ka la leit mih noh katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki: te halor u paidbah jong u, u la long u Elishama u khun u Ammihud.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Manasseh, u la long u Gamaliel u khun u Pedahsur.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Benjamin, u la long u Abidan u khun u Gideoni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka lama u paidbah ki khun u Dan, uba long khatduh eh na kita ki paidbah baroh, ka la leit mih noh katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki: te halor u paidbah jong u, u la long u Ahieser u khun u Ammishaddai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Asher, u la long u Pagiel u khun u Okran.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad halor u paidbah ka jaid ki khun u Naphtali, u la long u Ahira u khun u Enan.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta keiñ, ka la long ka rukom ki jingïaid jong ki khun Israel, katba kum ki paidïapom jong ki, haba ki la ïaleit mih noh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Moses u la kren ha u Hobab, u khun u Reuel u nong Midian, uba u kthaw kurim jong u Moses, “Ngi ïaleit ha kata ka jaka ba U Trai u la kren shaphang jong ka, ‘Ha phi ngan ai ïa ka’: to wan ma me lem bad ngi, ngi ruh ngin leh bha ïa me; naba U Trai u la kren ïa ka babha shaphang ki Israel.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U te u la ong ha u, “Ngan ym leit; hynrei, ngan leit ha la ka jong ka ri, bad ha la ki kur.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u la ïathuh, “To wat iehnoh ïa ngi, nga kyrpad ïa me; namar ma me, me tip hangno ngi lah ban ïashong dara ha ka ri khlaw, bad men long kum ki khmat ha ngi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad kan long, lada men leit lem bad ngi, ho-oid keiñ kan long ruh, ba ïa kaei kaei ka babha ba U Trai un leh ïa ngi, ïa kata kajuh hi ngi ruh ngin leh ïa me.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki la leit mih noh na uta u lum jong U Trai, lai sngi lynti; bad ka synduk ka jutang ka jong U Trai, ka la leit ha shuwa jong ki ha kita ki lai sngi lynti, ban wad ïa ka jaka shongthait ïa ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad uta u lyoh jong U Trai u la long halor jong ki mynsngi, haba ki la ju leit mih noh na ka jaka shong dara.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad haba kata ka synduk ka la ju mih noh ruh, u Moses u la ju ong, “To ïeng, Ko Trai, bad to ai ban pynsaphred ïa ki nongshun jong me; to ai ruh ba kita kiba shun ïa me kin ïaphet ïap noh ha khmat jong me.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba ka la ju shongthait, u la ju ong, “To phai pat, A Trai, ha ki phew hajar ki Israel.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kita ki briew, ki la long kum kiba ïakren khñium ba pynsngewsih ha ki shkor ki jong U Trai: te U Trai u la ïohsngew ïa kata, bad ka jingbitar jong u ka la meh lep; te ka ding ka jong U Trai, ka la wiang hapdeng jong ki, bad ka la thang duh ïa ka rmiang ka jaka shong dara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kita ki briew te, ki la kyang jam ha u Moses; bad haba u Moses u la duwai ha U Trai, ïa ka ding la pynlip noh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Taberah”: naba kata ka ding jong U Trai ka la ing hapdeng jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u paidbah baïakhleh uba don hapdeng jong ki, u la kwah kangar eh ïa ka doh: ki khun Israel ruh ki la ïaphai pat, bad ki la ïam pat, bad ki la ïapan, “Uei ban ai doh ïa ngi ban bam?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngi ïakynmaw ïa ki dohkha ba ngi la ju bam ei ha ka ri Ijipt, ïa ki sohkhia, bad ïa ki sohkhia pdang, bad ïa ki jhur lik, bad ïa ki piat, bad ïa ki rynsun:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hynrei mynta, ki mynsiem jong ngi ki tyrkhong noh; ba ym don ei ei ruh em, tang kane ka manna ha khmat jong ngi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kata ka manna, ka la long syriem kum ki symbai musla koriander, bad ka rong jong ka kum ka rong Bdellium.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kita ki briew ruh, ki la ju leit kylleng kylleng, bad ki la ju ïalum ïa ka, bad ki la ju tylliat ïa ka ha ki mawtylliat, lane ki la ju dung ïa ka ha ki thlong, bad ki la ju shet ha ki pliang, ïa ka ban thaw kpu da ka: te haba mad ïa ka, ka la long kumba mad ïa ka umphniang bathymmai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ka umjer ka la hap halor ka jaka shong dara mynmiet, kata ka manna, ka ju hap halor jong ka ruh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Moses te, u la ïohsngew ïa kita ki briew ba ki da ïaïam ha la i kur i kur baroh, uwei pa uwei u briew ha la ka jingkhang ka ïingjaiñ: bad ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep eh shikatdei; u Moses ruh u la sngewsih.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Moses te u la ong ha U Trai, “Balei ba me la pynjynjar ïa la u shakri? Balei ruh ba ngam shym la shem ka jingisynei ha khmat jong me, ba me la buh ïa ka jingkit jong kine ki briew baroh halor jong nga?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Long ma nga ba la pun ïa kine ki briew baroh? Long ma nga ba la pynkha ïa ki, ba me ong ha nga, ‘To bah kynthup ïa ki ha la ka shadem, kumba u kpa uba ri khun, u kynthup ïa i khunlung iba dang buiñ, sha kata ka ri ïa kaba me la kular da ka jingsmai ha ki kpa jong ki?’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nangno ma nga ngan ïoh doh, ban ai ha kine ki briew baroh? Namar ki ïam ha nga, ki da ong, ‘To ai doh ha ngi ïa ka ban bam.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Marwei ngam lah ban bah ïa kine ki briew baroh, naba ka kham khia eh ïa nga.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te lada me leh bad nga kumne, lada nga la shem ka jingisynei ha khmat jong me, nga kyrpad, to shu pynïap noh ïa nga, ba ngan ym ïohi ïa ka jynjar jong nga.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Moses, “To lum lang ha nga ïa ki hynñiewphew ngut na ki tymmen basan ki Israel, ïa kiba me tip hi ba ki long ki tymmen basan jong u paidlang, bad ki rangbah halor jong ki: to wallam ruh ïa ki ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ba kin ïaïeng hangta lem bad me.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba ngan wan hiar, bad ngan kren ha me hangta: bad ngan shim na kata ka mynsiem kaba don ha me, bad ngan buh ïa ka ha ki: kumta kin ïabah lem bad me, ïa ka jingkit jong kine ki briew, ba men ym bah marwei ïa ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Namar kata, men ong ha u paidbah, ‘To phin pynkhuid ïa lade hamar lashai, te phin ïoh bam doh: namar phi la ïam lynñiar ha ki shkor U Trai, phi da ong, “Uei u ban ai doh ïa ngi ban bam? naba ngi la long suk ha ka ri Ijipt”: namar kata, U Trai un ai doh ïa phi, bad phin ïoh bam ruh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te phin ïabam ym tang shi sngi, lymne ar sngi, lymne san sngi, lymne shiphew sngi, lymne tang arphew sngi ruh;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, baroh ki sngi shi bnai, ha ban da ka mih noh na ki thliew khmut jong phi, bad ba phi sngewjli ïa ka: namar ba phi la ñiewbeiñ ïa U Trai uba don hapdeng jong phi, bad ba phi la ïam lynñiar ha khmat jong u, phi da ong, “Balei ba ngi la wan mih noh na ka ri Ijipt?” ’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Moses te u la ong, “Kine ki briew, ba nga don hapdeng jong ki, ki long hynriewspah hajar ki rangbah; me te me la ong, ‘Ngan ai doh ïa ki, ban bam baroh ki sngi shi bnai.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Yn pynïap noh ne em ïa kita ki kynhun ki langbrot, bad ki masi ha ki, ba kin kdang? Yn ïalum lang ne em ïa ki dohkha ka duriaw baroh ha ki, ïa ka ban pynkdang ïa ki?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “La pynlyngkot ne em ïa ka kti jong U Trai? mynta men ïohi ïa ka ktien jong nga kan jia long ha me ne em.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Moses te u la mih shabar, bad u la ïathuh ïa kita ki ktien ki jong U Trai ha kita ki briew: bad u la lum lang ïa kita ki hynñiewphew ngut ki tymmen basan jong kita briew, u la buh ruh ïa ki baroh sawdong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Trai te u la wan hiar ha uta u lyoh, bad u la kren ha u, bad u la shim na kata ka mynsiem kaba la don ha u, bad u la ai ha kita ki hynñiewphew ngut ki tymmen basan: te haba kata ka mynsiem ka la shong sah halor jong ki, ki la ïathuhlypa, ki la wai noh ruh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ar ngut na kine ki briew, ki la sah ha kaba shong dara, ka kyrteng uwei ka la long “u Eldad”, bad ka kyrteng uta uwei pat, “u Medad”: te kata ka mynsiem ka la shong sah halor jong ki: namar ki la long na kita ïa kiba la thoh, hynrei, kim shym la leit mih noh sha Ka Tabernakl: pleng ki la ïathuhlypa ha kata ka jaka shong dara.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te uwei u samla u la phet, u la ïathuh ruh ha u Moses, bad u la ong, “U Eldad bad u Medad ki ïathuhlypa keiñ ha kata ka jaka shong dara.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Joshua u khun u Nun, u shakri u Moses, uwei na ki samla jong u, u la ïathuh u la ong ruh, “Ko Moses kynrad jong nga, to khang ïa ki.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Moses te u la ong ha u, “Me sngewpihuiñ na ka bynta jong nga? A ban da ki briew baroh ki jong U Trai kin long ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ba U Trai un buh ïa U Mynsiem jong u halor jong ki!”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Moses u la leit noh sha kata ka jaka shong dara, ma u, bad kita ki tymmen basan ki Israel.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ka lyer na U Trai, ka la mih noh, bad ka la wallam ïa ki 'iar khiar na ka duriaw, ka la pynhap ruh ïa ki, hajan kata ka jaka shong dara, kumba shi sngi lynti sha kawei ka liang, bad shi sngi lynti sha kawei pat ka liang, baroh sawdong kata ka jaka shong dara, te ki la dap kumba ar pruh nalor ka khyndew.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Uta u paidbah te, u la mih noh baroh shi sngi ha kata ka sngi, bad baroh kata ka miet, bad baroh shi sngi lashai ruh, bad ki la ïalum ïa kita ki 'iar khiar: te uta uba la lum kham khyndiat eh ruh, u la lum shiphew homer: bad ki la thad ïa ki ïa lade hi baroh sawdong kata ka jaka shong dara.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te katba kata ka doh ka shu dang don hapdeng ki bniat jong ki, bad haba ym pat shym la ktha ïa ka, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep pyrshah ïa kita ki briew, bad U Trai u la shoh ïa kita ki briew da ka jingïapthem kaba jur eh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Kibroth-hattaabah”: naba la tep hangta ïa kita ki briew kiba la kwah kangar ïa ka doh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na Kibroth-hattaabah, ki briew ki la leit mih noh haduh Haseroth; bad ki la shong ha Haseroth."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka Miriam, bad u Aaron ruh, ki la ïakren khñium pyrshah ïa u Moses, namar kata ka kynthei kaba na ka ri Ethiopia, ïa kaba u la shongkurim: naba u la shongkurim bad ka nong Ethiopia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki la ong, “Shisha u la kren U Trai tang da u Moses? Um shym la kren da ngi ruh de?” Te U Trai u la ïohsngew ïa kata.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, uta u briew, u Moses, u la long uba jemnud tam na ki briew baroh kiba ha khmat ka pyrthei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Shisyndon te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, bad ha ka Miriam de, “To ale mih noh phi baroh lai ngut ha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng:” te ki la ïamih noh baroh lai ngut.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Trai ruh u la wan hiar ha uta u rishot lyoh, u la ïeng ruh ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl, bad u la khot ïa u Aaron, bad ïa ka Miriam: te ki la mih noh baroh ar ngut.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U te u la ong, “To sngap mynta ïa ki ktien jong nga: Lada u nongïathuhlypa jong U Trai u don hapdeng jong phi, ngan pynpaw ïa lade ha u ha ka jingithuhpaw, ngan kren ruh ha u ha ka jingphohsniew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, u Moses, u shakri jong nga um long kumta; u long uba ïaineh keiñ ha ka ïing jong nga baroh:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha u ngan kren markhmat, da kaba paw shynna ym ha ka pharshi; bad ha ka dur un ïoh khmih ïa U Trai: namar kata, balei phim shym la sheptieng ïa ka ban kren pyrshah ïa u shakri jong nga, ïa u Moses keiñ?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka jingbitar jong U Trai ka la meh lep pyrshah ïa ki; bad u la leit noh soit.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Uta u lyoh ruh u la kynriah noh na Ka Tabernakl; ha khmih ruh, ka Miriam ka la pang 'ñiangthohlieh kum ka ïor: bad u Aaron u la khmih ïa ka Miriam, bad ha khmih, ka la pang 'ñiangthohlieh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Aaron te u la ong ha u Moses, “A ko kynrad jong nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, to wat pynkit halor jong ngi ïa kane ka pop, ha kaba ngi la leh bieit, bad ha kaba ngi la leh palat ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To wat ai kan long kum i khun baïap, iba haba i dang shu mih noh na ka kpoh la ka kmie, ïa ka doh jong i la bam duh lypa marshiteng.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Moses te u la kyang kyrpad ha U Trai, u da ong, “A Blei, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pynkhiah ïa ka mynta.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Lada u kpa jong ka, u la shu bynthiew ha ka khmat jong ka, kan ym da lehrain hynñiew sngi? to khang noh te ïa ka, shabar ka jaka shong dara, hynñiew sngi, hadien kata te, to pdiang ïa ka pat.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> La khang noh te ïa ka Miriam, shabar ka jaka shong dara, hynñiew sngi: te uta u paidbah, um shym la leit mih noh, tad ynda ka Miriam ka la wan pat hapoh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te hadien kata, uta u paidbah u la mih noh na Haseroth, bad ki la ïashong dara ruh ha ka ri khlaw Paran."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To men phah ki briew, ba kin ïakhmih syntiat ïa ka ri Kanaan, ïa kaba ngan sa ai ha ki khun Israel: ïa uwei u briew na kawei kawei ka jaid ki kpa jong ki men phah; ïa uwei uwei ruh uba rangbah hapdeng jong ki.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Moses te u la phah noh ïa ki na kata ka ri khlaw Paran da ka hukum U Trai: kita ki briew baroh, ki la long ki rangbah ki khun Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kine te ki la long ki kyrteng jong ki: na ka jaid Reuben — u Shammua u khun u Sakkur.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ka jaid Simeon — u Shaphat u khun u Hori.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ka jaid Judah — u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ka jaid Issakhar — u Igal u khun u Joseph.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ka jaid Ephraim — u Oshea u khun u Nun.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ka jaid Benjamin — u Palti u khun u Raphu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ka jaid Sabulon — u Gaddiel u khun u Sodi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ka jaid Joseph, kata ka long, na ka jaid Manasseh — u Gaddi u khun u Susi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ka jaid Dan — u Ammiel u khun u Gemalli.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ka jaid Asher — u Sethur u khun u Mikhael.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ka jaid Naphtali — u Nahbi u khun u Bophsi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ka jaid Gad — u Geuel u khun u Makhi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kine ki long ki kyrteng jong kita ki briew, ïa kiba u la phah noh u Moses ïa ka ban khmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri. Te u Moses u la khot kyrteng ïa u Hoshea, u khun u Nun “u Joshua.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Moses u la phah noh ïa ki, ïa ka ban khmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri Kanaan, u la ong ruh ha ki, “To khie leit kumne shaphang shathie, to kiew sha kata ka ri lum:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> to khmih ruh ïa kata ka ri, kaba kumno; bad ïa kita ki briew kiba ïashong sah ha ka, la ki long kiba khlaiñ, ne kiba tlot bor, kiba khyndiat, ne kiba bun;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ïa ka khyndew ruh ha kaba ki ïashong sah, la ka babha, ne ka basniew; ha kiba kumno ki shnong ki ïashong ruh, la ha ki ïingjaiñ, ne ha ki kut baskhem;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ïa ka khyndew ruh, la kaba don sboh, ne kaba lyngki, la ki don ki dieng ha ka ne em. To long phi ki bashlur, to wallam ruh na ki soh jong kata ka ri.” Te kata ka aïom ka la long ka aïom soh nyngkong ki dieng soh Waiñ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta te ki la ïaleit kiew, bad ki la ïakhmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri, naduh ka ri khlaw Sin haduh Rehob, ha ka lynti kaba leit sha Hamath.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki la ïaleit kiew na shathie, bad ki la ïawan poi ha Hebron; hangta ki la don u Ahiman, u Sheshai, bad u Thalmai, ki khun u Anak. (Te haba ym pat tei ïa ka Soan ha Ijipt, ïa ka Hebron la lah tei la hynñiew snem.)",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la poi haduh ka them Eshkol, nangta ruh ki la pom noh ïa kawei ka tnat ha kaba don shi rynjup u soh Waiñ, bad ki la ïabah ïa ka halor u dieng hapdeng ar ngut; ki la wallam ruh ïa ki soh Pong, bad ïa ki soh Dumbur de.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la khot ïa kata ka jaka “ka them Eshkol” namar kata ka shi rynjup ki soh Waiñ, ïa kaba la pom noh ki khun Israel nangta.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ynda la sawphew sngi, ki la ïawan phai pat na kaba khmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki la ïaleit wan ruh, bad ki la ïapoi ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, bad ha uta u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel, ha Kadesh, kaba ha ka ri khlaw Paran; ki la wallam ktien ruh ha ki, bad ha uta u paidlang baroh, bad ki la pyni ha ki, ïa ki soh jong kata ka ri.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u, ki la ong ruh, “Ngi la ïaleit poi ha kata ka ri ha kaba me la phah ïa ngi, shisha ruh ka long kaba shlei da ka dud, bad ka ngap; kine ruh ki soh jong ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, kita ki briew kiba shong ha kata ka ri, ki long kiba khlaiñ, ki shnong ruh ïa kiba la ker kynroh, bad ki bakhraw eh; hangta ruh, ngi la ïohi ïa ki khun u Anak.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kita ki Amalek, ki ïashong sah ha ka ri shathie: te ha ki ri lum, ki ïashong sah ki Heth, bad ki Jebus, bad ki Amor: ki Kanaan ruh ki ïashong hajan kata ka duriaw, bad harud ka Jordan.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Kaleb te, u la pynsngap jar ïa kita ki briew ha khmat u Moses, u la ong ruh, “To ïa, ngin ïaleit kiew shisyndon, ngin jop ruh ïa ka; namar ngi lah biang biang ban jop noh ïa ka.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, kita kiwei ki briew kiba la leit kiew lem bad u, ki la ong, “Ngim don bor ban ïaleit kiew ïaleh pyrshah ïa kita ki briew; namar ki long kiba kham khlaiñ ïa ngi keiñ.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki la wallam ïa ka jingbna basniew ha ki khun Israel, shaphang kata ka ri ïa kaba ki la khmih syntiat, ki da ong, “Kata ka ri, ïa kaba ngi la ïaid lyngba ïa ka ban khmih syntiat ïa ka, ka long ka ri kaba bam duh ïa la ki trai-shnong; ki briew baroh ruh ïa kiba ngi la ïohi ha ka, ki long kiba jrong eh ka rynïeng.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hangta ruh, ngi la ïohi ïa kita ki radbah, ki khun shynrang u Anak keiñ, kiba la mih na kita ki radbah: bad ha ka jingñiew jong ngi, ngi la long kum ki puit, kumta ruh ngi la long, ha ka jingñiew jong ki de.”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u paidlang baroh u la pyrta jam, bad u la kyang lynñiar; bad kita ki briew ki la ïam ha kata ka miet.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki khun Israel baroh, ki la ïakren khñium pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad pyrshah ïa u Aaron: bad uta u paidlang baroh, u la ong ha ki, “A suk ba ngin da la lah ïap noh ha kata ka ri Ijipt!” lane “A suk ba ngin da la lah ïap noh ha kane ka ri khlaw!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te balei ba U Trai u la wallam ïa ngi sha kane ka ri, ba ngin hap da ka waitlam? ki tnga, bad ki khun jong ngi, kin long ka jinglute: hato ym kham bha, ba ngin ïaphai pat sha ka ri Ijipt?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “To ïa, ngin ïathung ïa u nongïalam, bad ngin ïaleit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, u Moses bad u Aaron, ki la dem ngon la ki khmat ha khmat ka jingïaseng baroh u paidlang ki khun Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Joshua u khun u Nun ruh, bad u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh de, kiba na kita kiba la ïakhmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri, ki la kad ïa la ki jaiñ:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ki la kren ruh ha uta u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel, ki da ong, “Kata ka ri, ba ngi la ïaid lyngba ban khmih syntiat ïa ka, ka long ka ri ka babha eh shikatdei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lada U Trai u sngewbha ïa ngi, te un ïalam ïa ngi sha kata ka ri, un ai ruh ïa ka ha ngi; ka ri keiñ kaba shlei da ka dud, bad ka ngap.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tangba phin ym ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai, lymne wat sheptieng phi ïa ki briew jong kata ka ri; namar ki long kpu ïa ngi: ka jingïada ïa ki, ka la kynriah noh na ki, hynrei, U Trai u don lem bad ngi: to wat sheptieng te ïa ki.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, uta u paidbah baroh, u la ong ban lynthem ïa ki da ki maw. Te ka burom U Trai ka la paw ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ha khmat ki khun Israel baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Haduh katno kine ki briew kin ïa-pynbitar ïa nga? tad lano ruh kin long ki bymngeit ha nga, namar kita ki dak phylla baroh ba nga la leh hapdeng jong ki?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngan shoh ïa ki da kaba ïapthem, bad ngan pynsaphred ruh ïa ki, te ïa me, ngan pynlong ka jaid bynriew kaba kham khraw, bad kaba kham khlaiñ ruh ïa ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha U Trai, “Kumta ki Ijipt kin ïohsngew; namar me la wallam ïa kine ki briew da ka borbah jong me napdeng jong ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kin ïathuh ruh ha ki trai-shnong kane ka ri: namar ki la ïohsngew ba me U Trai, me long hapdeng kine ki briew; bad ba me U Trai, me paw markhmat markhmat, bad ba u lyoh jong me, u sah halor jong ki, bad ba me leit ha shuwa jong ki ha u rishot lyoh mynsngi, bad ha u rishot ding mynmiet.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te lada men pynïap noh ïa kine ki briew baroh kum ïa uwei u briew keiñ, te kumta, kita ki jaid bynriew kiba la bna ïa ka nam jong me, kin ïakren, kin da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ‘Namar ba U Trai um donbor ban wallam ïa kine ki briew sha kata ka ri ïa kaba u la smai ha ki, namar kata, u la pynïap noh ïa ki ha kata ka ri khlaw.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mynta te, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ai ba yn pynkhraw ïa ka bor U Trai jong nga, kat kumba me la kren, da kaba ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ‘U Trai u long uba shah slem, bad uba khraw ka jingisynei, uba map noh ïa ka pop, bad ïa ka jingpalat, khlem da pynksan da lei lei ruh ïa uba rem; uba pynwan hap ïa ka pop jong ki kpa halor ki khun ki ksiew, haduh ka balai, bad ka basaw pateng bynriew.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te nga kyrpad ïa me, to map ïa ka pop jong kine ki briew, katba kum ka jingisynei ka bakhraw jong me, bad kumba me la map ïa kine ki briew, naduh ka ri Ijipt jin haduh mynta.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Trai ruh u la ong, “Nga la map keiñ katba kum ka ktien jong me:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hynrei da shisha, katba nga im, ïa ka pyrthei baroh yn pyndap da ka burom jong U Trai:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kita ki briew baroh kiba la ïohi ïa ka burom jong nga, bad ïa ki dak phylla jong nga ïa kiba nga la leh ha ka ri Ijipt, bad ha kata ka ri khlaw, bad kiba la pynshoi ïa nga kine shiphew sien, bad kim shym la shahshkor ruh ïa ka ktien jong nga;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> da shisha, kin ym ïohi ïa kata ka ri ïa kaba nga la smai ha ki kpa jong ki, kita baroh keiñ kiba la pynbitar ïa nga, kin ym ïohi ïa ka:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, u shakri jong nga u Kaleb, naba u don ka jingmut ka bapher, bad ba u la bud ïa nga biang biang, ïa u keiñ, ngan ïalam sha kata ka ri sha kaba u la leit; bad u symbai jong u kin ïoh ïa ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei mynta, ki Amalek, bad ki Kanaan, ki ïashong sah ha kata ka ri them: lashai te to phai noh, to leit ruh sha kata ka ri khlaw da kata ka lynti ka Duriaw Basaw.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, u da ong,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Tad lano ngan shah ïa une u paidlang basniew, uba kren khñium ïa nga? Nga la ïohsngew ïa ki jingkren khñium jong ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ki la ïakren khñium ïa nga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To ong ha ki, ‘Katba nga im’, u ong U Trai, ‘kat kumba phi la kren ha ki shkor jong nga, kumta ruh ngan leh ïa phi:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha kane ka ri khlaw, ki metïap jong phi, kin kyllon ïap; bad baroh ïa kiba la ñiew katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong phi baroh, naduh uba arphew snem ka rta bad tam, kiba la kren khñium ïa nga,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> da shisha keiñ, phin ym ïoh poi sha kata ka ri, ïa kaba nga la smai da kyntiew ïa la ka kti, ïa ka ban pynshong duh ïa phi ha ka, hynrei, tang u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki khun khynnah jong phi, ïa kiba phi la ong ba kin long ka jinglute, ïa kita keiñ, ngan wallam sha kata ka ri, ma ki ruh, kin ïoh ithuh ïa kata ka ri ïa kaba phi la ïañiewbeiñ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, ki metïap jong phi, kin kyllon ïap ha kane ka ri khlaw.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki khun jong phi ruh, kin ïaidwir kylleng la kylleng ha kane ka ri khlaw jin sawphew snem, bad kin ïakit shitom shi jot ïa ki jingïaleh nuti jong phi ha ban da la duh noh khoit ki metïap jong phi ha kane ka ri khlaw.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong kita ki sngi ba phi la ïakhmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri, sawphew sngi keiñ, ïa kawei ka sngi namar kawei ka snem, phin ïakit shitom shi jot ïa ki pop jong phi jin sawphew snem, te phin ïoh tip keiñ, ïa ka jingkylla ïa ka jingthmu jong nga.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ma nga U Trai nga la kren, da shisha ngan leh ruh ïa kata ha une u paidlang basniew baroh, uba la ïalum lang ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga: ha kane ka ri khlaw yn pynduh noh khoit ïa ki, hangne ruh kin ïap noh.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te kita ki briew, ïa kiba u la phah u Moses ïa ka ban khmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri, kiba la wan phai pat, bad kiba la pynlong ïa uta u paidlang baroh ïa ka ban kren khñium ïa u, da kaba ki da ai ktien budnam ïa kata ka ri,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> kita ki briew keiñ, kiba la ai ktien budnam ïa kata ka ri, ki la ïap noh da kaba ïapkhlam ha khmat U Trai.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, na kita ki briew kiba leit ïa ka ban khmih syntiat ïa kata ka ri, u Joshua u khun u Nun, bad u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh, ki la ïoh im.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U Moses ruh u la ïathuh ïa kine ki ktien ha ki khun Israel baroh: kita ki briew te, ki la ïam sngewsih jam eh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ki la khie la dang step ïa ka ban sa leit kiew sha kliar uta u lum, ki da ong, “Ha khmih ïa ngi, ngin ïaleit kiew ruh sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba U Trai u la kular: namar ngi la leh pop.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, u Moses u la ong, “Hato balei phi ïaryngkang kumne ïa ka hukum ka jong U Trai? Hynrei, kane kan ym myntoi shuh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Wat leit kiew phi, namar U Trai um don hapdeng jong phi; ïoh ba yn pom noh ïa phi ha khmat ki nongshun jong phi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Namar kita ki Amalek, bad kita ki Kanaan, ki don ha khmat jong phi, bad phin hap da ka waitlam: naba phi la phai dien noh na U Trai, namar kata, U Trai un ym long lem keiñ bad phi.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Pynban, ki la shlan ban leit kiew sha kliar uta u lum: hynrei, kata ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, bad u Moses, kim shym la mih noh napdeng kata ka jaka shong dara.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te kita ki Amalek, bad kita ki Kanaan, kiba la ïashong sah ha uta u lum, ki la ïawan hiar, ki la shoh noh ruh ïa ki, bad ki la pynjot noh thiaw ïa ki, jin haduh Hormah."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Haba phi la poi sha kata ka ri shongneh jong phi, ïa kaba nga ai ha phi,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad haba phi ai ka jingainguh da ka ding ha U Trai, ka jingainguh thang, lane ka jingkñia ba pyndep ïa ka jingkular skhem, lane ka jingainguh sngewbha, lane ha ki Jingkhawai Niam bakyntang jong phi, ban pynlong ïa ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai, na ki masi dab, lane na ki langbrot:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta te, uta u ba ai ka jingainguh jong u ha U Trai, un wallam ka jingainguh bam da ka bynta bashiphew na u 'purew ïa uba la ïakhleh bad shi pawa hin ka umphniang:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Lem bad ka jingainguh thang ruh lane ka jingkñia, men khreh shi pawa hin ka Waiñ, namar uwei uwei u khun langbrot, ban long ka jingainguh dih.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te namar uwei uwei u langbrot, men ainguh ar bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew ba la khleh bad kaba lai bynta hin ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad namar ka jingainguh dih, men ai kaba lai bynta hin ka Waiñ, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Haba me khreh ïa u masi lyngraw ruh ban long ka jingainguh thang, lane ka jingkñia ba pyndep ïa ka jingkular skhem, lane ban long ka jingkñia bapynïasuk ha U Trai:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> te un wallam lem bad uta u masi lyngraw, lai bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew ba la khleh bad shiteng hin ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad namar ka jingainguh dih, men wallam shiteng hin ka Waiñ, ka ban long ka jingainguh kaba da ka ding, ïa ka ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Kumta, ka dei ban leh namar uwei uwei u masi lyngraw, lane namar uwei uwei u langbrot, lane namar uwei uwei u khun langbrot, ne u khun blang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong kita ïa kiba phin khreh, kumta phin leh ha uwei pa uwei katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki trai-shnong baroh kin leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh kumta, haba ki ai ka jingainguh kaba da ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad lada u nongwei u shong basa lem bad phi, ne lada uno uno ruh uba hapdeng jong phi ha ki jingkha pateng jong phi, bad un ai ka jingainguh kaba da ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai; kumba leh ma phi, kumta un leh ma u ruh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tang kawei ka rukom kan long ha phi, kiba dei ha uta u paidlang, bad ha uta u nongwei ruh uba shong basa lem bad phi, ka rukom keiñ kaba ha la ka rta ha ki jingkha pateng jong phi: kumba long ma phi, kumta un long uta u nongwei ha khmat U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kawei ka hukum, bad kawei ka rukom ruh kan long ha phi, bad ha u nongwei uba shong basa lem bad phi.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Haba phi la poi ha kata ka ri ha kaba ngan sa ïalam ïa phi,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te ynda phi la ïoh bam na u kpu jong kata ka ri, te phin kyntiew ïa ka jingainguh bakyntiew ha U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na u kpu im banyngkong jong phi, phin ainguh da uwei u kpu, ban long ka jingainguh bakyntiew; kumjuh kum ka jingainguh bakyntiew na ka kyntem, kumta phin kyntiew ïa ka ruh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na uta u kpu im banyngkong jong phi, phin ainguh ïa ka jingainguh bakyntiew ha U Trai ha ki pateng la pateng jong phi.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Te haba phi la leh palat, bad ba phim leh ïa kine ki hukum baroh, ïa kiba u la kren U Trai ha u Moses,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ïa kata baroh keiñ ba la hukum U Trai ïa phi da ka kti u Moses, naduh kata ka sngi ha kaba u la hukum U Trai, bad naduh mynta ha ki jingkha pateng jong phi;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> kan long te, lada yn leh ei ei ruh ha ka jingbymtip, khlem da tip u paidbah, ba uta u paidbah baroh un ainguh da uwei u masi lyngraw, ban long ka jingainguh thang, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai, lem bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka, katba kum ka rukom, bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u lyngdoh un pynlong ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta uta u paidbah baroh ki khun Israel, te yn map noh ïa ki; namar ka long ka jingbymtip, bad ki la wallam ruh ïa la ka jingainguh, ka jingkñia da ka ding ha U Trai, bad ïa ka jingkñia sait pop jong ki ha khmat U Trai, namar ka jingbymtip jong ki:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te yn map ïa u paidbah baroh ki khun Israel, bad ïa u nongwei uba shong basa hapdeng jong ki; naba ka la jia ha kita ki briew baroh da ka jingbymtip.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Te lada uno uno u briew un leh pop da ka bymtip; te un wallam kawei ka blang kaba shi snem, ban long ka jingkñia namar ka pop.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u lyngdoh un pynlong ka kuna namar uta u briew uba la leh pop da ka bymtip, haba u la leh pop da ka bymtip, ha khmat U Trai, u da pynlong ka kuna namar jong u; te yn map ïa u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ïa uta uba la kha na ki khun Israel, bad ïa u nongwei uba shong basa hapdeng jong ki, phin ïoh tang kawei ka rukom ïa uta uba la leh pop da ka bymtip.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, uta u briew uba leh pop da kaba leh meng, la u trai-shnong, lane u nongwei, uta keiñ u lehbeiñ ïa U Trai; ïa uta u briew yn ot noh napdeng ki briew jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar ba u la ñiewbeiñ ïa ka ktien U Trai, bad ba u la pynkheiñ ïa ka hukum jong u; ïa uta u briew yn ot noh, ka pop jong u kan long halor jong u.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te mynba ki khun Israel ki la don ha kata ka ri khlaw, ki la shem ïa uwei u briew uba lum prew ha ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kita te kiba la shem ïa u, ki la wallam ïa uta uba lum prew ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, bad ha u paidlang baroh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki la set byndi ruh ïa u, naba ym pat shym la pynpaw aïu ka dei ban leh ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Trai te u la ong ïa u Moses, “Ïa uta u briew ka dei shisha ban pynïap noh: u paidlang baroh kin ïalynthem ïa u da ki maw, shabar ka jaka shong dara.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad uta u paidlang baroh ki la leit lam ïa u shabar kata ka jaka shong dara, bad ki la lynthem ïa u da ki maw, bad u la ïap; kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki ba kin thaw ki jingjyrthiaw ha ki rmiang ki jaiñ jong ki, ha ki jingkha pateng phar jong ki, bad ba kin buh ïa ka jingteh babyrïong halor kita ki jingjyrthiaw jong ki rmiang jaiñ:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> te kan long ha phi kum ka jingjyrthiaw, ba, haba phi khmih ïa ka, phin kynmaw ïa ki hukum baroh ki jong U Trai, bad phin leh ruh ïa ki; bad ba phin ym beh katba kum la ka jong ka dohnud, bad la ki jong ki khmat, ïa kiba phi la ju beh brai:",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ba phin ïoh kynmaw, bad phin leh ruh ïa ki hukum jong nga baroh, bad ba phin long khuid ha U Blei jong phi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Nga U Trai U Blei jong phi, uba la wallam ïa phi na ka ri Ijipt ban long U Blei ïa phi: Nga long U Trai U Blei jong phi.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Korah, u khun u Ishar, uba u khun u Kohath, u khun u Lebi, bad u Dathan, bad u Abiram, ki khun shynrang u Eliab, bad u On u khun u Peleth, ki khun shynrang u Reuben, ki la ïashet buit:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ryngkat bad arspah sanphew ngut kiwei pat ki khun Israel, ki rangbah jong u paidlang, kiba donnam ha ka dorbar, ki briew kiba donburom, ki la ïeng ha khmat u Moses:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki la ïalum lang pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad pyrshah ïa u Aaron, ki la ong ruh ha ki, “Phi shimti ha lade kham bun, haba phi ïohi ba u paidlang baroh u long u bakhuid uwei pa uwei, bad ba U Trai ruh u don hapdeng jong ki: balei te phi pynkyntiew ïa lade halor u paidlang jong U Trai?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u Moses u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la hap dem la ka khmat:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la kren ruh ha u Korah, bad ha u paidlang jong u, u da ong, “Lashai un pyni U Trai ïa uei uba dei u jong u, bad ïa uei u bakhuid, bad ïa uei de uba dei ban wan hajan jong u; naba ïa uta uba u la jied, un pynwan hajan jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Phin leh kumne; ‘To shim ha phi ïa ki khiew thang iwbih, u Korah keiñ, bad u paidlang jong u baroh;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> te phin buh ding hapoh jong ki, to buh ruh ïa ka jingiwbih thang hapoh jong ki lashai ha khmat U Trai:’ te kan long, ba uta u briew ïa uba U Trai un jied, un long u bakhuid: phi shimti kham bun ha lade, phi ki khun shynrang u Lebi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ruh ha u Korah, “To sngap, nga kyrpad ïa phi, ki khun shynrang u Lebi:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> phi ñiew sting, ba U Blei jong u Israel u la pynkyrpang ïa phi na u paidlang ki Israel, ban pynwan hajan ha lade ïa phi; ban trei ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl U Trai, bad ban ïeng ha khmat u paidlang ïa ka ban shakri ïa ki?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba u la pynwan hajan ïa me, bad ïa ki para jong me de, ki khun shynrang u Lebi baroh lem bad me; te phi wad ïa ka jinglong lyngdoh ruh de?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Naba ïa kane khnang, ma me bad u paidlang jong me baroh, phi la ïalum lang pyrshah ïa U Trai: hynrei, u Aaron u long aïu ba phi ïakhñium ïa u?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Moses ruh u la phah khot ïa u Dathan, bad ïa u Abiram, ki khun u Eliab: kiba la ong, “Ngin ym wan kiew satia:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hato me ñiew sting ba me la pynwan ïa ngi na ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud, bad ka ngap, ïa ka ban pynïap ïa ngi ha kane ka ri khlaw, lymda men ïoh pynlong syiem phar ïa lade halor jong ngi?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Pynban, mem shym la pynpoi ïa ngi satia ha kata ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud, bad ka ngap, bad mem shym la ai bynta ruh ha ngi, lymne da ki lyngkha, lymne da ki brisoh Waiñ: te men khlaw noh ïa ki khmat jong kine ki briew? Ngin ym wan kiew keiñ.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Moses te u la bitar lep shikatdei, bad u la ong ha U Trai, “To wat khmih ha ka jingainguh jong ki: ngam shym la shim ïa uwei u kadda na ki, bad ngam shym la pynsniew ruh ïa uwei na ki.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ha u Korah, “Lashai, to long ma me, bad u paidlang jong me baroh, ha khmat U Trai, ma me, bad ma ki ruh, bad u Aaron:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad uwei uwei baroh, un shim ïa la ka pliang, bad un buh ruh ïa ka jingiwbih thang ha ki; bad un wallam ha khmat U Trai uwei uwei baroh ïa la ka pliang, arspah sanphew ki pliang; ma me ruh, bad u Aaron, uwei uwei ïa la ka pliang keiñ.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uwei uwei baroh, u la shim ïa la ka pliang, bad ki la thep ding hapoh jong ki, bad ki la buh ruh ïa ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ki, bad ki la ïeng ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, lem bad u Moses, bad u Aaron.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Korah u la lum lang ïa u paidlang baroh, pyrshah ïa ki ha kata ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: te ka burom U Trai ka la paw ha uta u paidlang baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron, U da ong,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “To pynkyrpang ïa lade napdeng une u paidlang, ba ngan pynjot noh thiaw ïa ki shisyndon.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la hap dem la ki khmat, bad ki la ong, “A Blei, uba U Blei jong ki mynsiem ki doh baroh, tang uwei u briew uba la leh pop, te men bitar lep ïa u paidlang baroh?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “To kren ha uta u paidlang, da kaba ong, ‘To kynriah noh na ki ïingjaiñ jong u Korah, u Dathan, bad u Abiram.’ ”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Moses u la ïeng, u la leit ruh ha u Dathan, bad ha u Abiram; bad ki tymmen ki san ki Israel ruh ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u la kren ha uta u paidlang, u da ong, “To kynriah noh, nga ong, na ki ïingjaiñ jong kine ki briew bymman, to wat ktah ruh ei ei ruh em ka jong ki, ïoh yn pynjot noh ïa phi ha ki pop jong ki baroh.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumta te, ki la kynriah noh na kita ki ïingjaiñ u Korah, u Dathan, bad u Abiram, baroh sawdong; te u Dathan, bad u Abiram, lem bad ki tnga jong ki, bad ki khun shynrang jong ki, bad ki khynnah jong ki, ki la ïamih shabar, bad ki la ïeng ha phyllaw ki ïingjaiñ jong ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Moses te u la ong, “Da kane phin ïoh tip ba u la phah U Trai ïa nga ïa ka ban leh ïa kine ki kam baroh; bad ba ngam shym la leh ïa ki, na la ka jong ka jingmut.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Lada kine ki briew kin ïap kumba ki ju ïap ki briew baroh, lane lada kan jia ïa ki kumba ju jia ïa ki briew baroh; te kumta U Trai um shym la phah ïa nga.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, lada U Trai un thaw ïa ka bathymmai, katba ka khyndew kan ang ïa la ka shyntur, bad kan nguid noh tylli ïa ki, bad baroh kat kiba long ki jong ki, ba kumta kin hap im ha dujok; te phin sngewthuh ba kine ki briew ki la pynbitar ïa U Trai.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ka la jia, katba u shu dang wai noh ïa kaba kren ïa kine ki ktien baroh, ba kata ka khyndew kaba hapoh jong ki, ka la kad ar liang:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te kata ka khyndew, ka la ang ïa la ka shyntur, bad ka la nguid noh tylli ïa ki, bad ïa ki ïing jong ki, bad ïa ki briew baroh kiba ïadei lang ha u Korah, bad ïa ki mar jong ki baroh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ma ki, bad baroh kat kiba ïadei lang ki jong ki, ki la leit hiar im ha dujok: bad kata ka khyndew ka la dam halor jong ki, bad ki la ïap duh noh napdeng uta u paidlang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ki Israel baroh kiba la don baroh sawdong ïa ki, ki la ïaphet ïap noh na ka jinglynñiar jong ki: naba ki la ïa-ong, “Ba ïoh nguid noh tylli ka khyndew ïa ngi ruh.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ka la mih noh ka ding na U Trai, bad ka la thang duh ruh ïa kita ki arspah sanphew kiba la ainguh ïa kata ka jingiwbih thang.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “To kren ha u Eleasar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, ba un rah noh ïa kita ki pliang kita kiba la ing; bad men pynsaphred shabar ïa ka ding na ki: naba ki long kiba la kyntang:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> na kita ki pliang jong kine kiba la leh pop ïa la ki mynsiem jong ki hi, to thaw sla ki baïar ïa ki, ban long ka jingtap ïa ka duwan: naba ki la ainguh ïa ki ha khmat U Trai, namar kata, ki long kiba la kyntang: bad kin long ka dak ha ki khun Israel.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Eleasar lyngdoh u la shim ïa kita ki pliang rnong, da kiba ki la ainguh kita ïa kiba la thang; bad ki la shoh pynstang ïa ki, ban long ka jingtap ïa kata ka duwan:",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ïa ka ban long ka jingpynkynmaw ïa ki khun Israel, ba uno uno ruh u nongwei, u bymdei na u symbai u Aaron, un ym wan hajan ban ainguh ïa ka jingiwbih thang ha khmat U Trai, ba ïoh un long kum u Korah, bad u paidlang jong u; kumba U Trai u la ong ha u da ka kti u Moses.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, ha kaba lashai, uta u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel u la kren khñium ïa u Moses, bad ïa u Aaron, ki da ong, “Phi la pynïap noh ïa ki briew ki jong U Trai.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba uta u paidlang u la ïalum lang ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad pyrshah ïa u Aaron, ba ki la khmih sha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: te ha khmih, uta u lyoh u la tap ïa ka, bad ka burom U Trai ka la paw.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Aaron, ki la ïawan ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “To khie leit noh napdeng une u paidlang, ba ngan ïoh pynjot noh ïa ki shisyndon.” Ki te ki la hap dem la ki khmat.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ha u Aaron, “To shim ïa ka pliang, to thep ruh ïa ka ding na ka duwan hapoh jong ka, to buh ruh ïa ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ka, bad to leit kloi kloi hapdeng u paidlang, bad to pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta jong ki: namar ka jingbitar ka la mih noh na U Trai; ka khlam ruh ka la sdang keiñ.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad u Aaron u la shim kumba u la hukum u Moses, bad u la phet hapdeng uta u paidlang; te, ha khmih, ka khlam ka la lah sdang hapdeng kita ki briew: bad u la ai ka jingiwbih thang, bad u la pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta uta u paidlang.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te u la ïeng hapdeng ki baïap bad ki ba-im: bad ïa kata ka khlam la pynsangeh.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te kita kiba la ïap noh na kata ka jingïapthem, ki la long khatsaw hajar bad hynñiewspah, nalor kita kiba la ïap noh ha ka jingïaleh jong u Korah.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Bad u Aaron u la leit phai pat sha u Moses ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: te ïa kata ka khlam la pynsangeh."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to shim ruh na uwei uwei baroh na ki, ïa uwei u diengduh katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, na ki rangbah jong ki baroh, katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, khat-ar tylli ki diengduh: to men thoh ruh ïa ka kyrteng jong uwei uwei baroh u briew ha u diengduh jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ha u diengduh u Lebi, men thoh ïa ka kyrteng u Aaron: namar uwei u diengduh un long na ka bynta u rangbah ka ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad men buh noh ïa ki ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ha khmat ka jingphla, ha kaba ngan ïashem bad phi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kan jia, ba u diengduh jong uta u briew ïa uba ngan jied un phuh, bad ngan pynduh na khmat jong nga ïa ki jingkhñium jong ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ki la ïakren khñium ïa phi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Moses u la kren ha ki khun Israel, te ki rangbah jong ki baroh, ki la ai ha u mar uwei uwei u diengduh, ïa uwei na ka bynta uwei u rangbah, katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, khat-ar tylli ki diengduh: bad u diengduh u Aaron, u la don hapdeng kita ki diengduh jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Moses u la buh noh ïa kita ki diengduh ha khmat U Trai ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, u Moses u la leit hapoh Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla; bad ha khmih, u diengduh u Aaron uba na ka bynta ka ïing u Lebi u la phuh, bad u la mih shylluit, bad u la phuh syntiew, u la sei ruh da ki soh Khyllam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Moses u la pynmih shabar ïa kita ki diengduh baroh na khmat U Trai ha ki khun Israel baroh: te ki la ïakhmih thuh, bad uwei uwei baroh u la shim ïa la u jong u diengduh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To wallam biang ïa uta u diengduh jong u Aaron ha khmat ka jingphla, ban ri ïa u, ïa ka ban long ka dak pyrshah ïa kine ki khun ba ïaleh pyrshah; khnang ïa ka ban pynduh na khmat jong nga ïa ki jingkhñium jong ki, ba kin ym ïap shuh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Moses u la leh kumta; kumba u la hukum U Trai, kumta u la leh keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la kren ha u Moses, ki da ong, “Ha khmih, ngi ïap; ngi ïap duh, ngi ïap duh baroh keiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Uno uno ruh uba kham wan hajan, uba kham wan hajan Ka Tabernakl U Trai, un ïap noh: yn pynjot noh ïa ngi da kaba ïap?”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Aaron, “Ma me, bad ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ka ïing u kpa jong me, lem bad me, phin ïakit ïa ka pop jong ka jaka kyntang: ma me ruh bad ki khun shynrang jong me, phin ïakit ïa ka pop jong ka jinglong lyngdoh jong phi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ïa la ki para ruh na ka jaid Lebi, ka jaid u kpa jong me, men shim lem bad me, ban pynïasoh ïa ki ha lade, ba kin shakri ïa me: hynrei, ma me bad ki khun shynrang jong me, phin ïashakri ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad kin ïa-ap sumar ïa ka jingsumar jong me, bad ïa ka jingsumar Ka Tabernakl baroh: tang ba, kin ym wan hajan ïa ki pliang ka jaka kyntang bad ïa ka duwan, ba ïoh kin ïap, ma ki, lane ma phi ruh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kin ïasoh bad me, bad kin ïa-ap sumar ïa ka jingsumar Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ha ka kam baroh ka jong Ka Tabernakl; wat ai ruh ba u nongwei un wan hajan jong phi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, phin ïa-ap sumar ma phi ïa ka jingsumar ka jaka kyntang, bad ïa ka jingsumar ka duwan: ba kan ym long shuh ka jingbitar halor ki khun Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ha khmih, nga la shim ma nga ïa ki para jong me, ki Lebi, napdeng ki khun Israel: ha me la ai ïa ki, kum ka jingai ha U Trai, ïa ka ban trei ïa ka kam jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, ma me bad ki khun shynrang jong me, phin ïasumar ïa ka kam lyngdoh jong phi shaphang kiei kiei baroh kiba dei ïa ka duwan, bad hapoh ka jingkah de phin trei; nga la ai ïa ka kam lyngdoh jong phi ha phi kum ka jingai ei: te ïa u nongwei u ban wan hajan yn pynïap noh.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Aaron, “Ha khmih, nga la ai ha me ruh ïa ka jingsumar halor ki jingainguh kyntiew jong nga, na kiei kiei baroh ba la kyntang jong ki khun Israel, ha me nga la ai ïa ki na ka bynta kata ka jingpynsleh, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong me, da ka hukum bymjukut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kane, kan long ka jong me, na kita kiei kiei ki bakhuid tam kiba la lait na ka ding: ki jingainguh jong ki baroh, ki jingainguh bam jong ki baroh, bad ki jingkñia sait pop jong ki baroh, bad ki jingkñia namar ki jingpalat jong ki baroh, ïa kiba dei ba kin ai ha nga, kin long ki bakyntang tam eh ha me, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong me.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha ka jaka kyntang tam, men bam ïa ka: u shynrang baroh un bam ïa ka; kan long ka bakyntang ha me.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kane ruh kan long ka jong me: ka jingainguh kyntiew na ki jingainguh jong ki, lem bad ki jingainguh kaweh baroh jong ki khun Israel: nga la ai ïa ki ha me, bad ha ki khun shynrang, bad ki khun kynthei jong me, lem bad me, da ka hukum bymjukut: uwei uwei baroh u bakhuid na ka ïing jong me, un ïoh bam na ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka babha tam baroh na ka umphniang, bad ka babha tam baroh na ka Waiñ, bad na u Kew, ki soh nyngkong jong ki keiñ ïa kiba kin ainguh ha U Trai, ïa kita, nga la ai ha me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kiba la ih nyngkong na kiei kiei baroh ha ka ri, ïa kiba kin wan ai ha U Trai, kin long ki jong me; bad uwei uwei baroh u bakhuid na ka ïing jong me, un ïoh bam na ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kiei kiei baroh ba la pynkyntang ha Israel, kin long ki jong me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kiei kiei baroh kiba kha nyngkong ka kpoh na ka doh baroh, ïa kiba kin wan ai ha U Trai, la ka long na ki briew, ne na ki mrad, kin long ki jong me: hynrei, ïa uta uba la kha nyngkong na u briew, men shah ban siewspah, bad ïa uba la kha nyngkong na ki mrad ki bymkhuid, yn siewspah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ïa kita kiba dei ban siewspah men siewspah ïa ki naduh kaba shi bnai ka rta, katba kum ka jingkheiñ dor jong me, da san shekel ki sbai rupa, katba kum ka shekel jong ka jaka kyntang, kaba long arphew gerah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ïa ita iba la kha nyngkong na ka masi, lane ïa iba la kha nyngkong na ka langbrot, lane ïa iba la kha nyngkong na ka blang, ïa kita, men ym shah ban siewspah; ki long ki bakhuid: men synreit ïa ka snam jong ki ha ka duwan, bad ïa ki khleiñ jong ki, men thang kum ka jingkñia ha ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ka doh jong ki, kan long ka jong me, kumba ka krung kaweh, bad kumba ka kti kamon, ki long ki jong me.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ïa ki jingainguh kyntiew baroh na kiei kiei ki bakhuid, ïa kiba ki khun Israel kin ainguh ha U Trai, nga la ai ha me, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ha ki khun kynthei jong me, lem bad me, da ka hukum bymjukut: ka long ka jutang kaba da ka mluh junom la junom ha khmat U Trai ha me, bad ha ki symbai jong me, lem bad me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Aaron, “Men ym ïoh ka jingïoh pateng ha ka ri jong ki, bad men ym ïoh bynta ruh hapdeng jong ki: nga long ma nga ka bynta, bad ka jingïoh pateng jong me hapdeng ki khun Israel.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Bad, ha khmih, nga la ai ha ki khun u Lebi ïa kaba shiphew baroh ha Israel ïa ka ban long ka jingïoh pateng, na ka bynta kata ka kam ïa kaba ki trei, kata keiñ, ka kam ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te wat ai ba ki khun Israel kin wan shuh hajan Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ba ïoh kin kit ïa ka pop, bad ba kin ïap.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, ki Lebi kin trei ïa ka kam Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, kin kit ruh ïa ka pop jong ki: kane kan long ka hukum bymjukut ïa ki jingkha pateng jong phi, bad hapdeng ki khun Israel, kim don ka jingïoh pateng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ïa kiba shiphew jong ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ki ainguh kum ka jingainguh kyntiew ha U Trai, nga la ai ha ki Lebi kum ka bynta: namar kata, nga la ong ha ki, ‘Hapdeng ki khun Israel kin ym ïoh ka jingïoh pateng.’ ”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Kumne men kren ha ki Lebi, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Haba phi shim na ki khun Israel ïa kita kiba shiphew, ïa kiba nga la ai ha phi na ki, ban long ka bynta jong phi, na kata te, phi ruh phin ainguh da ka jingainguh kyntiew ha U Trai, ïa kaba shiphew na kata kaba shiphew keiñ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ïa ka kam ka jingainguh kyntiew jong phi yn ñiew ha phi, kum u Kew na ka kyntem, bad kum ka jingdap jong ka kor khñiot soh Waiñ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, phi ruh phin ainguh da ka jingainguh kyntiew ha U Trai na kita kiba shiphew jong phi baroh, ïa kiba phi shim na ki khun Israel; bad na kata, phin ai ka jingainguh kyntiew ka jong U Trai ha u Aaron lyngdoh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ki jingïoh jong phi baroh, phin ainguh ïa ka jingainguh kyntiew baroh ka jong U Trai, na ka babha tam baroh ka jong ka, kata ka bynta keiñ kaba la kyntang na ka.’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Men ong te ha ki, ‘Haba phi pynkyntiew ïa ka babha tam jong ka na ka, te yn ñiew ïa ka ha ki Lebi kum ka jingkyrhai jong ka kyntem, bad kum ka jingkyrhai jong ka kor khñiot soh Waiñ.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Phin bam ruh ïa ka ha ki jaka baroh, ma phi bad ki kur shi ïing jong phi de: naba ka long ka nong jong phi namar ka kam jong phi ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te haba phi la pynkyntiew na ka, ïa ka babha tam jong ka, phin ym kit pop na ka bynta jong ka: to wat pynjakhlia ma phi ruh ïa kiei kiei ruh ki bakhuid ki jong ki khun Israel, ïoh phin ïap.’ ”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren pat ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kane ka long ka rukom jong ka hukum ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum, u da ong, ‘To kren ha ki khun Israel, ba kin wallam ha me ïa ka masi lud basaw ba-tlem, ha kaba ym don ka jingduna, bad ha kaba ym shym la buh ïa ka jwar mynno mynno ruh:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te phin aiti ïa ka ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, ba un ïalam ïa ka shabar ka jaka shong dara, te uno uno uwei un pynïap ïa ka ha khmat jong u:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u Eleasar lyngdoh un shim na ka snam jong ka da ka shynriah'ti jong u, bad un synreit na ka snam jong ka beit sha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, hynñiew sien:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> te uno uno uwei un thang ïa kata ka masi lud ha khmat jong u; ïa ka snieh jong ka, bad ïa ka doh jong ka, bad ïa ka snam jong ka, lem bad ka eit jong ka, un thang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u lyngdoh un shim ïa u dieng Kedar, bad ïa u Hyssop, bad ïa ka basaw hain hain, un bred ruh ïa ka hapdeng kata ka jingthang ïa kata ka masi lud.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u lyngdoh un sait ïa la ki jaiñ, bad un sum ïa la ka met ha ka um, hadien kata, to ai ba un wan ha kata ka jaka shong dara, bad u lyngdoh un long u bymkhuid haduh janmiet.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te uta ruh uba la thang ïa ka, un sait ïa la ki jaiñ ha ka um, bad un sum ruh ïa la ka met ha ka um, bad un long u bymkhuid haduh janmiet.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u briew u bakhuid un khur ïa ka dpei kata ka masi lud, bad un buh ruh ïa ka habar ka jaka shong dara, ha ka jaka ka bakhuid, bad un sumar de ïa ka ïa u paidlang ki khun Israel, ban long ka um ka jingpynkhuid: ka long ka jingkñia namar ka pop.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te uta uba khur ïa kata ka dpei jong kata ka masi lud, un sait ïa la ki jaiñ, bad un long u bymkhuid haduh janmiet: te ha ki khun Israel, bad ha u nongwei uba wanhap hapdeng jong ki, kane kan long ka hukum bymjukut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “ ‘Uta uba ktah ïa ka metïap jong uno uno u briew, un long u bymkhuid, hynñiew sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ha ka sngi ka balai, un pynkhuid ïa lade da kata ka um, bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, un long u bakhuid: hynrei, lada un ym pynkhuid ïa lade ha ka sngi ka balai, te un ym long u bakhuid ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Uno uno ruh uba ktah ïa ka metïap jong uno uno u briew uba la ïap, hynrei, u bym pynkhuid ïa lade, u pyntngit ïa Ka Tabernakl U Trai; bad ïa kata ka mynsiem yn ot noh na Israel: namar ba ym shym la synreit ïa kata ka um ka jingpynkhuid halor jong u, un long u bymkhuid; ka jingbymkhuid jong u ka dang sah keiñ ha u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “ ‘Kane ka long ka hukum haba u briew u ïap ha ka ïingjaiñ: kita baroh kiba wan hapoh kata ka ïingjaiñ, bad kita baroh kiba la don hapoh kata ka ïingjaiñ, kin long ki bymkhuid, hynñiew sngi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka jingdiang baroh ruh kaba rynghang, ïa kaba ym shym la teh jingtap halor jong ka, ka long ka bymkhuid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Uno uno ruh uba ktah ïa kaba la pynïap noh da ka waitlam ha ka lyngkha, lane ïa ka metïap, lane ïa ka shyieng jong u briew, lane ïa ka jingtep, un long u bymkhuid, hynñiew sngi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te namar uta u bymkhuid, kin shim na ka dpei jong kata kaba thang ïa ka jingkñia namar ka pop, bad ïa ka um na kaba tuid ruh yn buh ha ka, ha ka pliang:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u briew u bakhuid un shim ïa u Hyssop, bad un wieh ïa u ha kata ka um, bad un synreit ïa ka halor kata ka ïingjaiñ, bad halor ki pliang baroh, bad halor ki briew kat kiba la don hangta, bad halor uta uba la ktah ïa ka shyieng, lane ïa uba la pynïap noh, lane ïa uba la ïap hi, lane ïa ka jingtep:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te uta u bakhuid un synreit halor uta u bymkhuid ha ka sngi ka balai, bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew de: te ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, un pynkhuid ïa lade; bad un sait ruh ïa la ki jaiñ, bad un sum ïa lade ha ka um, te ha kaba la janmiet, un long bakhuid.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “ ‘Hynrei, uta u briew ïa uba la pyntngit, bad u ban ym pynkhuid ïa lade, ïa kata ka mynsiem yn ot noh napdeng u paidlang, namar u la pynsang ïa ka jaka kyntang ka jong U Trai: ïa ka um ka jingpynkhuid ym shym la synreit halor jong u; u long u bymkhuid.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te kan long ka hukum bymjukut ha ki: bad uta uba synreit ïa ka um ka jingpynkhuid, un sait ïa la ki jaiñ; bad uta uba ktah ïa ka um ka jingpynkhuid, un long u bymkhuid haduh janmiet.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba uta u bymkhuid un ktah, kin long bymkhuid; bad uta u briew ba ktah ïa kita, un long u bymkhuid haduh janmiet.’ ”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel, kata, u paidlang baroh, ki la ïawan poi ha ka ri khlaw Sin ha u bnai u banyngkong: bad uta u paidbah u la shong sah ha Kadesh; hangta ruh ka la ïap ka Miriam, bad hangta la tep ïa ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ym shym la don um ïa uta u paidlang: bad ki la ïalum lang ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad ïa u Aaron.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kita ki briew ruh ki la ïakren sngewsih ïa u Moses, bad ki la ïathuh, ki la ong, “A ban da ngi la lah ïap noh mynba ki para jong ngi ki la ïap noh ha khmat U Trai!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Balei ruh phi la ïalam ïa u paidlang U Trai sha kane ka ri khlaw, ba ngin ïap ha ka, lem bad ki jingri jong ngi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Balei ruh ba phi la pynmih artet ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, ban ïalam ïa ngi sha kane ka jaka ka basniew? ka jaka khlem symbai, khlem soh Dumbur, khlem soh Waiñ, bad khlem soh Pong; ka um ban dih ruh ym don.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Aaron, ki la leit noh na khmat uta u paidlang sha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ki la hap dem ruh la ki khmat: te ka burom U Trai ka la paw ha ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “To shim ïa uta u diengduh, to lum lang ruh ïa uta u paidlang, ma me, bad u Aaron u para jong me, to kren ruh ha uta u mawsiang ha khmat jong ki, te un ai noh ïa ka um jong u; bad to pynmih noh ma me ruh ha ki, ïa ka um na uta u mawsiang: kumta men ai dih ha uta u paidlang, bad ha ki jingri jong ki de.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la shim ïa uta u diengduh na khmat U Trai, kumba u la hukum ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Moses te, bad u Aaron, ki la ïalum lang ïa uta u paidlang ha khmat uta u mawsiang, bad u la ong ha ki, “To sngap mynta, phi ki nongïaleh pyrshah; ka long ne em ba ngin pynmih um ha phi na une u mawsiang?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Moses ruh u la rah ïa la ka kti, bad da uta u diengduh jong u, u la shoh ar sien ïa uta u mawsiang: bad ka la mih noh shibun ka um, te uta u paidlang u la dih, bad ki jingri jong ki de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, bad ha u Aaron, “Namar ba phim shym la ngeit ïa nga, ïa ka ban pyndonburom ïa nga ha khmat ki khun Israel, namar kata keiñ, phin ym ïoh ïalam ïa une u paidlang sha kata ka ri ïa kaba nga la ai ha ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kane long ka um Meribah: naba ki khun Israel ki la ïaleh ïa U Trai, bad la pyndonburom ïa U ha ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Moses u la phah ïa ki nongkit-ktien na Kadesh sha u syiem ka Edom, da kaba ong, “Kumne u ong u Israel u para jong me, ‘Me tip ïa ka jingjynjar baroh ïa kaba la jia ha ngi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> kumno ba ki kpa jong ngi ki la leit hiar ha ka ri Ijipt, bad ba ngi la shong sah ha ka ri Ijipt kham slem; ki Ijipt ruh ki la pynshitom ïa ngi, bad ïa ki kpa jong ngi;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad haba ngi la kyang duwai ha U Trai, u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ngi, bad u la phah ruh ïa u angel jong u, bad u la pynmih noh ïa ngi na kata ka ri Ijipt: te ha khmih, ngi don ha Kadesh, ka shnong ha ka bakut ka pud jong me:’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> nga duwai ïa me, ‘To shah ïa ngi ban ïaid lyngba ïa ka ri jong me: ngin ym ïaid lyngba ïa ki lyngkha, lane lyngba ïa ki brisoh Waiñ, lymne ngin ym dih ruh na ka um jong ki pukri: ngin ïaid na ka lynti bah jong u syiem, ngin ym phai sha kamon lane sha kadiang, tad ynda ngi la lait na ki pud jong me.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Edom u la ong ha u, “Wat wan ïaid hajan jong nga, ba ïoh ngan wan ïaleh ïa me da ka waitlam.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ong ha u, “Ngin leit kiew da ka lynti bah, bad lada ma nga, lane ki jingri jong nga, ngin dih na ka um jong me, ngan siew ïa ka dor jong ka: ngan tang shu ïaid lyngba da la ki kjat, khlem da leh ei ei ruh em.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U te u la ong, “Men ym ïoh leit lyngba.” U Edom ruh u la wan mih ïaleh ïa u da shibun u paidbah, bad da ka kti kaba donbor.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumne, u Edom um treh ban ai lynti ïa u Israel lyngba ka ri jong u: kumta u Israel u la phai noh na u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki khun Israel, kata, uta u paidlang baroh, ki la ïaid na Kadesh: bad ki la wan poi sha u lum Hor.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, bad u Aaron, ha u lum Hor, harud ka ri Edom, u da ong,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Ïa u Aaron yn ïalum lang sha ki briew jong u: naba un ym ïoh leit sha kata ka ri ïa kaba nga la ai ha ki khun Israel, namar phim shym la kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong nga ha kata ka um Meribah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> To shim ïa u Aaron, bad ïa u Eleasar u khun jong u, to wallam artet ruh ïa ki sha u lum Hor:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> te men loit noh ïa ki jaiñ jong u na u Aaron, bad men pynphong ruh ïa ki ha u Eleasar u khun jong u: te ïa u Aaron yn ïalum lang sha ki briew jong u, hangta ruh un ïap.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Moses u la leh kumba u la hukum U Trai: bad ki la ïaleit kiew sha uta u lum Hor ha khmat uta u paidlang baroh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Moses u la loit noh na u Aaron ïa ki jaiñ jong u, bad u la pynphong ïa ki ha u Eleasar u khun jong u; bad u Aaron u la ïap hangta ha khlieh uta u lum: te u Moses bad u Eleasar ki la ïahiar noh na uta u lum.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba uta u paidlang baroh u la ïohi ba u la ïap u Aaron, ka ïing ki khun Israel baroh, ki la ïambriew ïa u Aaron, laiphew sngi."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u syiem ka Arad, u kynja Kanaan, uba shong sah shaphang shathie, u la ïohsngew ba ki Israel ki ïawan na ka lynti ki nongsyntiat; bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel, bad khyndiat na ki u la kem ha kliar ka wait.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Israel u la kular da ka jingkular skhem ha U Trai, bad u la ong, “Lada men aiti noh shisha ïa kine ki briew ha ka kti jong nga, nga te ngan pynjot noh khoit ïa ki shnong jong ki.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Trai u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ki Israel, bad U la aiti noh ïa ki Kanaan; ki te ki la pynjot noh khoit ïa ki, bad ïa ki shnong jong ki: bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Hormah”.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la ïaid na u lum Hor da ka lynti ka Duriaw Basaw, ïa ka ban leit sawdong ïa ka ri Edom: te ka la pisa eh ka mynsiem jong uta u paidbah namar kata ka lynti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uta u paidbah u la kren pyrshah ïa U Blei, bad ïa u Moses, “Balei phi la ïalam ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt ba ngin ïap ha ka ri khlaw? namar, u kpu ym don, lymne ka um ruh ym don; bad ki mynsiem jong ngi ki la sngewjli ïa une u kpu basniew.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la phah ïa ki 'seiñ ding hapdeng uta u paidbah, bad ki la puh ïa ki briew; te ki la ïap shibun eh ki briew na ki Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te namar kata, kita ki briew ki la wan ha u Moses, ki la ong ruh, “Ngi la leh pop, ba ngi la kren pyrshah ïa U Trai, bad pyrshah ïa me ruh; to duwai ha U Trai, ba un shim noh ïa kine ki bseiñ napdeng jong ngi.” Bad u Moses u la duwai na ka bynta uta u paidbah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To thaw ïa me ïa u 'seiñ ding, bad to buh ruh ïa u halor u dieng: ba uwei uwei baroh ïa uba la puh, haba u la khmih ïa u, un ïoh im.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la thaw ïa u 'seiñ rnong, bad u la buh ïa u halor u dieng; te lada u bseiñ u la puh ïa uno uno u briew, haba u la khmih ïa uta u 'seiñ rnong, u la ïoh im keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la mih noh, bad ki la shong dara ha Oboth.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki la ïaid na Oboth ruh, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Ije-abarim, ha ka ri khlaw kaba marpyrshah ka Moab, shaphang kaba mih ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nangta ruh ki la mih noh, bad ki la ïashong dara hajan ka wah Sared.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nangta ki la ïamih noh, bad ki la ïashong dara sha shiliang ka Arnon, kaba ha ka ri khlaw, kaba mih noh na ki rud ki Amor: namar ka Arnon ka long ka pud ka Moab, hapdeng ka Moab bad ki Amor.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, ba la ong ha Ka Kitab Ki Thma Ki Jong U Trai, “Ïa kaba u la leh ha ka Duriaw Basaw, bad ha ki wah duid Arnon,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ha ka khriang ki wah duid kiba hiar ha kaba shong ka Ar, bad kaba don ha ka pud u Moab.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nangta ki la leit sha Beer: kata ka long kata ka pukri ba U Trai u la kren ha u Moses shaphang jong ka, “To ïalum lang ïa ki briew, nga te ngan ai um ha ki.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki Israel te ki la ïarwai ïa kane ka jingrwai: “A pukri to kyrsoi noh; ma phi to rwai phai ktien ïa ka:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki syiem ki la ïatih ïa kata ka pukri, ki rangbah jong u paidbah ki la ïatih ïa ka, lem bad uta u nongai hukum da ki diengduh jong ki.” Te na kata ka ri khlaw ki la ïaleit sha Mattanah:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad na Mattanah sha Nahaliel: bad na Nahaliel sha Bamoth:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad na Bamoth sha ka ri them kaba ha ka ri Moab, sha khlieh uta u lum uba khmih sha ka ri khlaw.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Israel u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, u da ong,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “To shah ïa nga ban ïaid lyngba ïa ka ri jong me: ngan ym phai sha ki lyngkha, lane sha ki brisoh Waiñ; ngin ym dih na ka um jong ki pukri: hynrei, ngin ïaid da ka lynti bah u syiem, tad ynda ngi la lait na ki pud jong me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Sihon te um shah ïa ki Israel ban ïaid lyngba ïa ka ri jong u: hynrei, u Sihon u la lum lang ïa ki briew jong u baroh, bad u la mih noh ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki Israel sha kata ka ri khlaw, bad u la wan sha Jahas; bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki Israel te ki la jop ïa u da ka syrti waitlam, bad ki la shimti ïa ka ri jong u naduh Arnon, haduh Jabbok, haduh ki khun u Ammon keiñ: naba ka pud ki khun u Ammon kaba skhem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki Israel ki la shimti ïa kito ki nongbah baroh: ki Israel ki la shong sah ruh ha ki nongbah baroh ki jong ki Amor, ha Heshbon, bad ha ki nongrit jong ki baroh de.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba ka Heshbon ka la dei ka nongbah u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, uba la lah ïaleh thma ïa uta u syiem ki Moab uba mynshuwa, bad uba la lah knieh noh ïa ka khyndew jong u baroh na ka kti jong u, haduh Arnon keiñ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kata, kiba ïaphawar ki ong, “To ïawan haduh Heshbon, to ai ban tei, to ai ban pynskhem ïa ka nongbah u Sihon:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> namar ka la mih noh ka ding na Heshbon, bad ka thylliej ding na ka nongbah u Sihon: ka la bam duh ïa ka Ar kaba ha Moab, bad ïa ki trai jong ki Bamoth Arnon.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kordit ïa me, u Moab! Me la ïap, A u paidbah u Khemosh: u la ai mraw ïa la ki khun shynrang ïa kiba la lait, bad ïa la ki khun kynthei ha u Sihon u syiem ki Amor.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngi la siat ïa ki; ka Heshbon ka la jot noh haduh Dibon, bad ngi la pynjot noh ïa ki haduh Nophah kaba kot haduh Medeba.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta, ki Israel ki la shong sah ha ka ri ki Amor.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Moses u la phah jngoh ïa ka Jaser, bad ki la ïajop ïa ki shnong rit jong ka, bad ki la beh noh ïa kita ki Amor kiba la don hangta.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki la ïaphai noh, bad ki la leit da ka lynti Bashan: te u Og u syiem jong ka Bashan u la mih noh, haduh Edrei, ma u bad ki briew jong u baroh, ban ïaleh thma ïa ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To wat sheptieng ïa u: naba ha ka kti jong me nga la aiti ïa u, bad ïa ki briew jong u baroh, bad ïa ka khyndew jong u; te men leh ïa u kumba me la leh ïa u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, uba la shong sah ha Heshbon.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kumta, ki la shoh ïap ïa u, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad ïa ki briew jong u baroh, haduh ba ym shym la iehnoh sah wat uwei ruh em: ki la shimti ruh ïa ka khyndew jong u."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaid noh, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ki pyntha jong u Moab, harud ka Jordan kaba shaphang shane marpyrshah ka Jerikho.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Balak u khun u Sippor, u la ïohi ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba ki la leh ki Israel ïa ki Amor.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki Moab ki la sheptieng eh ïa ki briew, naba ki la bun: bad ki la khuslai eh ki Moab namar ki khun Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki Moab ki la ong ha ki tymmen ki san ki Midian, “Mynta une u paidlang un jliah noh ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba don baroh sawdong ïa ngi, kumba u jliah noh u masi ïa u phlang jong ka khyndew.” Te u Balak u khun u Sippor, u la long u syiem ki Moab ha kata ka por.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha u Balaam u khun u Beor, sha Pethor, kaba hajan kata ka wah, ha ka ri ki khun ki briew jong u, ïa ka ban khot ïa u, u da ong, “Ha khmih, don u paidbah byllien uba la mih noh na Ijipt; ha khmih, ki ïatap lin ïa ka khmat ka pyrthei, bad ki ïashong ruh ha marpyrshah ïa nga:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa me, to wan mynta, to tim ïa une u paidbah na ka bynta jong nga; namar ki kham khraw bor ïa nga: toi lehse ngan da lah ïa ka ban jop noh ïa ki, bad ban beh noh ïa ki na kane ka ri: namar nga tip, ba ïa uta uba men kyrkhu ma me, un long ba la kyrkhu, bad ïa uta uba men tim ma me, un long ba la tim keiñ.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kita ki tymmen ki san ki Moab bad ki tymmen ki san ki Midian, ki la ïamih noh bad ka bainong khan ha la ki kti; bad ki la wan poi ha u Balaam, bad ki la ïathuh ruh ha u, ïa ki ktien jong u Balak.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “To thiah basa hangne mynta ka miet, te ngan phai ktien ha phi kat kumba un kren U Trai ha nga:” bad kita ki rangbah ki Moab ki la ïashong bad u Balaam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Blei u la wan ha u Balaam, bad U la ong, “Kiei kine ki briew kiba don bad me?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Balaam u la ong ha U Blei, “U Balak u khun u Sippor u syiem ki Moab, u la phah ktien ha nga, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ‘Ha khmih, don u paidbah byllien uba la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt, uba tap lin ïa ka khmat ka pyrthei: to wan mynta te, to tim ïa ki na ka bynta jong nga; toi lehse ngan da lah ïa ka ban jop ïa ki, bad ban beh noh ïa ki.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Blei te u la ong ha u Balaam, “Me wat leit ryngkat bad ki; lymne wat tim ïa uta u paidbah: naba u long ba la kyrkhu.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Balaam u la khie mynstep, bad u la ong ha kita ki rangbah u Balak, “To khie leit sha la ka ri: naba U Trai um shah ïa nga ban leit ryngkat bad phi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kita ki rangbah ki Moab ki ïakhie joit, bad ki la leit wan noh sha u Balak, ki la ong ruh, “U Balaam um treh ban wan ryngkat bad ngi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Balak u la phah pat ïa ki rangbah kham bun, bad kiba kham donburom ban ïa kita kiwei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la ïawan poi ha u Balaam, ki la ong ruh ha u, “Kumne u ong u Balak u khun u Sippor, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to wat shah ei ei ruh em da lei lei ban pynpep ïa me ban wan sha nga:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> namar ngan pynkyntiew ïa me sha ka burom ka bakhraw eh, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba men ong ha nga, ngan leh: namar kata, nga kyrpad ïa me, to wan, to da tim noh ruh ïa kine ki briew na ka bynta jong nga.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Balaam u la ïathuh, bad u la ong ha ki shakri u Balak, “Lada u Balak un ai ha nga ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, kat ban pyndap ïa ka ïing jong u, ngam lah leit palat ïa ka ktien U Trai uba U Blei jong nga, ïa ka ban leh ka barit, ne ka bakhraw keiñ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, nga kyrpad ïa phi, to sah ma phi ruh hangne mynta ka miet, ba ngan ïoh tip U Trai un ong aïu shuh ha nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Blei u la wan ha u Balaam mynmiet, bad U la ong ha u, “Lada ki la wan khot ïa me kine ki briew, to khie, to leit ruh lem bad ki; hynrei, pynban, ïa kata ka ktien ïa kaba ngan ïathuh ha me, ïa kata hi men leh keiñ.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Balaam u la khie dang step, bad u la teh jin halor ka kadda jong u, bad u la leit lem bad kita ki rangbah ki Moab.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Blei ka la meh namar ba u la leit: bad u angel U Trai u la ïeng ïaleh ïa u ha lynti. Te u la shong halor la ka kadda, bad ar ngut ki shakri jong u, lem bad u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kata ka kadda ka la ïohi ïa u angel U Trai ba u da ïeng ha kata ka lynti, bad ba u da don la ka waitlam ba la sei ha ka kti jong u: te ka kadda ka la kiar noh na kata ka lynti, bad ka la leit sha ka lyngkha: te u Balaam u la shoh ïa ka kadda ban pynphai ïa ka sha ka lynti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, uta u angel U Trai u la ïeng ha ka lynti ki brisoh Waiñ, ha kaba don ka kynroh baroh ar liang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba ka kadda ka la ïohi ïa uta u angel U Trai, ka la kyntur ïa lade sha kata ka kynroh, bad ka la ban eh ïa ka sla'jat jong u Balaam ha kata ka kynroh: te u la shoh pat ïa ka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u la leit kham jngai, bad u la ïeng ha ka jaka kaba khim, ha kaba ym don jaka ban phai, lymne sha kamon, lymne sha kadiang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba ka kadda ka la ïohi pat ïa uta u angel U Trai, ka la dem khop hapoh u Balaam: bad ka jingbitar u Balaam ka la khie lep, bad u la shoh ïa ka kadda da u diengduh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad U Trai u la plie ïa ka shyntur kata ka kadda, ka te ka la ong ha u Balaam, “Nga la leh aïu ïa me ba me la shoh ïa nga kumne lai sien?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Balaam u la ong ha ka kadda, “Namar ba pha la lehbeiñ ïa nga: A ban da don ka waitlam ha ka kti jong nga, ba kumta ngan da pom ïap ïa pha mynta.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kata ka kadda te ka la ong ha u Balaam, “Ngam dei ka kadda jong me, halor kaba me la ju shong naduh ba nga la long ka jong me, haduh mynta? Nga la ju leh kumne ïa me mynno mynno ruh ne em?” U te u la ong, “Em.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te U Trai u la pynpeit ïa ka khmat u Balaam, bad u la ïohi ïa uta u angel U Trai ba u da ïeng ha kata ka lynti, ba u da don ruh ka waitlam ba la sei ha ka kti jong u: te u la dem ïa la ka khlieh, u la dem ngon ruh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u ong ha u, “Balei ba me la shoh ïa la ka kadda kine lai sien? Ha khmih, nga la mih noh ban long u nongïaleh ïa me, namar kane ka lynti jong me ka long kaba mutlop ha khmat jong nga:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te kata ka kadda ka la ïohi ïa nga, bad ka la kiar noh na nga kine lai sien: lymda ka la lah kiar noh na nga, shisha mynta nga la lah pynïap noh ïa me, bad nga la ri pynim ïa ka.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Balaam u la ong ha uta u angel U Trai, “Nga la leh pop; naba ngam shym tip ba me la ïeng ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga ha kata ka lynti: te mynta, lada ka long ka basniew ha khmat jong me, ngan leit phai noh pat keiñ.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te uta u angel U Trai u la ong ha u Balaam, “To khie leit bad kine ki briew: hynrei, ïa kata ka ktien ïa kaba ngan kren ha me, tang ïa kata men kren.” Kumta, u Balaam u la leit lem bad ki rangbah u Balak.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba u Balak u la ïohsngew ba u la wan u Balaam, u la leit tan ïa u haduh ka nongbah u Moab, kaba harud Arnon, kaba ha ka bakut eh ka pud.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u Balak u la ong ha u Balaam, “Nga shisha ngam shym la phah khot eh ïa me? te na ka balei mem shym la wan ha nga? nga don bor ne em ban kyntiew burom ïa me?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U Balaam te u la ïathuh ha u Balak, “Ha khmih, nga la wan ha me: hynrei, nga hi, nga don bor aïu mynta ban ong ei ei ruh? Ïa kata ka ktien ïa kaba U Blei un buh ha ka shyntur jong nga, ïa kata ngan kren keiñ.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Balaam u leit ryngkat bad u Balak, bad ki la poi ha Kirjath-husoth.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te u Balak u la pynïap ïa ki masi dab, bad ïa ki langbrot, u la phah ai ruh ha u Balaam, bad ha kita ki rangbah kiba don lem bad u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kaba lashai, ba u Balak u la shim ïa u Balaam, bad u la ïalam ïa u sha ki jaka kyntang bajrong u Baal, bad nangta u lah ban ïohi ïa ka bakut eh jong uta u paidbah."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Balaam u la ong ha u Balak, “To tei hynñiew tylli ki duwan ha nga hangne, to khreh ruh ha nga hangne, hynñiew tylli ki masi dab, bad hynñiew tylli ki langbrot shynrang.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Balak u la leh kumba u la ong u Balaam; u Balak ruh bad u Balaam, ki la ainguh da uwei u masi dab, bad uwei u langbrot halor kawei kawei ka duwan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Balaam u la ong ha u Balak, “To ïeng ma me hajan ka jingainguh thang jong me, te nga ngan leit noh nangne; lehse U Trai un wan ïashem bad nga: bad ngan ïathuh ha me ïa kata ka ktien ïa kaba un pyni ha nga.” Bad u la leit kyrpang hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad U Blei u la ïashem bad u Balaam: bad u la ong ha U, “Nga la khreh hynñiew tylli ki duwan, nga la ainguh ruh halor kawei kawei ka duwan da uwei u masi dab, bad uwei u langbrot.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Trai u la buh ktien ha ka shyntur u Balaam, bad U la ong, “To leit phai sha u Balak, bad kumne men kren.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la leit phai sha u, te ha khmih, u dang ïeng hajan ka jingainguh thang jong u, ma u bad ki rangbah Moab baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “U Balak u syiem Moab u la wallam ïa nga na Aram, na ki lum mihngi; u ong, ‘Ale, to tim noh ïa u Jakob na ka bynta jong nga, to ale ruh, to beiñ ïa ki Israel.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumno ngan tim noh, ïa uba U Blei um shym la tim noh? lane kumno ngan beiñ, ïa uba U Trai um shym la beiñ?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Naba na khlieh ki mawsiang nga ïohi ïa u, bad nalor ki lum nga khmih ïa u: ha khmih, ki briew kiba ïashong sah kyrpang hi, ïa ki ban ym ñiew lang ruh bad ki jaid bynriew.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Uei ba lah ban ñiew ïa u shyiap u Jakob, bad ïa ka jingkheiñ shi pawa ki Israel? Ai ba ngan ïap da ka jingïap u riewhok, to ai ruh ba ka bakut jong nga kan long kum ka jong u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Balak u la ong ha u Balaam, “Me la leh aïu ïa nga? Nga la shim ïa me ïa ka ban tim noh ïa ki nongshun jong nga, hynrei, ha khmih, me la kyrkhu ïa kita naduh haduh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Nga dei ne em ban sumar, ba ngan kren ïa kaba U Trai u buh ha ka shyntur jong nga?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Balak u la ïathuh ha u, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to wan ryngkat bad nga sha kawei pat ka jaka, na kaba me lah ban ïohi ïa ki; nangta, men ïohi tang ïa ka bakut eh jong ki, te men ym ïohi ïa ki baroh: me ruh men tim noh ïa ki nangta, na ka bynta jong nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la ïalam ïa u sha ka madan Sophim, sha khlieh u lum Piskah, bad u la tei hynñiew tylli ki duwan, u la kñia ruh ïa uwei u masi dab, bad ïa uwei u langbrot, halor kawei kawei ka duwan.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U te u la ong ha u Balak, “To ïeng ma me hangne hajan ka jingainguh thang jong me, nga te ngan leit hangtai ban ïashem bad U Trai.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te U Trai u la ïashem bad u Balaam, bad U la buh ka ktien ha ka shyntur jong u, bad U la ong, “To leit phai pat sha u Balak, ong ruh kumne.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u la wan poi ha u, ha khmih, u dang ïeng hajan ka jingainguh thang jong u, bad ki rangbah Moab lem bad u. Te u Balak u la ong ha u, “U la kren aïu U Trai?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, u la ong ruh, “To ïeng, ko Balak; to sngap ruh; ko khun u Sippor, to shahshkor ïa nga:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Blei um long u briew, ba un lamler; lymne u khun u briew, ba un kylla-ka-bamut: ïa kaba U la ong, un ym leh? Lane ïa kaba U la kren, un ym pyndep noh?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ha khmih, nga la ïoh hukum ïa ka ban kyrkhu: U la kyrkhu ma U, te ngam lah pynkylla ïa kata.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Um ïohi ïa ka pop ha u Jakob, bad um ïohi ruh ïa ka jingpalat ha u Israel: U Trai U Blei jong u, U don ryngkat bad u, bad ka jingrisa u syiem ka hapdeng jong ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Blei u la ïalam ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt; U donbor kat kum ka bor u kynda.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar shisha ym don kaba ai ksuid pyrshah ïa u Jakob, lymne ruh kaba leh byrtong pyrshah ïa u Israel: ha kane ka por yn ong shaphang u Jakob bad shaphang u Israel, ‘Katno u la leh U Blei!’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha khmih, u paidbah un khie joit kum u sing uba heh, bad kum u sing basamla un pynkhie joit ïa lade; un ym thiah tad ynda u la ïoh bam na ka jinglute, bad ba u la ïoh dih ïa ka snam jong kita ïa kiba la pynïap.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Balak u la ong ha u Balaam, “To wat tim shuh ïa ki, lymne wat kyrkhu shuh ïa ki ruh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, u Balaam u la phai ktien, bad u la ong ha u Balak, “Nga la ïathuh ne em ha me, nga da ong, ‘Ïa kaba U Trai un kren baroh, ïa kata ngan leh?’ ”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Balak u la ong ha u Balaam, “To ale, nga kyrpad ïa me, ngan ïalam ïa me sha kawei pat ka jaka; lehse un ibit U Blei ba men tim noh nangta ïa ki, na ka bynta jong nga.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Balak u la ïalam ïa u Balaam sha khlieh u Peor, uba phai shaphang ka ri khlaw.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Balaam u la ong ha u Balak, “To tei ha nga hynñiew tylli ki duwan hangne, bad to khreh ïa nga hangne, hynñiew tylli ki masi dab, bad hynñiew tylli ki langbrot shynrang.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Balak u la leh kumba u la ong u Balaam, bad u la ainguh da uwei u masi dab, bad uwei u langbrot ha kawei kawei ka duwan."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Balaam u la ïohi ba U Trai u la sngewbha ban kyrkhu ïa ki Israel, um shym la leit shuh ïa ka ban wad ïa ki jingkhan jingluh, kumba mynshuwa, hynrei, u la thew ïa la ka khmat sha ka ri khlaw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Balaam u la khmied ruh ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa ki Israel ba ki da ïashong dara katba kum ki jaid jong ki; te U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan ha u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “U Balaam u khun u Beor u la ong, bad uta u briew uba la khap ïa la ki khmat u la ong:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u nongsngew ïa ki jingong U Blei u la ong, uba la ïohi ïa ka jingithuhpaw jong U Balah Baroh, uba la hap ha ka jingi-rngai, hynrei, haba ki dang peit ki khmat jong u:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> katno ki itynnad ki ïingjaiñ jong me, ko Jakob, ki tabernakl jong me, ko Israel!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> La pynphriang kyrhai ïa ki kum ki ri them, kum ki kper harud ka wah, kum ki dieng Aloes ïa kiba u la thung U Trai, bad kum ki dieng Kedar hajan ki umtuid.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Un theh ki um na ki khiew jong u baroh, bad u symbai jong u un long ha bun ki um, bad u syiem jong u un long kham ha khlieh ïa u Agag, bad yn pynkyntiew ïa ka hima jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Blei u la pynmih noh ïa u na Ijipt; u don ka bor kum ka jong u kynda: un bam duh noh ïa ki jaid bynriew ki nongshun jong u, un pynkheiñ lwet ruh ïa ki shyieng jong ki, bad un pynpei lyngba ïa ki da ki khnam jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U dem, u thiah kum u sing, bad kum u sing uba heh keiñ; uei u ban pynkhih ïa u? Suk uta uba kyrkhu ïa me, bad kordit ïa uta uba tim noh ïa me.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka jingbitar u Balak ka la meh lep pyrshah ïa u Balaam, bad u la thab kti: bad u Balak u la ong ha u Balaam, “Nga la khot ïa me ban tim ïa ki nongshun jong nga, te, ha khmih, da kaba kyrkhu me la kyrkhu ïa ki, kine lai sien.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mynta te, namar kata, to phet noh sha la ka shnong: nga la ong ba ngan kyntiew ïa me sha ka burom bakhraw; hynrei, ha khmih, U Trai u la khang noh ïa me na ka burom.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Balaam u la ong ha u Balak, “Nga la kren ne em ha ki nonglam-ktien jong me ïa kiba me la phah ha nga, da kaba ong,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ‘Lada u Balak un da ai ha nga ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, ba-dap ha ïing jong u, ngan ym lah ban ryngkang ïa ka ktien U Trai, ban leh ïa ka babha, lane ïa ka basniew na la ka jong ka jingmut; ngan kren tang ïa kaba U Trai un ong?’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mynta te, ha khmih, ngan sa leit noh sha la ki jong ki briew: to ale te, bad ngan ïathuh ïa me ïa kaba kine ki briew kin leh ïa ki briew jong me ha kita ki sngi ki bakhatduh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “U Balaam u khun u Beor u la ong, bad uta u briew uba la khap ïa la ki khmat, u la ong:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U nongsngew ïa ki jingong U Blei, u la kren, uba tip ïa ka jingtip jong U Bahakhlieh Tam, bad uba la ïohi ïa ka jingithuhpaw U Balah Baroh, uba la hap ha ka jingi-rngai, hynrei, haba ki dang peit ki khmat jong u:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nga ïohi ïa u, hynrei, ym mynta: nga ïoh khmih ïa u, hynrei, ym najan: u khlur un wan noh na u Jakob, bad u dieng synshar un mih noh na u Israel, u ban shoh lwet ïa ki Moab baroh sawdong, bad u ban pynjot noh ïa ki khun baroh u Sheth.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Edom un long ka bynta trai, u Seir ruh un long ka bynta trai ïa ki nongshun jong u; te u Israel un nang leh khraw bor.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uwei na u Jakob un synshar, bad un pynjot noh ruh ïa kaba dang sah na ka nongbah.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba u la khmih ha u Amalek, u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “U banyngkong na ki jaid bynriew u long u Amalek; hynrei, ka bakut jong u kan long ba un ïap duh noh junom.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la khmih ha ki Ken ruh, te u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “Ka jaka shongneh jong me kaba skhem, bad me buh ïa la ka skum ha uta u mawsiang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Pynban, ïa u Ken yn pynduh noh, ha ban da u Asshur un ïalam mraw ïa me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la shim ïa la ka pharshi, bad u la ong, “Waw uei u ban im haba U Blei u leh ïa kane?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kin wan ki lieng lama ruh na ki rud ka Kittim, bad kin ïa-pynshitom ïa u Asshur, bad kin ïa-pynshitom ruh ïa u Eber, te u hi ruh un ïap duh noh junom.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Balaam u la ïeng joit, bad u la leit wan noh ruh sha la ka jaka: bad u Balak ruh u la leit noh."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ki Israel ki la ïashong sah ha Shittim, bad ki briew ki la sdang ban klim bad ki khun kynthei ki Moab:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki ruh ki la khot ïa uta u paidbah ha ki jingkñia ainguh ïa ki blei jong ki; te uta u paidbah u la bam, bad u la dem ha ki blei jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki Israel ki la pynïasoh ïa lade bad u Baal-peor: te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep pyrshah ïa ki Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To shim ïa ki rangbah baroh ki jong ki paidbah, bad to phasi ruh ïa ki ha khmat U Trai ha pyrshah ka sngi, ba kumta, ka jingbitar ba-meh lep jong U Trai, kan ïoh phai noh na ki Israel.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ha ki nongbishar jong ki Israel, “To pynïap uwei uwei ïa la ki briew kat kiba la pynïasoh ïa lade bad u Baal-peor.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ha khmih, uwei na ki khun Israel u la wan, bad u la wallam ïa kawei ka briew, ka kynja Midian, ha ki para jong u ha khmat u Moses, bad ha khmat u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel, haba ki dang ïaïam ha phyllaw Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u Phinehas, u khun u Eleasar, uba u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, u la ïohi ïa kata, u la mih joit napdeng uta u paidlang, bad u la shim ïa u sum ha la ka kti;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u la bud nadien uta u briew uba kynja Israel hapoh ka ïingjaiñ, bad u la sum lyngba ïa ki baroh ar ngut, ïa uta u briew keiñ uba kynja Israel, bad ïa kata ka kynthei, lyngba na ka kpoh jong ka. Te kumta, la pynsangeh ïa ka jingïapthem na ki khun Israel.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la ïap noh ha kata ka jingïapthem jin arphew saw hajar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Trai te u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “U Phinehas, u khun u Eleasar, u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, haba u la long uba shitrhem na ka bynta jong nga hapdeng jong ki, u la pynphai noh ïa ka jingbitar jong nga na ki khun Israel, ba ngam shym la pynduh noh ïa ki khun Israel ha kaba nga la thut eh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata, to ong, ‘Ha khmih, nga ai ha u ïa ka jutang ka jingsuk jong nga:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> te kan long ha u, bad ha ki symbai jong u hadien jong u, kaba ka jutang ka jinglong lyngdoh ka bymjukut; namar ba u la long uba shitrhem na ka bynta U Blei jong u, bad ba u la pynlong ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta ki khun Israel.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ka kyrteng jong uta u briew uba kynja Israel ïa uba la pynïap, uta keiñ ïa uba la pynïap lem bad kata ka kynja Midian, ka la long “u Simri”, u khun u Salu, u rangbah ka ïing u kpa jong u na ka jaid Simeon.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka kyrteng kata ka briew kaba kynja Midian ïa kaba la pynïap, ka la long “ka Kosbi”, ka khun u Sur; u rangbah jong u paidbah, bad uba na ka ïing ka bakhraw ha ka ri Midian.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Trai ruh u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “To pynshitom ïa ki Midian, to pynïap ruh ïa ki:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> naba ki ïa-pynshitom ïa phi da ki buit runar jong ki, da kiba ki la ïashukor ïa phi shaphang u Peor, bad shaphang ka Kosbi, ka khun jong u rangbah ki Midian, kaba ka para jaid jong ki, ïa kaba la pynïap ha kata ka sngi ka jingïapthem kaba namar u Peor.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, hadien kata kaba ïapthem, ba u la kren U Trai ha u Moses, bad ha u Eleasar u khun u Aaron lyngdoh, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To shim ïa ka jingkheiñ ïa u paidbah baroh ki khun Israel, naduh uba arphew snem ka rta bad tam, ha ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, uwei uwei baroh kat uba lah ban leit ïaleh thma ha Israel.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh, ki la kren ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab hajan ka Jordan, ha marpyrshah ka Jerikho, ki da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “To ñiew ïa ki briew, naduh uba arphew snem ka rta bad tam;” kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses, bad ïa ki khun Israel, kiba la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Reuben, u khun nyngkong u Israel: ki khun u Reuben; na u Hanokh la mih ka ïing ki Hanokh; na u Phalu, ka ïing ki Phalu;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na u Hesron, ka ïing ki Hesron; na u Karmi, ka ïing ki Karmi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kine ki kur ki Reuben: te kita ïa kiba la ñiew na ki, ki la long sawphew lai hajar hynñiewspah laiphew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Phalu: u Eliab.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Eliab: u Nemuel, bad u Dathan, bad u Abiram. Kine ki long uta u Dathan, bad uta u Abiram, kiba la donnam hapdeng uta u paidlang, bad kiba la ïaleh pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad pyrshah ïa u Aaron, ha ka jingïalang u Korah, haba ki la ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ka khyndew ka la ang ïa la ka shyntur, bad ka la nguid tylli noh ïa ki, lem bad u Korah ruh, haba uta u paidbah u la ïap; ha ka por ba ka ding ka la bam duh ïa arspah sanphew ngut ki briew, te ki la jia long ka dak.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ki khun u Korah kim shym la ïap.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Simeon katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Nemuel, ka ïing ki Nemuel; na u Jamin, ka ïing ki Jamin; na u Jakhin, ka ïing ki Jakhin;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na u Serah, ka ïing ki Serah; na u Shaul, ka ïing ki Shaul.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Simeon, arphew ar hajar arspah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun u Gad katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Sephon, ka ïing ki Sephon; na u Haggi, ka ïing ki Haggi; na u Shuni, ka ïing ki Shuni;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na u Osni, ka ïing ki Osni; na u Eri, ka ïing ki Eri;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na u Arod, ka ïing ki Arodi; na u Areli, ka ïing ki Areli.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kine ki ïing ki khun u Gad kumba la ñiew ïa ki, sawphew hajar sanspah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Judah: u Err, bad u Onan; te u Err, bad u Onan, ki la ïap ha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Judah katba kum ki ïing jong ki, ki la long: na u Shelah, ka ïing ki Shelah; na u Phares, ka ïing ki Phares; na u Serah, ka ïing ki Serah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Phares ki la long: na u Hesron, ka ïing ki Hesron; na u Hamul, ka ïing ki Hamul.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Judah kumba la ñiew ïa ki, hynñiewphew hynriew hajar sanspah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ki khun shynrang u Issakhar katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Tola, ka ïing ki Tola; na u Puah, ka ïing ki Puah;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na u Jashub, ka ïing ki Jashub; na u Shimron, ka ïing ki Shimron.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Issakhar kumba la ñiew ïa ki, hynriewphew saw hajar laispah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Sabulon, katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Sered, ka ïing ki Sered; na u Elon, ka ïing ki Elon; na u Jahlil, ka ïing ki Jahlil.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Sabulon kumba la ñiew ïa ki, hynriewphew hajar sanspah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Joseph katba kum ki ïing jong ki: u Manasseh, bad u Ephraim.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Manasseh: na u Makhir, ka ïing ki Makhir; u Makhir te u la pynkha ïa u Gilead; na u Gilead, ka ïing ki Gilead.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kine ki khun shynrang u Gilead: na u Jeeser, ka ïing ki Jeeser; na u Helek, ka ïing ki Helek;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad na u Asriel, ka ïing ki Asriel; bad na u Shekhem, ka ïing ki Shekhem;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad na u Shemida, ka ïing ki Shemida; bad na u Hepher, ka ïing ki Hepher.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Selophehad u khun u Hepher, um shym la don ki khun shynrang, tang ki khun kynthei: te ki kyrteng ki khun kynthei ki jong u Selophehad ki la long “ka Mahlah”, “ka Noah”, “ka Hoglah”, “ka Milkah”, bad “ka Tirsah”.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Manasseh: bad kita ïa kiba la ñiew na ki, ki la long sanphew ar hajar hynñiewspah.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kine ki khun shynrang u Ephraim katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Shuthelah, ka ïing ki Shuthelah; na u Bekher, ka ïing ki Bekher; na u Tahan, ka ïing ki Tahan.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad kine ki khun shynrang u Shuthelah: na u Eran, ka ïing ki Eran.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kine ki ïing ki khun shynrang u Ephraim katba kum kita ïa kiba la ñiew ha ki, laiphew ar hajar sanspah. Kine ki khun shynrang u Joseph katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Benjamin katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Bela, ka ïing ki Bela; na u Ashbel, ka ïing ki Ashbel; na u Ahiram, ka ïing ki Ahiram;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> na u Shupham, ka ïing ki Shupham; na u Hupham, ka ïing ki Hupham.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Bela ki la long u Ard, bad u Naaman: na u Ard, ka ïing ki Ardi; na u Naaman, ka ïing ki Naaman.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kine ki khun shynrang u Benjamin katba kum ki ïing jong ki: te kita ïa kiba la ñiew na ki, ki la long sawphew san hajar hynriewspah.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kine ki khun shynrang u Dan katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Shuham, ka ïing ki Shuham. Kine ki ïing ki Dan katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Baroh ki ïing ki Shuham, katba kum kita ïa kiba la ñiew na ki, ki la long hynriewphew saw hajar sawspah.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Asher katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Jimnah, ka ïing ki Jimnah; na u Jesui, ka ïing ki Jesui; na u Beriah, ka ïing ki Beriah.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na ki khun shynrang u Beriah: na u Heber, ka ïing ki Heber; na u Malkhiel, ka ïing ki Malkhiel.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka khun ka jong u Asher, ka la long “ka Sara.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Kine ki ïing ki khun shynrang u Asher katba kum kita ïa kiba la ñiew ha ki, sanphew lai hajar sawspah.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Naphtali katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Jahsil, ka ïing ki Jahsil; na u Guni, ka ïing ki Guni;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> na u Jeser, ka ïing ki Jeser; na u Shillem, ka ïing ki Shillem.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Naphtali katba kum ki ïing jong ki: te kita ïa kiba la ñiew ha ki, ki la long sawphew san hajar sawspah.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Kine keiñ ki la long ïa kiba la ñiew na ki khun Israel, hynriewspah hajar bad shi hajar hynñiewspah laiphew.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> “Ha kine yn pynïasam ïa ka khyndew ban long ka jingïoh pateng katba shong ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng jong ki.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Ha kiba bun, men ai ïa ka bynta pateng kaba kham khraw, bad ha kiba khyndiat, men kham pynduna ïa ka bynta pateng: ha uwei uwei baroh, yn ai ïa ka bynta pateng katba shong kita ïa kiba la kheiñ jong u.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Pynban, ïa ka khyndew yn sam da ka jingkhalai: katba kum ki kyrteng jong ki jaid ki kpa jong ki, kin ïoh bynta pateng.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Katba hap kata ka jingkhalai, yn sam ïa ka bynta pateng jong u hapdeng kiba bun bad kiba khyndiat.”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Te kine, ki long kita ïa kiba la kheiñ na ki Lebi katba kum ki ïing jong ki: na u Gershon, ka ïing ki Gershon; na u Kohath, ka ïing ki Kohath; na u Merari, ka ïing ki Merari.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Kine ki ïing ki Lebi: ka ïing jong ki Libni, ka ïing jong ki Hebron, ka ïing jong ki Mahli, ka ïing jong ki Mushi, ka ïing jong ki Korah. Te u Kohath u la pynkha ïa u Amram.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka tnga u Amram ka la long “ka Jokhebed”, ka khun u Lebi, ïa kaba la kha ha u Lebi ha ka ri Ijipt: ka te ka la kha ha u Amram ïa u Aaron, bad ïa u Moses, bad ïa ka Miriam ka hynmen jong ki.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Te ha u Aaron la kha ïa u Nadab, bad ïa u Abihu, ïa u Eleasar, bad ïa u Ithamar.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Te u Nadab, bad u Abihu ki la ïap, mynba ki la ainguh da ka ding bakhyllah ha khmat U Trai.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Te kita ïa kiba la ñiew na ki, ki la long arphew lai hajar, ki shynrang baroh, naduh uba shi bnai ka rta bad tam: namar ym shym la ñiew ïa ki hapdeng ki khun Israel, namar ba ym shym la lah ai ïa ka bynta pateng ha ki hapdeng ki khun Israel.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba la ñiew da u Moses, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh; kiba la ñiew ïa ki khun Israel ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, hajan ka Jordan, ha marpyrshah ka Jerikho.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Hynrei, hapdeng kine, ym don uwei na kita ïa kiba la ñiew u Moses, bad u Aaron lyngdoh; kiba la ñiew ïa ki khun Israel ha ka ri khlaw Sinai.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Naba U Trai u la lah ong shaphang jong ki, “Da kaba ïap kin ïap shisha ha kata ka ri khlaw.” Te lait na u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun, ym don uwei na ki, ïa uba la pynsah."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la wan ki khun kynthei ki jong u Selophehad, uba u khun u Hepher, uba u khun u Gilead, uba u khun u Makhir, uba u khun u Manasseh, na ki kur u Manasseh u khun u Joseph: te kine ki kyrteng ki khun kynthei jong u: “ka Mahlah”, “ka Noah”, “ka Hoglah”, “ka Milkah”, bad “ka Tirsah”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki la ïeng ha khmat u Moses, bad ha khmat u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha khmat ki rangbah, bad ki paidlang baroh, ha phyllaw Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ki da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “U kpa jong ngi u la ïap ha ka ri khlaw, te um shym la don ha kata ka jingïalang jong kita kiba la ïalum lang pyrshah ïa U Trai, ha ka jingïalang u Korah: hynrei, u la ïap ha la ka jong ka pop; bad um shym la don ki khun shynrang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te namar ba um shym la don khun shynrang, balei ba yn pyndam ïa ka kyrteng u kpa jong ngi napdeng ki kur jong u? To ai te ïa ka bynta trai ha ngi hapdeng ki para u kpa jong ngi.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Moses u la wallam ïa ka jingdawa jong ki ha khmat U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ki khun kynthei jong u Selophehad ki ïakren hok keiñ: ka dei ba men ai ïa ka bynta trai, ban long ka jingïoh pateng jong ki hapdeng ki para u kpa jong ki; te men pynai pateng ha ki, ïa ka bynta trai u kpa jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To kren ruh ha ki khun Israel da kaba ong, ‘Haba uno uno ruh u ïap, khlem khun shynrang, te phin pynai pateng ha ka khun kynthei jong u, ïa ka bynta trai jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad lada um don khun kynthei ruh, te phin ai ïa ka bynta trai jong u ha ki para jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te lada um don para ruh, te phin ai ïa ka bynta trai jong u ha ki para u kpa jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad lada ym don ki para ïa u kpa jong u ruh, te phin ai ïa ka bynta trai jong u ha u para kur jong u, uba bud na ka ïing jong u, te uta un ïoh pateng ïa ka: kane ruh kan long ka hukum ka jingbishar ha ki khun Israel, kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To leit kiew sha une u lum Abarim, to jngoh ruh la ka ri ïa kaba nga la ai ha ki khun Israel.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda me la ïohi ïa ka, yn buh lang ïa me ruh bad la ki briew, kumba la buh lang ruh ïa u Aaron u hynmen jong me:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba ha ka ri khlaw Sin, ha kata ka jingïakhñium u paidlang, phi la ïaleh kiat pyrshah ïa ka hukum jong nga, ïa ka ban pyndonburom ïa nga ha khmat jong ki hajan kata ka um.” (Kata, long ka um Meribah ha Kadesh keiñ kaba ha ka ri khlaw Sin.)",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Moses u la kren ha U Trai, u da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ai ba U Trai, uba U Blei ki mynsiem ka doh baroh, un thung da u briew halor une u paidlang,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> u ban leit shabar ha shuwa jong ki, bad u ban wan shapoh ha shuwa jong ki, bad uba lah ban ïalam shabar ïa ki, bad uba lah ban ïalam shapoh ïa ki; ba u paidlang jong U Trai un ym long kum ki langbrot ki bymdon u nongsharai.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To shim ha me ïa u Joshua u khun u Nun, u briew ha uba don uta u mynsiem, bad men buh ïa la ka kti halor jong u;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> to buh ruh ïa u ha khmat u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha khmat u paidlang baroh; bad men ai ka hukum ha u ha khmat jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Men ai ruh na ka burom jong me hi halor jong u, ba u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel kin kohnguh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te un ïeng ha khmat u Eleasar lyngdoh, u ban ïakylli na ka bynta jong u, katba kum ka jingbishar ki Urim ha khmat U Trai: da ka ktien jong u, kin ïamih noh shabar, bad da ka ktien jong u, kin ïawan shapoh, ma u, bad ki khun Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, bad u paidlang baroh ruh de.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Moses u la leh kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u: bad u la shim ïa u Joshua, bad u la pynïeng ïa u ha khmat u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha khmat u paidlang baroh de:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u la buh ïa la ki kti halor jong u, bad u la ai ka hukum ha u, kumba u la ong U Trai da ka kti u Moses."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To hukum ïa ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ïa ki, ‘Ïa ka jingainguh jong nga, ïa ka jingbam jong nga, ïa ki jingkñia kiba da ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha nga, to phin sumar ban ainguh ha nga ha ka aïom ïa kaba la buh.’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Men ong ruh ha ki, ‘Kata ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding ïa kaba phin ainguh ha U Trai, ka dei kane: ar tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem kiba khlem thohbria, ha la ka sngi, ban long ka jingainguh thang baïailong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ïa uwei u khun langbrot men ainguh mynstep, bad ïa uta uwei pat u khun langbrot de men ainguh janmiet;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ban long ka jingainguh bam, shi bynta na kaba shiphew na ka shi ephah u 'purew, ïa kaba la khleh bad shi pawa hin ka umphniang ba la tylliat.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kane ka long ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud, ïa kaba la buh ha u lum Sinai, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih, ka jingkñia keiñ kaba da ka ding ha U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka jingainguh dih jong ka, kan long shi pawa hin, lem bad uwei uwei u khun langbrot: men pyntheh ha ka jaka kyntang ïa ka Waiñ ka babha, ban long ka jingainguh dih ha U Trai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ïa uta uwei pat u khun langbrot, men ainguh janmiet: kum kata ka jingainguh bam mynstep, bad kata ka jingainguh dih jong ka, men ainguh ïa ka, ban long ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding, ka jingiw baiwbih keiñ ha U Trai.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Te ha ka sngi Sabbaton, ar tylli ki khun langbrot ki bajanai bha kiba shi snem, bad ar bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew, ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam, lem bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kane te ka jingainguh thang man ka Sabbaton, nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Ha kaba sdang ki bnai jong phi ruh, phin ainguh ïa ka ban long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai; da ar tylli ki masi lyngraw, bad uwei u langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki bajanai bha ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad lai bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew, ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam lem bad uwei uwei u masi lyngraw; bad ar bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew, ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam, lem bad uwei uwei u langbrot;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad shi bynta na kaba shiphew u 'purew, ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, ban long ka jingainguh bam, lem bad uwei uwei u khun langbrot; ïa ka ban long ka jingainguh thang baiwbih, namar ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding ha U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long shiteng hin ka Waiñ ïa uwei uwei u masi lyngraw, bad shi bynta na kaba lai hin ïa uwei uwei u langbrot, bad shi pawa hin ïa uwei uwei u khun langbrot: kane ka long ka jingainguh thang jong uwei uwei u bnai lyngba ïa ki bnai jong ka snem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud, yn ainguh da uwei u khun blang, lem bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop ha U Trai.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Te ha ka bakhatsaw sngi na u bnai banyngkong, ka long Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ka jong U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ha ka bakhatsan sngi na une u bnai kan long Ka Jingkhawai Niam: hynñiew sngi yn bam ïa U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha ka sngi banyngkong, kan long ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang, phi wat trei ïa ka kam shakri satia:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, phin ainguh da ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding, ban long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai; ai ar tylli ki masi lyngraw, bad ïa uwei u langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem: ïa kine phi dei ban ïoh ki bajanai bha:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka jingainguh bam jong ki kan long u 'purew ba la ïakhleh da ka umphniang; lai bynta na kaba shiphew, phin ainguh bad uwei u masi lyngraw, bad ar bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei u langbrot;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> shi bynta na kaba shiphew, phin ainguh bad uwei uwei u khun langbrot, na kita ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop, ïa ka ban pynlong ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta jong phi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa kine, phin ainguh keiñ nalor kata ka jingainguh thang mynstep, kaba long ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Da kane ka rukom, phin ainguh ha la ka sngi, baroh hynñiew sngi, da ka jingkñia bam kaba da ka ding, ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai: nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud, phin ainguh ïa ka, lem bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha ka sngi bahynñiew, kan long ha phi ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang; phi wat trei ïa ka kam shakri satia.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ki soh nyngkong jong phi ruh, haba phi ainguh da ka jingainguh bam ka bathymmai ha U Trai ynda la lah ki taïew jong phi, kan long ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang ha phi; phi wat trei ïa ka kam shakri satia:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> hynrei, phin ainguh da ar tylli ki masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem, ban long ka jingainguh thang baiwbih ha U Trai;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> te ka jingainguh bam jong ki kaba da u 'purew ïa kaba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, kan long lai bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u masi lyngraw, ar bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u langbrot,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> shi bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u khun langbrot na kita ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> uwei u khun blang, ïa ka ban pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta jong phi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba khlem da pud, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, phin ainguh da kine (ai ba phin ïoh da ki bajanai bha keiñ), lem bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki.”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Bad ha u bnai u bahynñiew, ha ka sngi ka banyngkong uta u bnai, kan long ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang ha phi; wat trei ei ei ruh ka kam shakri satia: kan long ka sngi ïa ka ban put ki ronsing ha phi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te phin ainguh da ka jingainguh thang, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai; ïa uwei u masi lyngraw, ïa uwei u langbrot, bad ïa hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka jingainguh bam jong ki ruh kan long u 'purew ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, lai bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei u masi dab, ar bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei u langbrot,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad shi bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u khun langbrot na kita ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad uwei u khun blang, ban long ki jingkñia sait pop, ïa ka ban pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta jong phi:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nalor ka jingainguh thang ka jong u bnai, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki de, ha la ki rukom rukom, namar ka jingiw baiwbih, ban long ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding ha U Trai.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi bashiphew une u bnai bahynñiew, kan long ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang ha phi; te phin pynshitom ïa la ki mynsiem; wat trei shuh ïa ka kam ei ei ruh ha ka:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> hynrei, phin ainguh da ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai ban long ka jingiw baiwbih: ïa uwei u masi lyngraw, ïa uwei u langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem; to ai phin ïoh ïa ki, ki bajanai bha keiñ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> te ka jingainguh bam jong ki, kan long u 'purew ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, lai bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei u masi dab, ar bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei u langbrot,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad shi bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u khun langbrot na kita ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingkñia sait pop ka jingpynïasuk, bad kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ka bakhatsan jong uta u bnai bahynñiew, kan long ka jingïaseng ka bakyntang ha phi; wat trei ei ei ka kam shakri satia: hynrei phin ïarakhe Ka Jingkhawai Niam ha U Trai, hynñiew sngi:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> te phin ainguh da ka jingainguh thang, ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai; khatlai tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki 'lang shynrang, khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem; ai kin long ki bajanai bha keiñ:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki, kan long u 'purew ba la ïakhleh bad ka umphniang, lai bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u masi na kita ki khatlai tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u langbrot na kita ki ar tylli ki langbrot shynrang,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad shi bynta na kaba shiphew, ïa uwei uwei u khun langbrot na kita ki khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, phin ainguh ïa khat-ar tylli ki masi lyngraw, ïa ar tylli ki lang shynrang, ïa khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> te ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki 'lang shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot de, katba kum ka rukom jong ki:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki de.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ka balai, khatwei tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki lang shynrang, bad khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem ki bajanai bha;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> te ki jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki 'lang shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka de.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ka basaw, shiphew tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki lang shynrang, khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki 'lang shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad uwei u khun blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka de.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Bad ha ka sngi ka basan, khyndai tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki 'lang shynrang, bad khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki 'lang shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot de, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Te ha ka sngi ka bahynriew, phra tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki lang shynrang, bad khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki langbrot shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Te ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, hynñiew tylli ki masi lyngraw, ar tylli ki 'lang shynrang, bad khatsaw tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa ki masi lyngraw, ïa ki 'lang shynrang, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Te ha ka sngi ka baphra, kan long Ka Jingkhawai Niam ka bakyntang ha phi: wat trei ei ei ruh ka kam shakri ha ka:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> hynrei, phin ainguh da ka jingainguh thang, ka jingkñia kaba da ka ding, ban long ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai: uwei u masi lyngraw, uwei u langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot ba shi snem ki bajanai bha:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, kin long katba shong ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ïa u masi lyngraw, ïa u langbrot, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, katba kum ka rukom:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad uwei u blang, ban long ka jingkñia sait pop; nalor kata ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ka, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ka.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Ïa kine phin ainguh keiñ ha U Trai ha kita Ki Jingkhawai Niam jong phi, nalor ki jingkular skhem jong phi, bad ki jingainguh sngewbha jong phi, ban long ki jingainguh thang jong phi, bad ki jingainguh bam jong phi, bad ki jingainguh dih jong phi, bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk jong phi.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u Moses u la ïathuh ha ki khun Israel ïa baroh kat kiba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Moses u la kren ha ki rangbah ki jaid Israel, u da ong, “Ka long kane ba u la hukum U Trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ‘Lada u briew un kular ïa ka jingkular skhem ha U Trai, lane un smai ïa ka jingsmai, ban teh ïa la ka mynsiem da ka jingteh, wat ai ba un pynkheiñ ïa kata ka ktien jong u: to un pyndep noh ïa baroh katba kum ba-mih noh na ka shyntur jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad lada ka kynthei kan kular ïa ka jingkular skhem ha U Trai, bad ba ka la teh ïa lade da ka jingteh ha ïing u kpa jong ka, haba ka dang khynraw;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te lada u kpa jong ka, u ïohsngew ïa kata ka jingkular skhem, bad ïa kata ka jingteh jong ka, da kaba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem, bad ba u un sngap jar ruh ha ka: te kumta, ki jingkular skhem jong ka baroh, kin neh, bad ki jingteh baroh da kiba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem, kin neh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, lada u kpa jong ka um shah ïa ka ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u ïohsngew; te na kita ki jingkular skhem jong ka baroh, bad na kita ki jingteh da kiba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem, kawei ruh em kan ym neh: te U Trai un map ïa ka, namar ba u kpa jong ka, um shah shuh ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad lada ka la don tnga, mynba ka la don la ki jingkular skhem halor jong ka, lane mynba ka la kren ei ei ruh na ki rmiang shyntur jong ka da kaba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> te lada u la ïohsngew u tnga jong ka, bad u sngap jar ruh ha ka ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u la ïohsngew: ki jingkular skhem jong ka kin neh, bad kita ki jingteh da kiba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem, kin neh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, lada u tnga jong ka um da shah ïa ka ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u la ïohsngew; te un pyndam noh ïa ka jingkular jong ka ïa kaba ka la kular skhem, bad ïa kata kaba ka la kren da la ki rmiang shyntur da kaba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem: U Trai ruh un map ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, ka jingkular skhem baroh ka jong ka riewkynthei, bad ka jong kaba la iehnoh tnga ruh, da kaba ki la teh ïa la ki mynsiem, kan ïaineh keiñ halor jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, lada ka dei ha ïing u tnga jong ka, ba ka la kular skhem, lane ka la teh ïa ka jingkular da ka jingsmai halor ka mynsiem jong ka,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad haba u la ïohsngew u tnga, bad u sngap jar, bad u shah ruh ïa ka; te kumta, ki jingkular skhem jong ka baroh, kin ïaineh, bad ki jingteh baroh da kiba ka la teh ïa la ka mynsiem, kin ïaineh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, lada u tnga jong ka, u la pyndam noh khoit ïa ki ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u la ïohsngew ïa ki; te kan ym neh ei ei ruh na kiba la mih noh na ki rmiang shyntur jong ka, na ki jingkular skhem jong ka, lane na ki jingteh ka mynsiem jong ka; u tnga jong ka u la pyndam noh ïa ki; bad U Trai un map ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka jingkular skhem baroh, bad ka jingteh baroh da kaba smai, ïa ka ban pynshitom ïa ka mynsiem, u tnga jong ka u lah ban pynskhem ïa ka, bad u tnga jong ka u lah ban pyndam noh ruh ïa ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, lada u tnga jong ka un nang sngap jar hi ha ka man la ka sngi; te kumta, u la pynskhem ïa ki jingkular skhem jong ka baroh, bad ïa ki jingteh jong ka baroh kiba la don ha ka: u la pynskhem keiñ ïa ki, da kaba u la sngap jar ha ka ha kata ka sngi ha kaba u la ïohsngew ïa ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, lada kumno kumno ruh un pyndam noh ïa ki ynda u la lah ïohsngew ïa ki; te kumta, un kit ma u ïa ka pop jong ka.’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kine kita ki hukum, ïa kiba la hukum U Trai ha u Moses, hapdeng u tnga bad ka tnga jong u, bad hapdeng u kpa bad ka khun jong u, mynba ka dang khynraw, ha ïing u kpa jong ka."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To pynhiar kput halor ki Midian na ka bynta ki khun Israel: hadien kata, yn ïalum lang ïa me ha ki briew jong me.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Moses te u la kren ha uta u paidbah, u da ong, “To kieng atiar ïa ki rangbah napdeng jong phi ïa ka ban ïaleh thma, te kin mih ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki Midian, ïa ka ban pynhiar kput halor kita ki Midian na ka bynta U Trai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Phin phah shi hajar hajar shi jaid, na ki jaid Israel baroh, sha kata ka jaka thma.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, la pynmih noh na ki hajar Israel, shi hajar hajar na shi jaid baroh, khat-ar hajar keiñ kiba la kieng atiar ïa kata ka thma.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses u la phah noh ïa ki sha kata ka thma, shi hajar hajar na shi jaid baroh, ïa ki bad u Phinehas u khun u Eleasar lyngdoh, sha kata ka thma, lem bad ki jingbuh ki bakyntang, bad ki ronsing ban put ha ka kti jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Midian, kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses; bad ki la pynïap ïa ki shynrang baroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad nalor kita kiwei ïa kiba la pynïap, ki la pynïap ruh ïa ki syiem ki Midian: ïa u Ebi, bad ïa u Rekem, bad ïa u Sur, bad ïa u Hur, bad ïa u Reba, san ngut ki syiem ki Midian: ïa u Balaam ruh u khun u Beor, ki la pynïap da ka waitlam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki khun Israel ki la kem mraw ruh ïa ki kynthei ki Midian, bad ïa ki khun khynnah jong ki; ki la lute ruh ïa ki jingri jong ki baroh, bad ïa ki kynhun jong ki baroh, bad ïa ki spah jong ki baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ïa ki nongbah jong ki baroh ruh ha kiba ki la ïashong sah, bad ïa ki kut skhem baroh jong ki, ki la thang da ka ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ki la shim ïa ka jingkurup baroh, bad ïa ka jinglute baroh, kita kiba na ki briew, bad na ki jingri ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la ïawallam ïa kiba la kem mraw, bad ïa kita ki jinglute, bad ïa kata ka jingkurup, ha u Moses, bad ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha u paidlang ki khun Israel, ha ka jaka shong dara kaba ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, kiba hajan ka Jordan marpyrshah ka Jerikho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ki rangbah baroh jong u paidlang, ki la ïamih noh ban leit tan ïa ki shabar ka jaka shong dara.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Moses u la sngewbitar eh ïa ki rangbah ki nongïapom, ïa ki rangbah ki hajar, bad ïa ki rangbah ki spah, kiba la ïawan phai na kata ka jingïaleh thma.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Moses u la ong ruh ha ki, “Hato phi la ri pynim ïa ki kynthei baroh?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha khmih, ki dei kine, da ka buit u Balaam, kiba la pynwan ïa ki khun Israel ïa ka ban leh palat ïa U Trai shaphang u Peor, bad ba la don ka jingïapthem hapdeng u paidlang jong U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mynta te, namar kata, to pynïap noh ïa ki khynnah shynrang baroh, bad to pynïap noh ruh ïa ki kynthei baroh kiba la ïa-ithuh ïa u briew da kaba ki la thiah bad u shynrang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki khynnah kynthei baroh, ki bym shym la ïa-ithuh ïa u briew, phin ri pynim na ka bynta ïa lade.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Phi te phin ïashong shabar ka jaka shong dara, hynñiew sngi: jar uba la pynïap ïa u briew, bad jar uba la ktah ïa uba la ïap, to phin pynkhuid ïa lade, bad ïa kiba la kem mraw jong phi, ha ka sngi ka balai, bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ïa ki jaiñ ruh baroh, bad ïa ki jingdiang snieh baroh, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba la thaw da ki 'ñiuh blang, bad ïa ki khiew dieng baroh, to phin pynkhuid keiñ.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Eleasar lyngdoh u la ong de ha kita ki nongïapom, kiba la leit sha kata ka jingïaleh thma, “Kane ka long ka rukom jong kata ka hukum ïa kaba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> tang ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ka rupa, ïa ka rnong, ïa u nar, ïa ka sador, bad ïa ka sisa,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ïa kaei kaei baroh keiñ kaba lah ban shah ding, phin syaw ha ka ding, te kan long bakhuid; pynban, yn pynkhuid ïa ka da ka um ka jingpynkyntang: te ïa kiei kiei baroh ki bym shah ding, phin pynïaid lyngba ïa ka um.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad phin sait ïa la ki jaiñ ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, te phin long ba khuid, hadien kata ruh phin ïoh rung hapoh ka jaka shong dara.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “To shim ka jingkheiñ jong ki jinglute ba la shim, kita kiba na jong ki briew, bad na jong ki jingri, ma me, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ki tymmen ki san jong uta u paidlang:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> te phin ïasam marshiteng ïa ka jinglute: hapdeng kita ki nongïapom, kiba la leit ha kata ka thma, bad hapdeng u paidlang baroh:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad men shim khrong ïa U Trai na kita ki nongïapom kiba la leit ha kata ka thma: ïa kawei ka mynsiem napdeng sanspah, kata, na kita ki briew, bad na kita ki masi dab, bad na kita ki kadda, bad na kita ki langbrot:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> katta keiñ phin shim na kaba shiteng jong ki, phin ai ruh ïa ka ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, ïa ka ban long ka jingainguh kyntiew ha U Trai.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad na kaba shiteng jong ki khun Israel, phin shim shi bynta na kiba sanphew, na kita ki briew, bad na kita ki masi dab, bad na kita ki kadda, bad na kita ki blang, bad na ki jaid baroh ki jingri, bad phin ai ïa ki ha ki Lebi kiba ap khmih ïa ka jingsumar Ka Tabernakl jong U Trai.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh, ki la leh kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad kata ka jinglute, kata kaba dang sah na ka jinglute ïa kaba kita ki nongïapom ki la lah wan kem, ka la long hynriewspah bad hynñiewphew san hajar ki langbrot,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad hynñiewphew ar hajar ki masi dab,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad hynriewphew wei hajar ki kadda,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> na ki briew ruh, kata, na ki kynthei ki bym shym la ïa-ithuh ïa u briew da kaba thiah lem bad u, laiphew ar hajar ki mynsiem.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te kata kaba shiteng, kata ka bynta jong kita kiba la ïaleit sha kata ka thma, ka la don ha ka jingkheiñ, laispah bad laiphew hynñiew hajar sanspah ki langbrot:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ka khrong ka jong U Trai, ka la long na kita ki langbrot, hynriewspah hynñiewphew san.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad kita ki masi dab la don laiphew hynriew hajar; na kita, ka khrong ka jong U Trai ka la long hynñiewphew ar tylli.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad kita ki kadda la don laiphew hajar sanspah; na kita, ka khrong ka jong U Trai ka la long hynriewphew wei.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad kita ki briew la don khathynriew hajar; na kita, ka khrong ka jong U Trai ka la long laiphew ar ngut ki mynsiem.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Moses u la aiti ïa kata ka khrong, ka jingainguh kyntiew ka jong U Trai, ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, kumba u la hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te na kata ka shiteng bynta jong ki khun Israel ruh, ïa kaba u Moses, u la pynkyrpang na kita ki nongïapom,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> (te kata ka shiteng kaba la dei ha uta u paidlang na ki langbrot, ki la don laispah laiphew hynñiew hajar sanspah,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad na ki masi dab, laiphew hynriew hajar;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> bad na ki kadda, laiphew hajar sanspah,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> bad na ki briew de, khathynriew hajar);",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> wat na kata ka shiteng keiñ ka jong ki khun Israel, u Moses u la shim shi bynta na kaba sanphew, kata, na kita ki briew, bad na kita ki jingri, bad u la aiti ïa ki ha ki Lebi, kiba la khmih ïa ka jingsumar Ka Tabernakl U Trai; kumba u la lah hukum U Trai ïa u Moses.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te kita ki nongïalam, kiba halor ki hajar kita ki nongïapom, kita ki rangbah ki hajar, bad ki rangbah ki spah, ki la ïawan ha u Moses:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad ki la ïa-ong ha u Moses, “Ki shakri jong me ki la shim ïa ka jingkheiñ ïa kita ki nongïapom kiba hapoh ka jingsumar jong ngi, te na ngi, ym don uwei u briew ba la duna.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Namar kata, ngi la wallam ka jingainguh ha U Trai, uwei uwei kat kiba u la ïoh, na ki jingdeng ksiar, na ki kynjri, ki syngkha, ki sa'ti, ki sohshkor, bad ki 'pieng ksiar, ban pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta ki mynsiem jong ngi ha khmat U Trai.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te u Moses, bad u Eleasar lyngdoh, ki la shim na ki ïa ka ksiar, kata, ki jingdeng keiñ ba la thaw baroh.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad kata ka ksiar baroh ka jong ka jingainguh kyntiew, ïa kaba ki la ainguh ha U Trai, na kita ki rangbah ki hajar, bad na kita ki rangbah ki spah, ka la long khathynriew hajar bad hynñiewspah sanphew shekel.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> (Namar kita ki nongïapom ki la lute, uwei uwei baroh na ka bynta ïa lade.)",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te u Moses bad u Eleasar lyngdoh ki la shim ïa kata ka ksiar jong kita ki rangbah ki hajar, bad ka jong kita ki rangbah ki spah, ki la ïawallam ruh ïa ka ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ïa ka ban long ka jingpynkynmaw na ka bynta ki khun Israel ha khmat U Trai."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun u Reuben, bad ki khun u Gad, ki la don shikatdei eh ki jingri: bad haba ki la ïohi ïa ka ri Jaser, bad ïa ka ri Gilead, te ha khmih, kata ka jaka ka la long ka jaka ïa ki jingri;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> te ki khun u Gad, bad ki khun u Reuben, ki la ïawan, bad ki la ïakren ha u Moses, bad ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha ki rangbah jong uta u paidlang, ki da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ka Ataroth, bad ka Dibon, bad ka Jaser, bad ka Nimrah, bad ka Heshbon, bad ka Elealeh, bad ka Shebam, bad ka Nebo, bad ka Beon,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> kata ka ri keiñ ïa kaba U Trai u la jop ha khmat u paidlang ki Israel, ka long ka ri ïa ki jingri, te ki shakri jong me ki don ki jingri.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, ki la ïa-ong, “Lada me la sngewsynei ïa ngi, to pynai ïa kane ka ri ha ki shakri jong me ïa ka ban long ka bynta trai; te to wat ïalam ïa ngi sha shiliang ka Jordan.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha ki khun u Gad, bad ha ki khun u Reuben, “Haba ki para jong phi kin ïaleit ïaleh thma, ma phi te phin ïashong hangne mo?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te balei phin ïa-pynsyier ïa ki dohnud ki khun Israel ba kin ym leit sha shiliang sha kata ka ri ïa kaba u la aiti U Trai ha ki?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, kumne hi ki la leh ki kpa jong phi, mynba nga la phah ïa ki na Kadesh-barnea ïa ka ban jngoh ïa ka ri.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Naba haba ki la ïaleit kiew haduh ka them ka ri Eshkol, bad ki la ïohi ïa ka ri, ki la ïa-pynsyier ïa ka dohnud jong ki khun Israel, ba kin ym leit sha kata ka ri ïa kaba u la lah ai U Trai ha ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha kata ka por ruh, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep, bad u la smai, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ‘Shisha uwei na kita ki briew kiba la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt, naduh uba arphew snem ka rta bad tam, un ym ïohi ïa kata ka ri ïa kaba nga la kular da ka jingsmai ha u Abraham, ha u Isaak, bad ha u Jakob; naba kim shym la pynbiang ban bud ïa nga:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> lait na u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh uba u Kenis, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun: naba ki la pynbiang keiñ ban bud ïa U Trai.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep pyrshah ïa ki Israel, bad u la pynïaid kylleng la kylleng ïa ki ha kata ka ri khlaw sawphew snem, ha ban da la pynduh noh khoit ïa kata ka pateng bynriew baroh, kaba la leh sniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad, ha khmih, phi la mih joit ha ka jaka ki kpa jong phi, phi la man ki briew ki bapop, ïa ka ban nang pynkhraw ïa ka jingbitar barhem jong U Trai sha ki Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba lada phin phai noh na kaba bud ïa U, un iehnoh pat keiñ ïa ki briew ha kata ka ri khlaw; phi ruh phin pynjot noh ïa une u paidbah baroh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki la ïawan hajan jong u, bad ki la ong ruh, “Ngin shu thaw ïa ki jingker langbrot hangne ïa ki jingri jong ngi, bad ïa ki nongbah ïa ki khun khynnah jong ngi:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ngi hi ngin ïaleit kloi ba la kieng atiar ha khmat ki khun Israel, tad ynda ngi la wallam ïa ki ha ka jaka jong ki hi: te ki khun khynnah jong ngi, kin ïashongneh ha kita ki nongbah ïa kiba la ker kut namar ki trai-shnong jong kane ka ri.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngi, ngin ym leit phai pat sha ki ïing jong ngi, tad ynda ki khun Israel ki la ïoh bha uwei uwei baroh ïa la ka jingïoh pateng.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ngi ngin ym ïaïoh bynta trai ryngkat bad ki sha shiliang ka Jordan, lane sha lyndet; namar ka jingïoh pateng jong ngi ka la hap ha ngi sha kane ka liang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha ki, “Lada phin leh ïa kane; lada phin leit ba la kieng atiar ïa ka ban ïaleh thma ha khmat U Trai,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> lada phin ïaleit uwei uwei baroh ruh ba la kieng atiar sha shiliang ka Jordan ha khmat U Trai, tad ynda u la beh noh ïa ki nongshun jong u na khmat jong u,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ba la jop thiaw ïa kata ka ri ha khmat U Trai: te hadien kata, phin ïoh wan phai pat, bad phin long ruh kiba khlem pop ha khmat U Trai, bad ha khmat ki Israel; bad kane ka ri kan long ka bynta trai jong phi ha khmat U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, lada phin ym leh kumne, ha khmih, phi leh pop ïa U Trai: bad to tip skhem ruh ba ka pop jong phi kan lap ïa phi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> To phin tei ïa ki nongbah ïa ki khun khynnah jong phi, bad ïa ki jingker ïa ki langbrot jong phi; to leh ruh kat kumba la mih noh na ka shyntur jong phi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki khun u Gad, bad ki khun u Reuben, ki la ïakren ha u Moses, ki da ong, “Ki shakri jong me kin leh kumba u la hukum u kynrad jong ngi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki khun khynnah jong ngi, ki tnga jong ngi, ki kynhun jong ngi, bad ki jingri jong ngi baroh, kin ïashongneh hangne ha ki nongbah Gilead:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> hynrei, ki shakri jong me kin ïaleit sha shiliang, ha khmat U Trai sha ka thma, kiba la kieng atiar uwei uwei baroh, kumba u ong u kynrad jong ngi.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la hukum ïa u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ïa u Joshua u khun u Nun, bad ïa ki tymmen ki san jong ki jaid ki khun Israel, shaphang jong ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha ki, “Lada ki khun u Gad, bad ki khun u Reuben, kin ïaleit sha shiliang ka Jordan lem bad phi, uwei uwei baroh ba la kieng atiar sha ka thma, ha khmat U Trai, bad ba yn jop thiaw ïa ka ri ha khmat jong phi; te kumta, phin ai ïa ka ri Gilead ha ki, ban long ka bynta trai jong ki:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> hynrei, lada kin ym ïaleit sha shiliang ba la kieng atiar ryngkat bad phi, kin ïoh ïa ki bynta trai hapdeng jong phi ha ka ri Kanaan.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki khun u Gad, bad ki khun u Reuben, ki la ïathuh, ki da ong, “Kumba u la ong U Trai ha ki shakri jong me, kumta ngi ruh ngin leh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngin ïaleit keiñ sha shiliang sha ka ri Kanaan ha khmat U Trai ba la kieng atiar ïa ngi, bad ka hok ban ïoh ïa la ka bynta trai shaphang shane ïa ka Jordan kan ïoh long ka jong ngi.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Moses u la ai ha ki, kata ka long, ha ki khun u Gad, bad ha ki khun u Reuben, bad ha kaba shiteng na ka jaid u Manasseh u khun u Joseph, ïa ka hima u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, bad ïa ka hima u Og u syiem ka Bashan, ïa ka ri, bad ïa ki nongbah jong ka ha la ki phang, kita keiñ, ki nongbah jong kata ka ri baroh sawdong.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ki khun u Gad, ki la ïatei pat ïa ka Dibon, bad ïa ka Ataroth, bad ïa ka Aroer;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad ïa ka Atroth, ïa ka Shophan, bad ïa ka Jaser, bad ïa ka Jogbehah;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad ïa ka Beth-nimrah, bad ïa ka Beth-haran: ki nongbah ba la ker kynroh ïa ki, bad ïa ki jingker ïa ki langbrot.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad ki khun u Reuben, ki la ïatei pat ïa ka Heshbon, bad ïa ka Elealeh, bad ïa ka Kirjathaim:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ïa ka Nebo ruh, bad ïa ka Baal-meon (haba la pynkylla ïa ki kyrteng jong ki,) bad ïa ka Shibmah: te ki la khot kyrteng da kumwei ïa kita ki nongbah ïa kiba ki la ïatei pat.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te ki khun u Makhir u khun u Manasseh ki la ïaleit sha Gilead, bad ki la jop ïa ka, bad ki la beh noh ruh ïa ki Amor kiba shong ha kata.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u Moses u la ai ïa ka Gilead ha u Makhir u khun u Manasseh; te u la shongneh ruh ha ka.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> U Jair ruh u khun u Manasseh u la leit, bad u la jop ruh ïa ki nongrit jong ki, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ki, “Ki Haboth-Jair.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U Nobah ruh u la leit, bad u la jop ïa ka Kenath, bad ïa ki nongrit jong ka, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, da la ka jong ka kyrteng “Nobah”."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kine ki long ki jingleit ki khun Israel, kiba la ïamih noh na ka ri Ijipt, lem bad ki paidïapom jong ki da ka kti u Moses, bad u Aaron.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Moses u la thoh ïa ki jingmih noh jong ki katba kum ki jingleit jong ki da ka hukum U Trai; te kine ki long ki jingleit jong ki katba kum ki jingïaid noh jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Rameses ha u bnai u banyngkong, ha ka bakhatsan sngi uta u bnai banyngkong; ha ka sngi kaba bud, ha Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ki khun Israel ki la ïamih noh da ka kti ka badonbor ha kaba ïohi ki Ijipt baroh,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> namar kita ki Ijipt ki dang ïatep ïa ki khun nyngkong jong ki baroh, ïa kiba u la lah shoh U Trai hapdeng jong ki: bad U Trai u la buh ïa ki jingpynshitom halor ki blei jong ki ruh de.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïamih noh na Rameses, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Sukkoth.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Sukkoth, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Etham, kaba harud ka ri khlaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Etham, bad ki la ïaleit phai pat sha Pihahiroth, kaba ha khmat ka Baal-sephon: bad ki la ïashong dara ruh ha khmat ka Migdol.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na khmat ka Pihahiroth, bad ki la ïaid lyngba napdeng kata ka duriaw sha kata ka ri khlaw: bad ki la ïaleit lai sngi lynti ha ka ri khlaw Etham, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Marah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Marah, bad ki la ïapoi sha Elim: te ha Elim, la don khat-ar tylli ki umpohliew, bad hynñiewphew tylli ki dieng Tlai; te ki la ïashong dara hangta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Elim, bad ki la ïashong dara hajan ka Duriaw Basaw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na ka Duriaw Basaw, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ka ri khlaw Sin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na ka ri khlaw Sin, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Dophkah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Dophkah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Alush.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Alush, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Rephidim, ha kaba ym don um ïa ki briew ban dih.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Rephidim, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ka ri khlaw Sinai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na ka ri khlaw Sinai, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Kibroth-hattaabah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Kibroth-hattaabah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Haseroth.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Haseroth, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Rithmah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Rithmah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Rimmon-pares.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Rimmon-pares, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Libnah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Libnah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Rissah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Rissah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Kehelathah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Kehelathah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha u lum Shapher.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na u lum Shapher, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Haradah,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Haradah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Makheloth.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Makheloth, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Tahath.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Tahath, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Tarah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Tarah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Mithkah.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Mithkah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Hashmonah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Hashmonah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Moseroth.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Moseroth, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Bene-jaakan.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Bene-jaakan, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Hor-hagidgad.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Hor-hagidgad, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Jotbathah.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Jotbathah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Ebronah.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Ebronah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Esion-geber.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Esion-geber, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ka ri khlaw Sin, kaba long ka Kadesh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Kadesh, bad ki la ïashong dara ha u lum Hor, harud jong ka ri Edom.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Aaron lyngdoh, u la leit kiew ha u lum Hor da ka hukum U Trai, te hangta u la ïap, ha ka basawphew ka snem ynda ki khun Israel ki la ïawan mih noh na ka ri Ijipt, ha ka sngi ka banyngkong u bnai u basan.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Aaron u la don shispah arphew lai snem ka rta mynba u la ïap ha u lum Hor.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te u Arad syiem u kynja Kanaan, uba shong sah shaphang shathie ha ka ri Kanaan, u la ïohsngew shaphang ka jingwan ki khun Israel.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Hor, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Salmonah.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Salmonah, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Punon.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Punon, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Oboth.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Oboth, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Ije-abarim, ha khap ka ri Moab.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Iyim, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Dibon-gad.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Dibon-gad, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Almon-diblathaim.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na Almon-diblathaim, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ki lum Abarim, ha khmat u lum Nebo.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te ki la ïamih noh na ki lum Abarim, bad ki la ïashong dara ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, harud ka Jordan marpyrshah ka Jerikho.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te ki la ïashong dara harud ka Jordan, naduh Beth-jeshimoth jin haduh Abel-shittim ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, harud ka Jordan, marpyrshah ka Jerikho, U da ong,",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Ynda phi la ïaleit sha shiliang ka Jordan sha ka ri Kanaan,",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> te phin ïabeh noh ïa ki trai-shnong jong ka ri baroh ha shuwa jong phi, te phin ïa-pynjot noh ruh ïa ki dur baroh jong ki, bad ïa ki bleithaw ba la saiñ jong ki baroh ruh phin pynjot noh, bad phin ïa-pynduh noh khoit ïa kiei kiei ha ki jaka lum jong ki baroh:",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> bad phin ïaknieh kynthet ïa kata ka ri, bad phin ïashongneh ha ka: naba nga la aiti ïa kata ka ri ha phi, ba phin ïoh pateng ïa ka.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Bad phin ïasam ïa kata ka ri ïa ka ban long ka bynta pateng hapdeng ki kur jong phi da ka jingkhalai; te ha kiba kham bun, phin ai ka bynta pateng da kaba kham khraw, bad ha kiba kham khyndiat, phin ai ka bynta pateng da kaba kham rit: ka bynta pateng jong uwei uwei baroh kan long ha kata ka jaka ha kaba kan hap ka jingkhalai jong u; phin ïoh bynta pateng katba kum ki jaid ki kpa jong phi.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te lada phin ym beh noh ïa ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri ha shuwa jong phi; kan jia long, ba kita ïa kiba phin pynsah na ki, kin long ki shiah ha ki khmat jong phi, bad ki speh ha ki krung jong phi, bad kin ïa-pynshitom ruh ïa phi ha kata ka ri ha kaba phi ïashongneh.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Nalor kata ruh, kan jia long, ba ngan leh ïa phi, kumba nga la thew ban leh ïa ki.’ ”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To hukum ïa ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Ynda phi la poi ha ka ri Kanaan, (kane, ka long kata ka ri ka ban sa hap ha phi ïa ka ban long ka bynta pateng, kata ka long keiñ, ka ri Kanaan, bad ki rud jong ka,)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> te ka phang kaba shaphang shathie jong phi kan long naduh ka ri khlaw Sin ter ter, ryngkat bad ka pud ka ri Edom, bad ka pud ka bashathie jong phi kan long naduh ka rud ka bakut eh kata ka Duriaw Mluh shaphang mihngi:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ka pud jong phi, kan phai na shathie sha ka thiep Akrabbim, bad kan ïaid palat haduh Sin: bad ka jinglam noh jong ka, kan long na shathie haduh Kadesh-barnea; kan nang leit ruh haduh Hasar-addar, bad ïaid lyndet ruh haduh Asmon:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ka pud ruh kan phai sawdong na Asmon, jin haduh ka wah ka ri Ijipt, bad ka jingmih ka bakut jong ka kan long ha ka duriaw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “ ‘Te ban long pud kaba shaphang sepngi ha phi, kan long ka Duriaw Bakhraw; kane ka pud kan long ka pud sepngi jong phi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “ ‘Te kane kan long ka pud kaba shatei jong phi: na kata ka Duriaw Bakhraw, phin thew dak ha u lum Hor:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na u lum Hor, phin thew haduh ba phi poi bsut sha Hamath; bad ka jinglam noh jong kata ka pud, kan long sha Sedad:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ka pud kan nang suh haduh Siphron, bad ka bakut jong ka, kan long ha Hasar-enan: kane keiñ kan long ka pud shaphang shatei jong phi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “ ‘Te phin buh pud, ban long ka pud shaphang mihngi naduh Hasar-enan haduh Shepham:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kata ka pud, kan hiar naduh Shepham haduh Riblah, shaphang mihngi na Ain, bad kata ka pud, kan noh arsut, bad kan kot ruh haduh ka rud ka duriaw Khinnereth shaphang mihngi:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kata ka pud, kan leit hiar haduh ka Jordan, bad ka bakut jong ka, kan long ha kata ka Duriaw Mluh: kane keiñ kan long ka ri jong phi, bad ki pud jong ka baroh sawdong.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses u la hukum ïa ki khun Israel, u da ong, “Kane ka long kata ka ri ïa kaba phin ïoh bynta da ka jingkhalai, ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum ban ai ha ki khyndai jaid, bad ha kata ka shiteng kawei ka jaid:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> namar ka jaid ki khun u Reuben katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, bad ka jaid ki khun u Gad katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki la lah shim ïa la ka bynta trai, bad kaba shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh ki la lah shim ïa la ka bynta trai:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ar jaid, bad shiteng jaid, ki la lah shim ïa la ka bynta trai shaphang shane ka Jordan, marpyrshah ka Jerikho shaphang mihngi, shaphang kaba mih ka sngi keiñ.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Kine ki long ki kyrteng jong kita ki rangbah ki ban pynïabynta ïa kata ka ri ha phi: u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te phin shim ïa uwei uwei uba rangbah na kawei kawei ka jaid, ban ïasam bynta ïa kata ka ri.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te kine ki long ki kyrteng jong kita ki briew: na ka jaid Judah — u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad na ka jaid ki khun u Simeon — u Shemuel u khun u Ammihud.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ka jaid Benjamin — u Elidad u khun u Khislon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Dan — u Bukki u khun u Jogli.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U rangbah ki khun u Joseph, namar ka jaid ki khun u Manasseh — u Hanniel u khun u Ephod.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Ephraim — u Kemuel u khun u Shiphtan.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Sabulon — u Elisaphan u khun u Parnakh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Issakhar — u Paltiel u khun u Assan.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Asher — u Ahihud u khun u Shelomi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u rangbah ka jaid ki khun u Naphtali — u Pedahel u khun u Ammihud.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kine keiñ ki dei kita ïa kiba U Trai u la hukum ba kin ïasam bynta ha ki khun Israel ha ka ri Kanaan."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, harud ka Jordan, marpyrshah ka Jerikho, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To hukum ïa ki khun Israel, ba kin ai ha ki Lebi na kata ka bynta trai ka jingïoh pateng jong ki, ïa ki nongbah ba kin ïashongneh ha ki; bad phin ai ruh ha kita ki Lebi, ïa ki rudnong hajan kita ki nongbah baroh sawdong ïa ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ïa kita ki nongbah kin ïoh, ba kin ïashongneh ha ki; bad kita ki rudnong jong ki, kin long ïa ki jingri jong ki, bad ïa ki spah jong ki, bad ïa ki mrad jong ki baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kita ki rudnong jong kita ki nongbah, ïa kiba phin ai ha kita ki Lebi, kin kot naduh ka kynroh ka nongbah shabar shi hajar pruh baroh sawdong.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te phin thew na shabar kata ka nongbah ha ka phang mihngi, ar hajar pruh, bad ha ka phang shathie, ar hajar pruh, bad ha ka phang sepngi, ar hajar pruh, bad ha ka phang shatei, ar hajar pruh, te kata ka nongbah kan long hapdeng. Kane keiñ kan long ki rudnong jong kita ki nongbah ha ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te na kita ki nongbah ïa kiba phin ai ha kita ki Lebi, hynriew tylli, kin long ki nongbah jaka rieh, ïa kiba phin buh ba u nongpynïap briew u lah ban phet ïap hangta: bad nalor kita, phin pyntam sa sawphew ar ki nongbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kita ki nongbah baroh ïa kiba phin ai ha kita ki Lebi, kin long sawphew phra ki nongbah, ïa kita keiñ, lem bad ki rudnong jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kita ki nongbah ïa kiba phin ai na ka jingïoh pateng ki khun Israel, na kita kiba bun, phin shim shibun; bad na kita kiba khyndiat, phin shim khyndiat: uwei uwei baroh un ai na la ki nongbah ha kita ki Lebi katba shong ka bynta pateng jong u, ïa kaba u la ïoh pateng.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, U da ong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, to ong ruh ha ki, ‘Ynda phi la poi sha shiliang ka Jordan ha ka ri Kanaan,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> te phin ïabuh ki nongbah, ban long ki nongbah jaka rieh ïa phi; ba u nongpynïap briew uba la kum pynïap ïa u briew, u la lah ban phet ïap hangta.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kine ki nongbah, kin long ki jaka rieh ha phi na u nongpynhiar kput ka snam; ba yn ym pynïap ïa uta u nongpynïap briew, tad ynda u la ïeng ha ka jingbishar ha khmat uta u paidlang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te na kine ki nongbah ïa kiba phin ai, hynriew tylli ki nongbah, kin long ki jaka rieh ha phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lai tylli ki nongbah, phin ai shaphang shane ka Jordan, bad lai tylli ki nongbah, phin ai ha ka ri Kanaan; kin long ki nongbah jaka rieh ha phi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kine ki hynriew tylli ki nongbah, kin long ki jaka rieh, ïa ki khun Israel, bad ïa u sohshnong, bad ïa u nongwan hap hapdeng jong ki de: ba uno uno baroh uba kum pynïap ïa u briew, u lah ban phet ïap hangta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “ ‘Te lada u shoh ïa u da ka atiar nar, ba kumta u ïap noh, u long u nongshohnoh: ïa uta u nongshohnoh, yn pynïap noh shisha.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te lada u lynthem ïa u da u maw, ba kumta u lah ban ïap, te lada u ïap noh, uta u long u nongshohnoh: ïa uta u nongshohnoh, yn pynïap noh shisha.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Lane lada u shoh ïa u da u sping, da kaba u lah ban ïap, bad lada u ïap noh, uta u long u nongshohnoh: ïa uta u nongshohnoh, yn pynïap noh shisha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Dei uta u nongpynhiar kput ka snam hi u ban pynïap ïa uta u nongpynïap briew: haba u shem ïa u, un pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad lada u khynñiat ïa u, na kaba shun, lane ba u shat ha u, ba u da leh khnang, ba kumta u ïap;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> lane na kaba shun u da shoh ïa u da ka kti jong u, ba kumta u ïap: ïa uta uba la shoh ïa u, yn pynïap noh shisha; naba u long u nongshohnoh: u nongpynhiar kput ka snam, un pynïap noh ïa uta u nongshohnoh, haba u shem ïa u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “ ‘Hynrei, lada u kum khynñiat kyndit ïa u, khlem ka jingshun, lane lada u la shat ei ei ruh ha u, khlem da leh khnang,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> lane da u maw, da kaba u lah ban ïap, te haba um ïohi ïa u, u la pyndei ïa uta ha u, ba kumta u ïap, haba um long u nongshun jong u, bad ba um wad khnang ïa ka ban pynsniew ïa u:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> te kumta, to ai ba uta u paidlang un bishar hapdeng uta u nongpynïap briew bad u nongpynhiar kput ka snam katba kum kine ki jingbishar:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad uta u paidlang un pyllait noh ïa uta u nongpynïap briew na ka kti jong uta u nongpynhiar kput ka snam, bad uta u paidlang un pynphai pat ïa u sha ka nongbah jaka rieh ka jong u, sha kaba u la phet ïap: te un ïaishong sah hangta ha ban da ïap u rangbah lyngdoh ïa uba la pynsleh lyngdoh, ïa uba la pynsleh da ka umphniang bakyntang,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> hynrei, lada uta u nongpynïap briew un leit palat ïa ka pud ka nongbah jaka rieh jong u, sha kaba u la phet ïap;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> te lada uta u nongpynhiar kput ka snam un shem ïa u shabar kata ka pud ka nongbah jaka rieh jong u, bad lada uta u nongpynhiar kput ka snam un pynïap noh ïa uta u nongpynïap briew; wat tei pop ka snam halor jong u:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> namar ka la dei keiñ ïa u, ban shong sah hapoh kata ka nongbah jaka rieh jong u haduh ka jingïap uta u rangbah lyngdoh: hynrei, ynda u la ïap uta u rangbah lyngdoh, uta u nongpynïap briew u lah ban leit phai pat sha ka ri ka bynta trai jong u.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Kumta, kine kin long ka hukum ka jingbishar ha phi ha ki jingkha pateng baroh jong phi ha ki ïing jong phi baroh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ‘Uno uno ruh u ban pynïap ïa u briew, ïa uta u nongpynïap briew yn pynïap na ka shyntur ki sakhi: hynrei, tang uwei u nongsakhi um bit ban sakhi pyrshah ïa u briew ba un ïap.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Nalor kata ruh, to wat shim kuna na ka bynta ka jingim u nongshohnoh, ïa uba la pynrem ban ïap: hynrei shisha to pynïap duh ïa u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To wat shim kuna ruh na uta uba la phet ïap noh sha kata ka nongbah jaka rieh jong u, ba un ïoh wan phai pat ban shongneh ha ka ri, haduh ka jingïap uta u lyngdoh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ba phin ym pyntngit sang ïa ka ri ha kaba phi shong: namar kane ka snam kan pyntngit sang ïa ka khyndew: bad yn ym lah pynkhuid ïa kata ka khyndew na kata ka snam ïa kaba la theh ha ka, hynrei, tang da ka snam jong uta uba la theh ïa ka.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Namar kata, to wat pyntngit sang ïa ka khyndew ha kaba phin ïashongneh, hapdeng kaba nga shongneh ma nga: namar nga U Trai, nga shongneh hapdeng ki khun Israel.’ ”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki tymmen ki san ki ïing ki khun u Gilead, u khun u Makhir, uba u khun u Manasseh, na ki ïing ki khun u Joseph, ki la ïawan hajan, ki la kren ruh ha khmat u Moses, bad ha khmat ki rangbah, kata, ha khmat ki tymmen ki san ki khun Israel:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ki la ong, “U Trai u la hukum ïa u kynrad jong nga ba un ai ïa kata ka ri ban long ka bynta pateng ha ki khun Israel da ka jingkhalai: bad la hukum ïa u kynrad jong nga na U Trai ba un ai ïa ka bynta pateng u Selophehad uba u para jong ngi ha ki khun kynthei jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te lada kin long ki tnga ki khun shynrang kiba na kiwei pat ki jaid ki khun Israel, kumta ïa ka bynta pateng jong ki, yn shim noh na kata ka bynta pateng jong ki kpa jong ngi, bad yn pynïasoh lang ïa ka bad ka bynta pateng jong kata ka jaid ha kaba la pdiang ïa ki: te yn pynduna ïa kata ka bynta jingïoh pateng jong ngi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad haba kan long ka jubili jong ki khun Israel, te ïa ka bynta pateng jong ki, yn pynïasoh lang bad ka bynta pateng jong kata ka jaid ha kaba la pdiang ïa ki: bad kumta, yn shim noh ïa ka bynta pateng jong ki na kata ka bynta pateng ka jaid ki kpa jong ngi.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Moses, u la hukum ïa ki khun Israel katba kum kata ka ktien U Trai, u da ong, “Ka jaid ki khun shynrang u Joseph ka kren ïa kaba dei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Dei kane ïa kaba la hukum U Trai shaphang ki khun kynthei u Selophehad, u da ong, ‘To ai kin long ki tnga jongno jongno katba ki ibit hi; hynrei, kin long ki tnga tang ha kiba na ki ïing ka jaid u kpa jong ki.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, ïa ka bynta pateng jong ki khun Israel, yn ym pynkynriah noh na kawei ka jaid sha kawei pat ka jaid; namar uwei uwei baroh na ki khun Israel, un ïaineh keiñ ha ka bynta pateng ka jaid ki kpa jong u hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ka khun kynthei baroh, kaba don ka bynta pateng ha kano kano ruh ka jaid ki khun Israel, kan long ka tnga ha uwei uba na ka ïing ka jaid u kpa jong ka hi, ba ki khun Israel kin dup ïoh uwei uwei baroh ïa ka bynta pateng ki kpa jong u hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lymne wat ai ban pynkynriah ïa ka bynta pateng na kawei ka jaid sha kawei pat ka jaid; namar ki jaid ki khun Israel, kin ïaisah kawei kawei baroh ha la ka jong hi ka bynta pateng.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumba u la hukum U Trai ha u Moses, kumta keiñ ki la leh ki khun kynthei u Selophehad:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> namar ka Mahlah, ka Tirsah, bad ka Hoglah, bad ka Milkah, bad ka Noah, kiba ki khun kynthei u Selophehad, ki la long ki tnga ha ki khun shynrang ki kpanah ki kpasan jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki la long ki tnga ha kiba na ki kur ki khun shynrang u Manasseh uba u khun u Joseph, bad ka bynta pateng jong ki ka la ïaisah ha ka jaid ki kur u kpa jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kine long ki hukum bad ki jingbishar, ïa kiba u la hukum U Trai ha ki khun Israel da ka kti u Moses, ha ki pyntha ka ri Moab, hajan ka Jordan, ha marpyrshah ka Jerikho."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;